# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:12
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_7f31fb74:

    # "I make it in time for class, though not in time for breakfast."
    "なんとか授業には間に合う、朝食はパスする羽目になったけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:14
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_76acec4f:

    # "The classroom is bathing in the gentle light of the sun."
    "教室はやわらかな日差しに包まれている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:16
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_84b35954:

    # "This means that it's going to be intolerably hot in the afternoon. For now, though, it's pleasant."
    "ということは、午後にはどうしようもないほど暑くなる。でも今のところは快適だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:18
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ef36b290:

    # "I look at Misha and Shizune's animated discussion about whatever, Hanako staring out of the classroom window, Mutou stumbling into the classroom four minutes late and with no recollection of what he's supposed to be teaching today."
    "ミーシャと静音は活き活きとなにかを話し合っていて、華子は窓の外を眺めている。武藤先生はよろめきながら、今日はなにを教えるのかも覚えていないまま、４分遅れで教室に入ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:20
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_bb7f4611:

    # "I could never imagine dropping out of school just like that, even if it's only for a few weeks."
    "自分があんなにあっけなく学校に来なくなるさまは想像できないな。たとえたった数週間であっても。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:22
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_bac92b0e:

    # "On the other hand, Rin doesn't seem to have a problem with the idea, or going through with it."
    "一方で、琳はそんな考えにも、実際にそうしてしまうことにも、抵抗はないように見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:24
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_5caa598f:

    # "Then again, somehow I got caught along in her insane isolation, even if we ended up hurting each other."
    "とはいえ、どういうわけか俺は琳の常識外れな孤独になし崩しに身を委ねていった。その結果、お互いを傷つけることになると分かっていても。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:26
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9a496fce:

    # "Or did we? Maybe only I got hurt."
    "いや、ほんとうにお互いか？　ひょっとしたら傷ついたのは俺だけだったのかも。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:31
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3a907645:

    # "It takes me until late in the afternoon to realize that today is Monday. The art club meets today."
    "午後の遅い時間になるまで、今日が月曜だと気づかなかった。美術部の活動がある日だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:33
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_a416797a:

    # "Not just that. Due to the exams, this will be the last art club meeting before summer vacation."
    "それだけじゃない。試験があるので、これが夏休み前の最後の活動だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:36
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_c7a2ba03:

    # "I have no real business going there…"
    "もう顔を出す筋合いもないけど……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:38
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_692d23cb:

    # "But I want to talk with the teacher."
    "でも先生とは話しておきたい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:43
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_e0072604:

    # "So, I end up loitering awkwardly in front of the art room, waiting for the meeting to end."
    "そんなわけで俺は美術室の前で部活が終わるのを待って、所在なげにうろうろすることになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:45
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_cd742d22:

    # no "That's it for this trimester, everyone!"
    no "今学期の活動は以上だ、諸君！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:47
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_834b7f71:

    # "His voice is loud enough to be heard through the door and way too enthusiastic for it to be genuine."
    "先生の声はドア越しでも届くくらい大きい。熱が入りすぎていて、わざとらしく聞こえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:49
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2e218c04:

    # no "The next meeting is after summer vacations, on the Monday of the first week of next term."
    no "次の活動は夏休みが明けてから、２学期の最初の月曜日だ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:51
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_931a477c:

    # no "I hope to see everyone there again!"
    no "また元気でこられるようにな！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:53
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2d4e2ee4:

    # no "Have a nice vacation!"
    no "ではいい夏休みを！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:61
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_65ba730a:

    # "There's a confused answering chorus of voices, and the door to the classroom opens, releasing a flow of students."
    "困惑したような返答が唱和されると、教室のドアが開いて生徒たちが流れ出てくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:63
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4ee3fa5a:

    # "I wait for everyone else to leave, so that I can talk to Nomiya alone. It's almost dinnertime, so I don't have to wait too long."
    "先生と二人きりで話せるよう、みんなが出ていくのを待つ。もうすぐ夕飯の時間なので、長くは待たずに済む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:70
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ad927562:

    # "Without Rin, it feels pretty pointless to go there, but I want to talk with the teacher."
    "琳がいないと、あそこに行く意味はまるでない気がするけど、でも先生と話がしたい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:75
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_be2393a2:

    # "The meeting itself isn't noteworthy, just as my skills with water colors are not worth mentioning."
    "俺の水彩画の腕と同じで、今日の活動自体は特に大したことはない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:77
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4fe8a008:

    # "Nomiya tries to encourage and advise me without sounding too condescending, but he's not doing a very good job of it."
    "野宮先生はあまり上から目線に聞こえないよう努力しながら、俺を励ましたり助言をしたりするけど、大してうまくいっていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:79
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_46374257:

    # "If nothing else, joining the art club has taught me that I like art. It would be nice if I could actually try and make some art in the art club, though."
    "少なくとも、美術部に入ったことで、俺は芸術が好きなんだということが理解できた。実際に美術部で芸術作品を作り上げることができたら良かったんだけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:81
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_f0c94bcf:

    # "After the fruits of everyone's labor have been piled into a neat stack on the teacher's desk, he clears his throat to give a little speech."
    "みんなの作業の成果が先生の机の上にきれいに重ねられると、先生はまたちょっとしたスピーチをしようと咳払いをする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:86
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_cd742d22_1:

    # no "That's it for this trimester, everyone!"
    no "今学期の活動は以上だ、諸君！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:88
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ad24b41e:

    # "His voice is pretty loud and way too enthusiastic for it to be genuine."
    "先生の声はやたらと大きい上に、熱が入りすぎていて、わざとらしく聞こえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:93
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2e218c04_1:

    # no "The next meeting is after summer vacations, on the Monday of the first week of next term."
    no "次の活動は夏休みが明けてから、２学期の最初の月曜日だ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:95
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_931a477c_1:

    # no "I hope to see everyone there again!"
    no "また元気でこられるようにな！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:100
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2d4e2ee4_1:

    # no "Have a nice vacation!"
    no "ではいい夏休みを！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:107
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_8ad95814:

    # "Everyone wishes him a nice vacation back as they file out the door."
    "みんなも同じように返事を返しながら、ぞろぞろと教室を出ていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:109
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6f112a37:

    # "I stay behind, waiting until the two of us are alone. It's almost dinnertime, so I don't have to wait long."
    "俺はその場にとどまって、先生と二人きりになるまで待つ。もうすぐ夕飯の時間なので、長くは待たずに済む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:111
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_980d9bf6:

    # "Nomiya is looking through the paintings, some of which are actually pretty nice."
    "野宮先生は提出された絵に目を通している。そのいくつかは本当によく描けている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:113
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_fb54616f:

    # "Rin might outclass everyone else in the art club, but she isn't the only one with talent."
    "琳は美術部の他の誰よりも上手いかもしれないけど、才能があるのは琳だけじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:115
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_54219272:

    # hi "Excuse me, teacher…"
    hi "すみません、先生……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:122
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_54034757:

    # no "Hmm? What is it, Nakai?"
    no "んん？　どうかしたのかね、中井？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:124
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3aab9384:

    # "He raises his eyebrows questioningly, smiling widely."
    "先生は尋ねるように眉をつり上げて、大きく笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:126
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_31f4c323:

    # hi "It's about Rin…"
    hi "琳のことなんですけど……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:131
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_36329094:

    # no "Oh? Is something wrong with Tezuka?"
    no "ほう？　手塚がどうかしたのかね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:133
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_fc0a34fe:

    # hi "No, but…"
    hi "いえ、ただ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:135
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d38f6202:

    # "I hesitate for a split second, not certain how to say what I want to say, giving Nomiya enough time to start blabbering by himself."
    "言いたいことをどう伝えるべきかわからなくて、俺はほんの一瞬、躊躇してしまう。それでも先生のほうからべらべらとしゃべりだすのには十分な時間だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:140
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_e4bf3b74:

    # no "I saw her a few days ago when I was passing by at Sae's gallery."
    no "何日か前にさえの画廊に立ち寄ったら、手塚に会ったぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:142
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_337601cf:

    # no "She said she'd get one or two more paintings done for the exhibition."
    no "展覧会に向けて絵をもう１、２枚描くといっていたな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:147
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_8b9867f4:

    # no "I was quite pleased, she's a surprisingly hard worker. I'd always thought she was a bit lazy, doing what she wants instead of the assignments…"
    no "本当にうれしかったよ、驚くほどよく努力している。かねがね手塚は少々怠けがちだと思っていたのだがな、課題よりも自分のやりたいことをして……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:149
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9f26bea0:

    # "He seems to notice my anxiety and realizes he is digressing, shutting up before finishing the thought."
    "先生は俺の不安と話が脱線していることに気づいたようで、話を終える前に口を閉じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:154
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6257930d:

    # no "Ah, but you had something to talk about. What is it?"
    no "ああ、なにか話すことがあったんだったな。どうしたのかね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:156
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_38c55f9b:

    # hi "I don't know… she feels detached from everything, as if she can't think of anything but the exhibition."
    hi "なんていうか……琳はいろんなことから距離をおこうとしてるみたいなんです、展覧会のこと以外は考えられないみたいに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:161
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_9f0b7322:

    # no "Well, isn't that good? She is focused on her painting, as she should be."
    no "そりゃあ、良いことじゃないかね？　手塚は絵に集中しているんだ、そうしなきゃいかんのだからな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:163
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6a3888e3:

    # hi "Yeah, but this is different. It's like she's obsessed. I went to see her, and…"
    hi "ええ、でもそれとは違うんです。なんだかとりつかれてるみたいで。俺も会いにいったんです、それで……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:168
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ced88658:

    # no "Have you been bothering her?"
    no "なにかちょっかいを出したんじゃあるまいな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:170
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_58bc905f:

    # "He cuts in before I finish saying what I meant to say, instantly looking quite irritated."
    "先生は一瞬ですっかり怒り出した様子で、俺が言い終わる前に割り込んでくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:172
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_76d971b7:

    # hi "No… I don't… think so."
    hi "いえ……そんなことは……ないと思います"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:174
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_c9025062:

    # hi "I'm just concerned because she's stopped coming to school completely. She feels strange, too."
    hi "ただ全然学校に来なくなって心配だったんです。琳も様子が変だったし"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:176
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ea4d8105:

    # hi "Stranger than usual, at the very least."
    hi "いつもより変だったんです、どう見ても"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:181
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_2be6fe65:

    # no "Humbug! This is much more important for her than some lousy math class, or physics, or whatever."
    no "くだらない！　手塚にとってはろくでもない数学だか物理だかの授業よりずっと重要なことだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:183
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_49df6569:

    # no "This is exactly why this school is so flexible, to give every student a chance to fulfill themselves."
    no "この学校がこれほど融通が利くのはまさにそれが理由なのだ。すべての生徒に自己実現の機会を与えるためだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:188
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_07931ba5:

    # no "Tezuka is a painter, so she should paint, no? And have an exhibition. That's what artists do. She should be allowed to concentrate on that, not these other frivolous classes. She should be encouraged."
    no "手塚は絵描きなのだから、絵を描くべきだ、違うか？　そして展覧会をやる。それが芸術家というものだ 手塚はそれに集中することを認められるべきなのだ、取るに足らない授業よりもな。それを後押ししてやらねばいかんのだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:190
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_1f5efcfb:

    # no "If you think about it, it's really quite obvious."
    no "そう考えれば、まったく異論の余地はないだろう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:192
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_46db08e4:

    # "His counterarguments are not very convincing, but I'm having a hard time trying to make any kind of rebuttal."
    "先生の反論はあまり説得力がないけど、何か言い返そうとしてもなかなかできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:194
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_3c6f0e91:

    # "My grudging silence is interpreted as assent, and Nomiya turns to shuffle the stack of turned-in assignments on his desk like a deck of cards."
    "俺がしぶしぶ黙り込むと、先生は俺が納得したととらえたようで、また机の上の提出された課題の束をトランプのようにシャッフルする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:199
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_4fd197c4:

    # no "I have to say, while we're talking about Tezuka's exhibition…"
    no "率直に言って、手塚の展覧会のことを話している間も……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:201
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_7f74f1ac:

    # no "I'm very excited to see how it turns out."
    no "これがどう転ぶか、とても楽しみだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:206
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d0e69e36:

    # no "She's still so young, yet has such wonderful skill, and style!"
    no "手塚はまだ若い、それでいてあれほど優れた技能をもっている。そしてスタイルもな！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:208
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_95a73d61:

    # "He's talking to the air, to relax the mood that got a bit too negative."
    "先生は少し暗くなりすぎた雰囲気を和らげようとして、なにもない空間に向かって話をする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:213
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_6bbc934c:

    # no "I take it that you will be attending?"
    no "中井も展覧会には行くんだろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:215
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_028d71b4:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess so."
    hi "ええ、たぶん"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:220
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_5e0f21ac:

    # no "Well, we'll meet there next."
    no "うむ、ではまたそこで会おう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:227
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_d991f2c6:

    # "I take that as my cue to leave. And I do, although I'm not happy about it."
    "それは下がってよしという合図と受け取る。そしてその通りにする。不満ではあるけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:229
translate jp a4_rin_illusions_for_people_ca80d7e4:

    # "My message didn't get through, to say the least."
    "控えめに言っても、俺の言いたいことは伝わらなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:240
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:249
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ff53f23f:

    # n "{vspace=270}The day after that, all the missed opportunities and things I should have said come crashing down on me. There's nothing left to do afterwards but brood."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n翌日、言うべきなのに言えなかったこと、その機会を逃したことがどっとのしかかってくる。今となってはくよくよと考え込むことしかできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:251
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:258
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9afb296f:

    # n "{vspace=270}Second day. I begin to feel anxious. I start doubting my doubt and it feels stupid, especially since I still can't think about anything else than Rin."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n２日目。心配になってくる。その心配が疑わしく思えてきてバカみたいな気分になる。今でも琳のこと以外は考えられないおかげで、余計にそう思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:260
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:267
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e59a7803:

    # n "{vspace=270}Third day. Japanese exam, {b}and{/b} world history exam. Great. The thing I hate most about her is that she can make me feel this awful even though I should be focusing on entirely different stuff right now."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n３日目。国語のテスト、と同時に、世界史のテストがある。参った。あいつの一番嫌なところは、まるっきり別のことに集中しなきゃいけないのに、俺をこんなにひどい気分にさせるってことだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:269
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:276
translate jp a4_rin_demused_7bd0d1d0:

    # n "{vspace=270}Fourth day. Math exam. We have a math exam. It goes how it goes. I don't care."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n４日目。数学のテスト。なんと数学のテストだ。なるようになる。どうでもいい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:278
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:285
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c189afa1:

    # n "{vspace=270}Fifth day. Nomiya asks me again if I will attend the exhibition opening. I can't say no to him even though I seriously want to. I just don't want to discuss with him anything Rin-related so it's just better to take the path of least resistance."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n５日目。野宮先生がまた展覧会のオープニングに出席するか聞いてくる。行かないと言ってやりたくて仕方ないけど、先生にノーとはいえない。とにかく先生と琳に関することは一切話したくないので、無難な答えを返しておくのがいいってことだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:287
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:296
translate jp a4_rin_demused_784a49fa:

    # "On the sixth day, the day before the exhibition opening, I find Rin standing in the hallway in front of my room when I return to the dorms after dinner."
    "そして６日目、展覧会の前日。夕食を済ませて寮に戻ると、琳が俺の部屋の前の廊下に立っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:300
translate jp a4_rin_demused_31192155:

    # hi "What are you doing here?"
    hi "何してるんだよ、こんなところで？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:302
translate jp a4_rin_demused_6b0080ca:

    # "My tone is angrier than I intended. I'm a little disappointed that I was unable to restrain myself, but it can't be helped."
    "意図していたよりも怒った口調になってしまう。自分を抑えられないことに少し失望したけど、でもどうしようもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:304
translate jp a4_rin_demused_7b1bc929:

    # "Rin just stands there, like she just happened to coincidentally be standing around here where she has no business being. The way she reacts so coolly to everything annoys me now."
    "琳は用もなく偶然そこに居合わせたかのように、ただ突っ立っている。琳のリアクションはなにに対してもそっけなくて、それがまた俺をいらだたせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:306
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76bb851c:

    # "This is not good. It's been six days, and the sight of her has me boiling. She hasn't even opened her mouth yet."
    "良くないな。あれから６日も経っているけど、琳の姿を見ただけで怒りが爆発しそうだ。琳はまだ口も開いてないのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:311
translate jp a4_rin_demused_574f5625:

    # rin "Finished painting."
    rin "絵が描きあがったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:313
translate jp a4_rin_demused_0339551f:

    # hi "Shouldn't you be at the gallery? Preparing?"
    hi "画廊にいなきゃだめなんじゃないのか？　準備とかあるんだろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:318
translate jp a4_rin_demused_32e621dd:

    # rin "They said no."
    rin "いなくていいって"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:320
translate jp a4_rin_demused_59f480b4:

    # "I guess the gallery owner does that part then, getting the paintings framed, hung on the walls and whatnot."
    "さえさんが準備をしてるんだろう。絵を額に入れたり、壁にかけたりとか、そんなことを。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:322
translate jp a4_rin_demused_72b47445:

    # hi "So, why are you here?"
    hi "それで、なんでここにいるんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:327
translate jp a4_rin_demused_94a52e1f:

    # rin "Felt like it."
    rin "来たかったから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:329
translate jp a4_rin_demused_6bdaaf03:

    # "This same old stupid pattern emerges again; me asking her questions to which she replies with answers that don't answer anything, because it's the only other way we can converse."
    "またいつもの馬鹿なパターンが浮かび上がる。俺が琳に質問をして、琳は答えになっていない答えを返す。なぜなら、俺たちはそんな形でしか会話ができないからだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:331
translate jp a4_rin_demused_663541e5:

    # "Apart from me listening to her blabbering about whatever, which isn't really a conversation."
    "俺が琳のどうでもいいおしゃべりを聞くのは別だけど、それは会話とはいえないだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:333
translate jp a4_rin_demused_794ad679:

    # "Is this a play? Are there some unseen roles that we have unknowingly set ourselves into, dictating the rules of engagement whenever we see each other, inevitably leading to us hurting each other?"
    "これは演劇なのか？　俺たちは知らないうちに目に見えない役に配されていて、顔を合わせている間は決められた条件にしたがって行動させられて、否応なくお互いに傷つけあうように仕向けられているのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:335
translate jp a4_rin_demused_d4744e37:

    # "Her nonchalant answers accompanied by even more nonchalant shrugs leave me none the wiser. I guess I should be happy that the exhibition preparations are complete."
    "琳の無頓着な答えと、さらに無頓着そうに肩をすくめる様子を見ても、相変わらず何も分からない。展覧会の準備が済んだことを俺は喜ぶべきなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:343
translate jp a4_rin_demused_eb7842ab:

    # "When I walk into my room, I hear her footsteps following me in."
    "部屋に入ると、琳が中までついてくるのが足音でわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:345
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e50c3695:

    # "I didn't invite her in. I won't ask her to leave."
    "迎え入れたつもりはないぞ。追い出すつもりもないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:359
translate jp a4_rin_demused_51c8ea4c:

    # "She claims my bed without asking permission, making me wish that I had taken the time to make it before I left in the morning, then stands up again as though she sat on hot coals."
    "琳は俺に黙ってベッドに腰掛ける。朝、部屋を出る前に整えておけばよかった。すると今度は焼けた炭の上にでも座ったかのように立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:364
translate jp a4_rin_demused_76d044ed:

    # "I half-lean against the single corner of my desktop that isn't cluttered with stuff, to rest my legs at least a little bit."
    "俺は散らかっていない机の一角に寄り掛かって、足だけでも休める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:369
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9fc28e0d:

    # "Rin spends a few moments glancing curiously around my room. It makes me realize that she's never seen it before."
    "琳はしばらくの間、もの珍しそうに部屋を見回している。そういえば琳はここに来たことがなかったな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:371
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ad9059a3:

    # "For a moment, she actually looks like she's concentrating. Trying to get everything. This must be the eye for detail that makes her an artist."
    "一瞬、琳は本当に集中しているような様子を見せる。すべてを感じとろうとしている。これが琳を芸術家たらしめる観察眼にちがいない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:376
translate jp a4_rin_demused_15d65c2d:

    # "Since the room is small, she quickly runs out of things to look at, but nothing else transpires, allowing the uncomfortable silence to take over the atmosphere."
    "部屋が小さいから、観察するようなものもすぐになくなるけど、他に何が出てくるでもなくて、空気が気まずい沈黙で満たされる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:378
translate jp a4_rin_demused_449f3709:

    # "The mood is chilly to say the least, and both of us are on guard, waiting for the other to make the first move."
    "控えめにいっても冷ややかな雰囲気のなか、俺たちのどちらも警戒して、お互いに相手が先に行動するのを待ち構えている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:380
translate jp a4_rin_demused_88ca76fd:

    # "Of course, Rin could play this game forever. So it has to be me."
    "もちろん、琳ならこの心理戦を永遠にでも続けられる。なら俺が先手を打つしかない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:382
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c85221a4:

    # hi "So…"
    hi "それで……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:384
translate jp a4_rin_demused_2a535c94:

    # "I give up because she'd never try to open conversation, and because it seems that she wants to say something, and I want to get it over with."
    "琳は絶対に自分から会話を始めないけど、言いたいことがあるみたいだし、俺もさっさと終わりにしたかったので、諦めて自分から話をする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:386
translate jp a4_rin_demused_d7cffadc:

    # "Why else would she be here if she didn't want to talk?"
    "話がしたくないなら、どうしてここにくるっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:388
translate jp a4_rin_demused_14925818:

    # "I don't know what to say myself. I want to be angry, but I can't bring myself to yell at her or anything."
    "何を言えばいいのか俺にもわからない。怒りたいけど、琳を怒鳴りつけたり、何かをしたりする気持ちにもなれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:390
translate jp a4_rin_demused_b908b896:

    # "My voice catches her attention, and she tries to search for words as well, but it seems that she is not entirely certain as to why she's here either."
    "俺の声が琳の注意を引いて、琳も同じように言葉を探そうとするけど、どうも琳もここに来た理由をちゃんと理解しているわけではないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:400
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e3b745d1:

    # "And so, Rin simply takes a few steps to close the distance between us and rises on the tips of her toes to even out the height difference…"
    "そこで琳はただ数歩進んで俺に近づき、高さを合わせるために爪先立ちになって……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:407
translate jp a4_rin_demused_4cf20e4a:

    # centered "'It was a bad idea.'"
    centered "『やっぱりやめておけばよかった』"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:409
translate jp a4_rin_demused_b2968db4:

    # centered "'Maybe you should forget about it, and I will too.'"
    centered "『たぶん、あのことは忘れた方がいいよ。私もそうするから』"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:413
translate jp a4_rin_demused_90729675:

    # "It's a reflex, and almost as an afterthought, the words 'no,' 'yes' and 'maybe' simultaneously surface inside my mind."
    "反射的に、そしてほとんど思いつきで、『イエス』『ノー』『たぶん』の言葉がいっせいに頭をよぎる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:415
translate jp a4_rin_demused_d38d5f1d:

    # "My hand is between her lips and mine, a wall that I raised to guard against… something."
    "俺の手が琳と俺の唇の間に割って入る。それは……何かを防ぐために打ち立てた壁だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:417
translate jp a4_rin_demused_2bc22592:

    # "Her breath feels warm against my fingers. The scent of her skin lingers about, the mysterious indescribable sensation that captures me and draws my eyes deep into hers."
    "琳の温かい息が俺の指に当たる。肌の匂いがあたりに漂い、得体のしれない、言葉では言い表せない感覚が俺をとらえ、俺の視線を琳の目の奥深くへと引きずり込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:424
translate jp a4_rin_demused_fb68f57c:

    # "The look in her eyes is surprised, quizzical as to why the impertinent hand prevented her advances."
    "琳は驚いたような目つきで、この無作法な手が琳の前進を阻んだ理由をいぶかしんでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:426
translate jp a4_rin_demused_03c5f631:

    # "Her eyes are really big and glistening with moisture, and staring right into my own with a soft gaze that I'm having a hard time to match."
    "琳の目は本当に大きく、潤いで輝いていて、俺の目を柔らかな視線でまっすぐ見つめている。俺は視線を合わせることができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:428
translate jp a4_rin_demused_03b9a4e4:

    # "Rin's half-open mouth makes her look even more confused, although the sensual way her lips are arching is signaling something completely different."
    "半開きの口のせいで琳の表情はよけいに混乱しているように見える。でもその唇が描く官能的な曲線は全く別の合図を発している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:433
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ce0164c3:

    # rin "Please."
    rin "お願い"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:438
translate jp a4_rin_demused_1f1699db:

    # rin "I need you."
    rin "君が必要なんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:440
translate jp a4_rin_demused_d927605a:

    # "The words come from her throat as a coarse whisper meant only for me, bypassing her tongue and teeth without giving them any chance to interrupt."
    "俺だけに向けられた言葉が、舌や歯に邪魔される隙を一切与えずに、琳ののどからざらついたささやきとなって出てくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:447
translate jp a4_rin_demused_acecb949:

    # "They sober me in an instant, and I clumsily flinch back to get a little bit of distance between us, painfully scraping against my desk in the process."
    "その言葉で俺は瞬時に正気に返り、不格好に後ずさって琳との距離を少し開く。体を机にこすってしまい、ひどく痛む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:449
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c77bf8b9:

    # "Maybe it's her choice of words, maybe the way she says it, but something in it puts me off."
    "琳の言葉遣いのせいかもしれないし、言い方のせいかもしれない、でもその何かが俺を不愉快にする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:451
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9cc620ed:

    # "Something is wrong, something is terribly wrong again."
    "何かが間違ってる。またしても、何かがとんでもなく間違ってる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:453
translate jp a4_rin_demused_25827a5e:

    # hi "Need me for what?"
    hi "必要って何のために？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:455
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e9163df2:

    # "All the unpleasant feelings emerge again, and I feel my heartbeat suddenly increasing at least tenfold."
    "もろもろの不快な気分がまた浮かび上がってきて、心臓の鼓動が突然１０倍は速くなった気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:460
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e17041e2:

    # "Rin's eyes go out of focus and back again as her body relaxes from its tensed state, and she stands upright again."
    "琳の身体が緊張状態からリラックスして、再びまっすぐに立つ。同時に琳の目の焦点がぼやけ、また元に戻る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:465
translate jp a4_rin_demused_0bc155f7:

    # rin "I don't think I was thinking about anything. Why do you draw patterns in that dust on your night table?"
    rin "何も考えてなかったと思う。どうしてナイトテーブルのほこりに模様を描くの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:470
translate jp a4_rin_demused_8c166848:

    # rin "There is a word for that kind of thing but I can't remember…"
    rin "そういう言葉ってあったはずなんだけど、思い出せないや……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:472
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c2ef6a90:

    # "Her remark almost throws me off track and I glance over her shoulder at the small table next to my bed, but I can't see anything from this distance."
    "琳の発言にほとんど話を煙に巻かれてしまった。琳の肩越しにベッドの横の小さいテーブルを見るけど、この距離じゃなにも見えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:474
translate jp a4_rin_demused_456d4f56:

    # "So she needs me for nothing specific?"
    "で、特に理由はないけど俺が必要だっていうのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:476
translate jp a4_rin_demused_deea301b:

    # "Just happened to come by because she thought I'd be glad to see her after she shut me out, no complaints accepted, for a week."
    "俺が喜ぶと思ってたまたまここに来たっていうのか。一週間も俺を締め出して、文句のひとつも聞いてくれないで。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:478
translate jp a4_rin_demused_a00b83cc:

    # "Completely altruistic motives?"
    "心底から人のためを思ってのことか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:480
translate jp a4_rin_demused_329b80b2:

    # "Felt like it?"
    "来たかったから？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:482
translate jp a4_rin_demused_909db814:

    # hi "Bullshit. I can answer myself."
    hi "ふざけんな。俺にはわかってるんだぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:484
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9fc58eff:

    # hi "To play mind games with whenever you want, to kiss whenever you want, to ignore whenever you want, to fulfill your whims whenever you want?"
    hi "お前の気まぐれで好き放題人を煙に巻いて、気まぐれでキスして、気まぐれで無視して、気まぐれで自分の思いつきを満たすためか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:486
translate jp a4_rin_demused_f97a24e8:

    # hi "Is that it? What you need me for?"
    hi "そういうことか？　そのために俺が必要なのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:488
translate jp a4_rin_demused_0cfbf71f:

    # "My voice is sounding very angry again, even to myself."
    "俺の声はとても怒っているように聞こえる、俺にとってさえ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:490
translate jp a4_rin_demused_809d2f18:

    # extend " Good."
    extend "いい調子だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:495
translate jp a4_rin_demused_a1c3fdcc:

    # "Rin too finally catches the mood and her curious expression changes instantly to something more uncharacteristic."
    "琳はようやく雰囲気を察したようで、その好奇心に満ちた表情から一瞬で、らしくない表情になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:500
translate jp a4_rin_demused_13f95aea:

    # rin "No—"
    rin "違う――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:502
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e282de84:

    # "She leaves it at that, her eyes restlessly wandering around, searching the room as if the words she tries to find were written in the tapestries of my walls."
    "琳はそれしか口にせず、落ちつきなく目を動かす。まるで壁のタペストリーに探している言葉が書かれでもしているかのように、部屋中を目で探し回っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:504
translate jp a4_rin_demused_a461d02c:

    # hi "Then what?"
    hi "じゃあなんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:511
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9af4a2f2:

    # rin "I needed to paint."
    rin "絵を描かなきゃいけなかったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:513
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ad9b967e:

    # "Paint."
    "絵。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:515
translate jp a4_rin_demused_21700daa:

    # "Of course. That's what artists do."
    "それはそうだろう。それが芸術家のすることだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:517
translate jp a4_rin_demused_06be40c7:

    # "The words reverberate through my being, beating in my blood over the piercing whistle of my anger."
    "その言葉が俺の中にこだまする。つんざくような怒りの音に重なって、血流の中で響き渡る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:521
translate jp a4_rin_demused_01704145:

    # hi "Don't give me that, Rin! I'm not some damn muse of yours, free to play with for the sake of painting!"
    hi "やめてくれよ、琳！　俺はお前の絵のために自由にもてあそばれる、くそったれなミューズじゃない！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:523
translate jp a4_rin_demused_5489b14d:

    # hi "I am not some medium for whatever you aspire to, I am me!"
    hi "お前が追い求めるもののための踏み台じゃない、俺は俺なんだ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:525
translate jp a4_rin_demused_26a3fc06:

    # hi "So what if I don't know anything about my future?"
    hi "自分の将来のことがなんにもわからなくて、だからなんだってんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:527
translate jp a4_rin_demused_da898656:

    # hi "There's things I want, and things I care about! Even I can dream of things other than nightmares!"
    hi "俺にだって欲しいものはあるし、気にしてることもあるんだよ！　こんな俺でも悪夢以外の夢だって見られるんだ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:529
translate jp a4_rin_demused_18b372de:

    # "I'm yelling, but I'm way past the point of caring about things like that."
    "俺は叫んでいるけど、そんなことを気にしていられる段階はとっくに通り過ぎている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:534
translate jp a4_rin_demused_6368f21f:

    # "Rin looks down at her toes and wiggles them a little melancholically while she takes in my outburst without saying anything to defend herself."
    "俺の怒鳴り声に対して何の反論もせず、琳は足下を見下ろし、つま先を若干憂鬱そうにもじもじと動かす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:536
translate jp a4_rin_demused_3478eebe:

    # "Only after I have finished does she try to respond somehow."
    "俺が怒鳴り終わって初めて、琳はなんとか答えようとする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:541
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e5d99da7:

    # rin "I can't do anything else. Or I can do all sorts of things, but I… can't… do."
    rin "私にはこれしかできないんだ。いや、どんなことでもできるけど、でも……私には……できない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:546
translate jp a4_rin_demused_3ef381c4:

    # rin "It's the only thing I sort of do properly. Most of the time."
    rin "私がわりとまともにできることはこれだけなんだ。だいたいの時は"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:548
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ffcb8c64:

    # "I understand completely. Art first, everything else second, or thousandth."
    "完全に理解できる。絵が１番で、ほかのことは全部２番目なんだ。それとも１０００番目か。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:550
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c2142b2f:

    # hi "What about me? Am I nothing? When I was interested in art, did that make you feel like I was a little interesting, for a little while?"
    hi "俺のことはどうなんだよ？　なんとも思ってないのか？　俺が美術に興味をもったとき、俺のことを少しでも面白いって思ったか？　しばらくの間でも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:552
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e245d512:

    # hi "Tell me. I really want to know. Did you ever think about my perspective, or is it just all you?"
    hi "教えてくれよ、本当に知りたいんだ。俺がどう思ってるかなんて一度でも考えたことあるか？　それとも自分さえよければそれでいいのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:554
translate jp a4_rin_demused_a3f931d8:

    # "The words rise like bile in my throat."
    "言葉が痰のようにのどに引っかかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:559
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e34a9b74:

    # "She looks alarmed. And also completely uncomprehending, as if she just doesn't understand what I'm angry about."
    "琳はおびえているみたいだ。そしてさっぱり理解できていないようだ。俺が何について怒っているのか全くわかっていないかのように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:561
translate jp a4_rin_demused_10996ab4:

    # "I can't believe she could be so stupid."
    "琳がここまでバカだったなんて、信じられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:566
translate jp a4_rin_demused_d0190ebc:

    # rin "I didn't want to—?"
    rin "そんなつもりじゃ――？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:568
translate jp a4_rin_demused_9fbe4b85:

    # "This time it's Rin who interrupts herself in midsentence."
    "今度は琳が途中で言葉を切る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:573
translate jp a4_rin_demused_5f8cd9ff:

    # rin "Don't you understand? I can't."
    rin "わからないの？　私にはできないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:575
translate jp a4_rin_demused_b046783b:

    # hi "Can't what?"
    hi "何ができないんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:577
translate jp a4_rin_demused_bf421548:

    # hi "You never explain! How am I supposed to understand anything if you never say anything?"
    hi "お前は絶対に説明しないじゃないか！　お前が何も言わないのに、どうして俺にわかるっていうんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:579
translate jp a4_rin_demused_fbab08c2:

    # hi "Why don't you ever talk?"
    hi "どうして、お前はいつも話さないんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:581
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e360754c:

    # hi "Say something!"
    hi "なんとか言えよ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:583
translate jp a4_rin_demused_0c8eefa8:

    # "But she doesn't."
    "けど琳は何も言わない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:585
translate jp a4_rin_demused_2dc193f7:

    # "Venting my anger at her feels satisfying. It feels wrong to take so much satisfaction in it, but I can't stop."
    "琳に向けて怒りをぶちまけることに満足感を覚える。こんなに満足感を覚えるのは間違っている気がするけど、自分を止めることができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:590
translate jp a4_rin_demused_3348afb5:

    # "Not wanting to face my anger head-on, Rin turns around to steadfastly look out of my window even though there is nothing to look at."
    "真正面から俺の怒りに向き合いたくない琳は窓のほうを向いて、頑なに外を見つめる。見るものなんて何もないのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:592
translate jp a4_rin_demused_74f1b510:

    # "The worst of my ire gone, I shut up as I can't be bothered to keep on yelling at the back of her head, so silence finally returns."
    "怒りのピークが過ぎ去ると、琳の後ろ頭に怒鳴り続ける気力が失せて、ようやく沈黙が戻る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:594
translate jp a4_rin_demused_1a0101c7:

    # "I try to discern some hints of her reaction through my adrenaline-distorted vision."
    "アドレナリンで歪んだ視界を通して、琳のわずかな反応をうかがおうとする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:596
translate jp a4_rin_demused_57528871:

    # "My feedback was not the best kind, but I hope Rin got the clue that she just can't ignore everything else whenever she feels like it."
    "俺の反応はベストとは言えないものだったけど、あらゆるものを気分次第で無視することなんてできないんだ、ということを少しでも琳が気づいてくれればと願う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:598
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c5280ef1:

    # "I'd hate it if she didn't. She never ever listens to anything, she's so unaffected by the world around her."
    "もし琳に伝わらなかったとしたら残念だ。琳はいつも絶対に人の話を聞かないし、周りの世界からまるで影響を受けていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:600
translate jp a4_rin_demused_159f59d9:

    # "Not this time, it seems."
    "でも今回はそうでもないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:602
translate jp a4_rin_demused_1371e84c:

    # "Her body is shaking like from holding back tears, but I already know that Rin is not crying."
    "琳の体は涙をこらえるかのように震えているけど、でも琳は泣いてなんかいないことはわかっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:604
translate jp a4_rin_demused_4c154e58:

    # "Her indifference made me so furious. Now that it's gone, I'm at a loss. I wonder…"
    "琳の無関心さが俺をあんなに怒らせた。それがなくなった今、俺は困り果てている。もしかして……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:606
translate jp a4_rin_demused_4966d1e6:

    # "Did I go too far?"
    "俺はやり過ぎたのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:608
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ca81d4a9:

    # hi "Look, I—"
    hi "なあ、俺――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:613
translate jp a4_rin_demused_1149e5d6:

    # rin "Go away."
    rin "あっち行って"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:615
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e6915669:

    # rin "Go away, Hisao."
    rin "出てって、久夫"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:617
translate jp a4_rin_demused_958e171d:

    # "Her voice is tiny and tired as she says this, but I hear the words clear as day."
    "そう呟く琳の声は小さく、くたびれていたけど、その言葉ははっきりと聞こえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:619
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:621
translate jp a4_rin_demused_e0f03b86:

    # "What is there to say any more?"
    "これ以上言うべきことがあるか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:623
translate jp a4_rin_demused_7f393299:

    # hi "This is my room."
    hi "ここは俺の部屋だぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:625
translate jp a4_rin_demused_7ec7dab5:

    # "The blunt, hollow remark is a fitting conclusion for this unpleasant discussion that became an even more unpleasant and very one-sided yelling match."
    "そっけなくうつろなその言葉はこの不愉快な議論、そして更に不愉快かつとても一方的な怒鳴り合いと化したこの議論の締めくくりにふさわしい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:630
translate jp a4_rin_demused_2cbb4a3b:

    # "After a moment of collecting herself Rin just gives up, I can see it from the way she slumps her shoulders, and walks out."
    "ふっと気を取り直すと、琳はただ諦める。その肩を落とした様子からわかる。そして部屋を出て行く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:635
translate jp a4_rin_demused_af16ff33:

    # "Even though she deliberately looks to the other direction, I can see how she's biting the corner of her lip so hard it might start bleeding if she won't stop."
    "わざとそっぽを向いているけど、くちびるの端を強く噛んでいるのが見える。早く止めないと出血しかねない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:637
translate jp a4_rin_demused_81325e86:

    # "As she makes her exit, I realize that she left the door open when she came in and my yelling must've echoed around the dorm hallways."
    "琳が出ていくと、琳が入ってきたときにドアを開けっ放しにしていたことに、そして俺の怒鳴り声が寮の廊下に響き渡っていたであろうことに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:639
translate jp a4_rin_demused_64b0036f:

    # "I sigh. Now that she's gone, I am left alone with my guilt."
    "俺はため息をつく。琳がいなくなった今、俺は罪悪感とともに一人残される。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:641
translate jp a4_rin_demused_91dd6dfe:

    # "As the thumping in my chest slowly subdues, anxiety replaces it."
    "少しずつ心臓が落ち着いていくと、今度は不安に駆られる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:643
translate jp a4_rin_demused_07372464:

    # "Somehow, I feel that none of this would've ever happened if not for me."
    "どうも、これは俺の身から出たことのように思えてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:645
translate jp a4_rin_demused_be3e51ff:

    # "No matter how infuriating, unbearable and outrageous Rin is, she is not the Rin I thought I knew."
    "琳がどんなに腹立たしくて、常軌を逸していて気に食わないやつだとしても、あれは俺が知っていると思っていた琳じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:647
translate jp a4_rin_demused_17f8e076:

    # "The Rin that I expected Rin to be."
    "俺の期待していた琳とは。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:649
translate jp a4_rin_demused_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:651
translate jp a4_rin_demused_87b374e0:

    # "Was it me who caused all this by talking Rin into taking her chances with the exhibition?"
    "展覧会に挑戦するよう琳を説得して、こんなことを引き起こしたのは俺だったっていうのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:653
translate jp a4_rin_demused_2ec4fcb3:

    # "Am I directly responsible for Rin becoming like she has been for the past weeks?"
    "この数週間、琳があんな状態になっていたのはひとえに俺の責任なのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:655
translate jp a4_rin_demused_daa1faec:

    # "I can't think of any other explanation for her weird behavior than the exhibition and all the things that came along with it."
    "展覧会と、それにかかわる全てのこと以外に、琳のおかしな振る舞いの理由を思いつくことができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:657
translate jp a4_rin_demused_c3e57bc0:

    # "Maybe it was the only way that could have brought us closer, but all it did was separate us further away from each other, and now beyond the reach of either of us."
    "これが俺たちが仲を深めることができる唯一の方法だったのかもしれない。でもその結果は、お互いをもっと遠くへと引き離しただけだった。今となっては、どちらからも手の届かない場所に。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:662
translate jp a4_rin_demused_6e0c50f7:

    # "I bang my head hard against the wall."
    "俺は頭を壁に強く打ちつける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:669
translate jp a4_rin_demused_498da18b:

    # "Twice, to make sure it hurts."
    "２回、確かに痛みを負うまで。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:686
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_e9ec2627:

    # "A headache is relentlessly thumping against the back of my head as I push open the door to the 22nd Corner."
    "22nd Cornerへのドアを押し開ける瞬間にも、頭痛がしつこく俺の後頭部をひっぱたいてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:688
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4ec2eeed:

    # "Apart from that, I'm perfectly calm."
    "それを除けば、俺はすっかり落ち着いている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:692
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:695
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_69ee39bd:

    # n "{vspace=60}After venting on Rin all that anger that I had bottled inside, it felt like a great weight had been lifted from my heart."
    n "\n\n琳に向かって溜まりに溜まった怒りをぶつけると、巨大な重しが心臓から取り外されたような気分になった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:697
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_18b060d2:

    # n "The tension that had grasped my mind for the past few weeks faded away without leaving even a shadow behind."
    n "この数週間、俺の心をつかんでいた緊張も跡形もなく消えていった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:699
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_35b9b761:

    # n "In this nearly Zen-like state of enlightenment I realized that perhaps it was a bad idea to yell at her like that."
    n "この禅の悟りのような状態になって初めて、俺は琳をあんなふうに怒鳴りつけたのはまずかったかもしれないという気になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:701
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a6e98ad6:

    # n "{vspace=30}I really meant it, but what good does blowing up like that do? Nothing."
    n "\nあれは俺の本音だった。でもあんな風に怒りをぶちまけて何かいいことがあるか？　あるわけがない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:703
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_de0cf754:

    # n "I am not like that. I don't normally yell at people. I don't know why I did yesterday."
    n "俺はそんなやつじゃない。普段なら俺は人を怒鳴りつけたりしない。どうして昨日は怒鳴ってしまったのかわからない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:705
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3256da36:

    # n "So I keep feeling really guilty about it and wanting to take my words back."
    n "だから俺はずっと後ろめたい気持ちが続いていて、言った言葉も取り消したいと思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:707
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5d9486bc:

    # n "{vspace=60}Rin is probably upset too. Even more than my own behavior, her reaction shocked me."
    n "\n\n琳もきっと怒ってるだろう。自分の取った態度よりも、琳の反応のほうがショックだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:709
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_18a0c250:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=30}I've always thought of her as unchanging, detached from her surroundings so that seeing my yelling get her so upset felt… out of place."
    nvl clear
    n "\n琳はいつも周囲から距離を置いていて、変わることがないとずっと思っていた。だから怒鳴ったあとに琳があんなに怒ったのを見て……琳らしくないと思った。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:713
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_23cfa8b2:

    # n "{vspace=30}I wonder if she understands how I feel?"
    n "\n琳は俺の気持ちをわかってくれたんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:715
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a416026e:

    # n "In Rin's world everything seems to be so absolute and subjective… absolutely subjective, as if she was completely unable to see things from other points of view than her own."
    n "琳の世界はなにもかもが絶対で、自分本位……絶対的に自分本位なんだ。自分以外の他者の視点でものを見ることが一切できないかのように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:717
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_492227c4:

    # n "But ultimately, is anyone able to do it? Maybe objectivity and altruism are just illusions for people who like to think of themselves as compassionate."
    n "でも結局、それができる人なんているんだろうか？　客観性とか利他主義なんて、自分が心優しいと思いたい人たちのための幻想でしかない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:719
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_84f03e94:

    # n "Just like art is an illusion for people who think reality is merely a veil for something greater."
    n "現実がより大きな何かを覆い隠すベールに過ぎないと考える人にとって、芸術が幻想でしかないのと同じように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:721
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_c9f1153e:

    # n "Even when you stop thinking that the world revolves around you or start thinking outside of the mythical box, you are just inside another, bigger box that you can't escape."
    n "もし世界が自分を中心に回っていると考えるのをやめても、あるいは神話的な箱の外側について考え始めても、人は抜け出すことのできないもっと大きな箱の中にいるに過ぎない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:723
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_c70301ec:

    # n "{vspace=30}Maybe that, ultimately, makes her like the rest of us."
    n "\nそうすると結局、琳も俺たちと同じってことかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:727
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:740
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_d25001ff:

    # "I step through the door to find a gallery full of illusioned people."
    "ドアをくぐりぬけると、ギャラリーの中は幻想にとらわれた人でいっぱいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:742
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3da58e1f:

    # "Despite Sae's remarks during my earlier visits I always thought it was very spacious, but now when it's crowded like this it looks positively cramped."
    "俺が前に来たときにさえさんがああ言ってはいたけど、ここはとても広いとずっと思っていた。だけど今はこんなにもごった返していて、とても窮屈だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:747
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_cc50cec4:

    # "I immediately notice Sae standing in the middle of a lively discussion, busily chattering with some old gentlemen."
    "俺はすぐにさえさんが活発な話し合いの中心に立っていて、忙しそうに何人かの老紳士と話をしていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:749
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_c361493f:

    # "She's actually pretty tall and kind of cool-looking, so she stands out in the crowd."
    "さえさんは実は結構背が高くて、見た目もどこかクールなので、人混みの中で目立っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:751
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a9ce38bc:

    # "There are a few dozen wine glasses laid on the tables along the back wall, filled with burgundy liquid. A vast majority of the guests are sipping from their own glasses."
    "ワイングラスが数十個、後ろの壁に沿って並んだテーブルの上に置かれていて、赤紫色の液体が注がれている。ほとんどの来客が自分のグラスに口をつけている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:753
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_7cd827ac:

    # "The socialites and art connoisseurs are mingling happily, exchanging mild opinions about Rin's art which seems to be a secondary object of interest for most."
    "著名人や芸術の専門家が楽しそうに行き交っていて、琳の作品について当たり障りのない意見を交わしている。ほとんどの人にとっては、そこは第一の目的じゃないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:755
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_d46da2da:

    # "I feel distanced, excluded from the other people here."
    "周りの人たちから遠ざけられ、爪弾きにされたような気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:757
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_73ce016d:

    # "I can't claim even at a stretch to be a social chameleon, so this situation is quite unnerving."
    "俺は控えめに言っても色んな人相手に話を合わせるのは苦手なので、この状況はひどく気が滅入る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:759
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_6f96359c:

    # "Since I don't blend into the crowd at all, I just fake that I do, trying to look as cool and smooth as I can."
    "この人混みの中で完全に浮いているので、俺は浮いていないふりをして、できるだけ平静で上品そうな風を装う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:761
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_6d98206a:

    # "I wonder how Rin is handling all this. If it was me, I would be quite freaked out."
    "こんなの、琳はどうしているんだろう。俺だったらパニくってしまうだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:769
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_cdc85e8e:

    # "Throwing the anxiety aside, I try to carefully navigate through the crowd, stealing peeks at the framed paintings now hanging on the walls."
    "不安を投げ打つと、俺は慎重に人だかりをかき分けながら、壁にかかっている額に収められた絵をちらちらと見る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:778
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_e37f01d4:

    # "Rin's exhibition takes about half of the gallery's wall space. Some paintings are less familiar than others, but I recognize most of them."
    "琳の展覧会はギャラリーの壁のスペースの半分を使っている。いくつかの絵はあまり見慣れないものだけど、大体は見分けがつく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:780
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_8051b9a2:

    # "Some I've seen being created at the club meetings after all, or remember from the time when Rin was choosing her portfolio."
    "そのうちいくつかは美術部の活動中に描いているのを見たし、あるいは琳が自分のポートフォリオから選んでいたときに見かけたのを覚えている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:782
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5c9641bc:

    # "I note that a couple of the unfinished paintings are framed and on the wall as well. Maybe that's what they call coincidental art?"
    "いくつかの未完成の絵も額に入れられて壁にかかっているのに気づく。偶然の産物ってやつだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:784
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_afe8fadc:

    # "Even Rin's failures, if you can call them that, became exhibits of her skill. Quite paradoxical."
    "琳の失敗作でさえ、仮にこれがそう呼べるとしてもだけど、その腕前の証しになった。実に矛盾しているな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:792
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_36595355:

    # "She herself is nowhere to be seen, which is strange because even though it's crowded, the gallery {b}is{/b} pretty small."
    "琳の姿はどこにも見あたらない。おかしいな。混んでいるとはいえ、このギャラリーは確かにかなり小さいから。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:794
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_78ea3f71:

    # "It's fine, sort of. I don't know how to face her after yesterday. Maybe I shouldn't have even come."
    "ある意味よかったと思う。昨日のことのあとで、どんな顔をして琳に会えばいいのかわからない。来るべきでさえなかったのかも。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:796
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b7b167a0:

    # "But I promised various people, Rin included, that I would, so…"
    "でも、いろいろな人に来ると約束してしまった。琳も含めて。だから……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:798
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_43093a63:

    # "Damn, it sounds like I do the things I do because some kind of instinctual properness compels me to, not because it would be sensible (or not)."
    "くそ、これじゃまるで理にかなっているか（あるいはないか）どうかじゃなくて、その場の愛想みたいなものに動かされてなにごとも決めているみたいじゃないか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:808
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_993ea1ac:

    # "I sneak closer to Sae to wait for a lull in the conversation so I can chat her up too."
    "俺はさえさんに忍び寄って、声をかけられるようになるまで、立ち話が途切れるのを待つ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:810
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_0ca65725:

    # "Even though her voice is almost completely buried under the general background noise, I hear bits and pieces of her talking about Rin."
    "さえさんの声はほとんど喧噪に埋もれてしまっているけど、琳のことを話しているのが断片的に聞きとれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:812
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3022a3f0:

    # sa "Yes, she is a high schooler at a local school… even though she's graduating next year I'm sure various art schools would be interested in…"
    sa "ええ、彼女は地元の高校生で……来年卒業するんですが、きっとさまざまな美術学校が興味を持つかと……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:814
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5c97a6ee:

    # sa "…I thought it'd be interesting to have an exhibition of someone who is still in early stages of development…"
    sa "……まだ成長期の早い段階にある子の展覧会をするのも面白いと思いまして……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:816
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_206f5e36:

    # "It's so strange, it's like Rin is some kind of mini-celebrity even though this is nothing but a small exhibition opening at a small art gallery of a small town."
    "本当に妙な感じだ、小さな町の小さなギャラリーでやる小さな展覧会に過ぎないのに、これじゃ琳がちょっとした有名人みたいじゃないか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:818
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_07764980:

    # sa "In fact, there is a friend of mine from…"
    sa "実は、私の友人が……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:823
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_40554ac7:

    # mystery "It's Hisao!"
    mystery "久夫くんじゃん！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:825
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_de462b46:

    # "My eavesdropping is interrupted by a familiar voice and a familiar slap to the back. I don't need to guess the source of either, even without turning around."
    "俺の盗み聞きは馴染みのある声と、馴染みのある背中への平手打ちに邪魔される。それが誰のものかは、振り返らなくたってわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:827
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_2b3d4056:

    # hi "Hi Emi."
    hi "よお、笑美"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:848
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_29e755bd:

    # emi "Hi! Are you like, a representative of the art club or something? I don't see anyone else from the school here…"
    emi "おっす！　美術部の代表かなにかできたの？　他に学校の子、見かけないからさ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:853
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a594f5be:

    # hi "Umm… I don't know, really. I guess I am if that's the case."
    hi "うーん……さあ。それが本当ならそうなのかもな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:855
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_0583026f:

    # hi "What about you?"
    hi "お前はどうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:860
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_de967264:

    # emi "What about me?"
    emi "あたしがなによ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:862
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f5a21f62:

    # hi "Err…"
    hi "えーっと……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:867
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_517d1d91:

    # emi "You didn't think I'm interested in art? Is that it, Hisao?"
    emi "あたしが美術に興味あるなんて思ってなかった？　そーゆーこと？　久夫くん"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:869
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_15f22183:

    # hi "No, that's not what I… well, maybe a little, if you put it that way."
    hi "いや、そういうつもりじゃ……まあ少しは思ってたかもな、そういう言い方するなら"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:871
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a1c1b2d5:

    # hi "I mean, even though you hang out with Rin I've never heard you talk about art with her so…"
    hi "そうじゃなくて、お前はいつも琳とつるんでるけど、お前が美術の話をしてるのなんて聞いたことなかったからさ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:876
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_83589a0d:

    # "Emi huffs and looks around her, looking discontented."
    "笑美は機嫌を損ねて、面白くなさそうに辺りを見回す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:881
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3e44e17a:

    # emi "It's true, I don't get it at all, but she came to my track meet so I thought it's only fair to return the favor."
    emi "確かにそうだよ。芸術なんて全然わかんない。でも琳は陸上の競技会に来てくれたから、恩返しするのが公平って話だよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:886
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_06111ba7:

    # "She leans closer, trying to look confidential but only managing to look conspiring."
    "笑美は身を乗り出してくる。秘密がありそうな素振りをしようとするけど、悪巧みをしているようにしか見えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:888
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_8221bfd4:

    # emi "Do you {b}get{/b} art?"
    emi "久夫くんは芸術ってわかる？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:890
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_2c690564:

    # hi "No. No, I don't."
    hi "いや。わからない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:892
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_689872df:

    # hi "At all."
    hi "全然"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:897
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_cce5fcc8:

    # "My emphasizing headshake draws a giggle and a cheery headshake of her own out of Emi."
    "俺が目立つように頭を振ると、笑美もくすくすと笑って元気よく頭を振る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:902
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5b34a6d0:

    # emi "Me neither!"
    emi "あたしもなんだ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:907
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b195e96f:

    # emi "Hey, let's go talk with Rin! I bet you haven't yet, because I haven't either."
    emi "ねえ、琳と話しにいこうよ！　まだなんでしょ、あたしもまだだから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:912
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_269bc9d0:

    # emi "Come on!"
    emi "いこ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:930
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a32ed3ae:

    # "Before she has a chance to forcefully drag me to Rin, Nomiya appears behind her with Rin in his tow."
    "笑美が俺を琳のところまで無理矢理引っ張り始める前に、野宮先生が笑美の後ろから琳を連れて現れる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:939
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_9160c98c:

    # "She's not dressed for the occasion, instead opting for the usual school uniform and unkempt hair."
    "琳は特別な格好はしていなくて、いつもの制服に乱れた髪のままだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:941
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f236e970:

    # "Maybe her natural look is what suits her the best."
    "自然な格好でいるのが琳には一番似合っているのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:946
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_03739b69:

    # emi "Hello, teacher! Hi, Rin!"
    emi "先生、こんにちは！　琳も！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:948
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_c73fdc78:

    # "Unfazed, Emi greets the teacher cheerfully, causing him to turn around and look down confusedly."
    "笑美は臆することなく元気に先生に挨拶する。先生は振り返って、混乱したように見下ろす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:953
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_e5a20256:

    # no "Who are you?"
    no "君は？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:958
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_34fed68d:

    # emi "I'm Emi, from school, class 3-4. Don't you remember?"
    emi "山久学園の茨崎です。３－４の。覚えてませんか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:960
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_89bce785:

    # "She looks positively shocked at the prospect that there could be a person who doesn't know her."
    "自分を知らない人間が存在しうるという可能性に、笑美は明らかにショックを受けたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:965
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_11ee8254:

    # no "Oh, sorry. You are in the same class as Tezuka is, right?"
    no "おお、すまない。手塚と同じクラスだったな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:970
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b286e85a:

    # emi "Yeah!"
    emi "はい！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:975
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_1daed64e:

    # no "You'll have to pardon me, I have trouble remembering students who don't take art."
    no "許してくれ、美術をとっていない生徒を覚えるのは苦手なものでな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:980
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f8e4b68f:

    # emi "Don't mind, don't mind!"
    emi "気にしないでください！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:985
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f9024bee:

    # emi "Hi Rin!"
    emi "こんちは、琳！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:990
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "どうも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:995
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_9cda1dad:

    # emi "Congratulations for your super cool art thing! I'm sure you'll be a big hit!"
    emi "とってもすっごい展覧会でよかったね！　きっと大ヒットになるよ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:997
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_aed72305:

    # "She throws her arms into the air for boisterous emphasis, almost hitting me in the face."
    "笑美は腕を乱暴に振り上げて力説すると、俺の顔に当たりそうになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1002
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a21e593c:

    # emi "And look, Hisao came too!"
    emi "それにほら、久夫くんも来てくれたよ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1007
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5f559886:

    # "Rin doesn't look at me, nor does she greet me."
    "琳は俺のほうを見ないし、挨拶もしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1009
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_503fd49a:

    # hi "Congratulations, Rin."
    hi "おめでとう、琳"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1011
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_08fc470e:

    # "She keeps averting her gaze, pointedly looking at her sandals."
    "視線は逸らしたまま、サンダルをじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1016
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_649d4c9b:

    # "Oblivious to the tension between us and ignorant of what happened yesterday, Emi keeps on blabbering about this and that to an unresponsive Rin."
    "俺たち２人の間の緊張に気づかず、昨日の出来事についても知らない笑美は、無反応な琳に向かってあれこれとおしゃべりを続けている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1018
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_e9294ae9:

    # "I guess she's used to not getting much out of her at times."
    "きっと笑美は、琳からあまり反応が返ってこないことに慣れているんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1043
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_e99d6ce1:

    # "Before long, Nomiya and Sae turn to Rin, introducing her."
    "やがて野宮先生とさえさんが琳のほうを向いて、琳を紹介する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1045
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_9aa74b97:

    # "Expecting it, I catch the second of confusion when the guests see her arms."
    "予想はついていたけど、来客が琳の腕を見て困惑する瞬間をとらえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1050
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_6d88c598:

    # "Sae is luckily on the ball and briefly explains about our school."
    "幸い、さえさんはそれに感づいて、俺たちの学校のことを簡潔に説明する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1052
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f47b727b:

    # "Doubtful faces quickly change to curious."
    "疑問に満ちた顔つきが興味深々なものに早変わりする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1054
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5f14c8e3:

    # "Man" "Would you mind telling us something about your art?"
    "男性" "君の作品についてなにか話してくれないかね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1056
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_68f9a3e4:

    # "Man" "I thought the development is quite easily noticeable, what do you yourself think of the differences between the older and more current works?"
    "男性" "成長がとても目覚しいと私は感じたんだ、君自身は過去の作品といまの作品の違いについてなにか思うことは？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1058
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_98907ffb:

    # "Man" "It's quite rare for someone so young to dabble into abstraction."
    "男性" "その若さで抽象画に手をつけるというのは本当に珍しいね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1060
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4e19473e:

    # "Woman" "It would've been interesting to see how you work!"
    "女性" "どうやって描くのか見てみたいわ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1062
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4834f385:

    # "Man" "Oh, definitely! I assume you use your feet? Must've been a great trouble to learn it, you should be proud."
    "男性" "ああ、まったくだ！　足を使うんだろう？　慣れるまでは相当苦労したんだろうね、立派なことだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1067
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_7c641666:

    # rin "I… ummm…"
    rin "私……うーん……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1071
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_888dbb6e:

    # "Man" "Will you be pursuing a career as an artist after school?"
    "男性" "卒業しても芸術家としての道を進むつもりかい？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1073
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_1598f9c5:

    # "She is bombarded with so many questions she can't even hope to answer all of them."
    "琳はあまりにたくさんの質問を浴びせられて、全部に答えることは望むべくもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1075
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_08ee072a:

    # "Maybe that's for the best, Rin tends to talk nonsense more than occasionally."
    "その方がいいのかもしれない。琳は馬鹿げたことを口走ることが多すぎるからな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1077
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4da16c57:

    # "Man" "So where do you get your ideas?"
    "男性" "それで、どこからアイディアを得るのかね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1082
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_673dbc28:

    # rin "That's the fourth, I mean fifth worst…"
    rin "それ、４番目、いや５番目に最悪……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1084
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_ed5867c3:

    # "Rin keeps stumbling with her words, looking more and more vexed by the expectant inquiries."
    "琳はずっと言葉を詰まらせている。期待のこもった質問にどんどんいらだちが募っているようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1089
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b7f8fd67:

    # rin "Ah…"
    rin "ああ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1091
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_cecd7896:

    # "Everyone is waiting for her to say something, but she looks like a cat got her tongue."
    "みんな琳が何か言うのを待っているけど、琳は黙りこくったままだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1093
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b75b20f1:

    # "Each question piling up just adds to her distress."
    "質問が一つ重なるたびに、琳の苦痛が増えていくだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1098
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a86cd36d:

    # "I fail to hear the question that is the proverbial one too many."
    "慣用句で言うところの『一言多すぎる』質問を、俺は聞き損ねる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1100
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_225297ac:

    # "It's like a motor stalling."
    "エンジンが止まってしまうかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1121
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_7fd81128:

    # "Rin just freezes for a long, long second until she falls on her knees, hitting the floor ungracefully like a sack of potatoes."
    "琳はしばらくの間ただ固まっていて、そしてジャガイモで一杯の袋のように、不恰好にひざから崩れ落ちて床に座り込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1123
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_be781a3f:

    # "Woman" "Are you all right?"
    "女性" "どうしたの、大丈夫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1125
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_48efa8e6:

    # rin "I don't know…"
    rin "わかんない……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1127
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_96e070f8:

    # no "Tezuka? What's wrong, girl?"
    no "手塚？　どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1129
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_eab25463:

    # rin "I don't know what's wrong…"
    rin "なにがおかしいのかわかんない……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1131
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_f080eb7f:

    # "A terrible silence falls upon the people gathered around Rin."
    "凄絶な沈黙が琳を取り囲む人たちに覆い被さる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1133
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_2a09f94f:

    # "Everyone is petrified, not knowing how to react to her sudden… seizure, or something."
    "みんな身動きもできず、琳の突然の……発作、のようなものにどう反応したらいいかわからないでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1135
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_2e170a2d:

    # "She breathes with deep, trembling gasps as if she was running out of air, staring ahead of herself with hollow eyes."
    "空虚な目で前を見つめながら、琳は深く息をついて、空気が薄くなっているかのように震えて息を切らしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1154
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3b57b7b5:

    # "Seeing that nobody does anything, I force myself to step to Rin and lift her up from the floor, letting her lean against me to keep standing."
    "誰もどうにもできないのを見て、俺はむりやり琳のもとに歩み寄ると、床から立ち上がらせて俺のほうへ寄りかからせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1156
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b605b41d:

    # hi "Would you like some fresh air? OK, let's go outside for a bit."
    hi "外の空気でも吸うか？　よし、ちょっと外に出よう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1158
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a01b4bc5:

    # "I don't even wait for her to answer before grasping her shoulder and pulling her past the stunned-looking Nomiya, Sae, Emi and guests."
    "俺は返答を待つこともせず、琳の肩を引っつかむと、茫然とした顔つきの野宮先生やさえさん、笑美や他の来客の前を通り過ぎていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1160
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5ae85c24:

    # hi "Excuse us."
    hi "失礼します"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1169
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_47ff5bf3:

    # "The cool evening breeze hits my face at the door."
    "戸口に立つと、涼しい夜の空気が俺の顔に当たる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1174
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_769ae004:

    # "I let go of Rin and she leans against the stone wall, trying to catch her breath."
    "琳を放すと、琳は石の壁に寄りかかって、息を整えようとする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1176
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_dd0872f3:

    # hi "Are you all right?"
    hi "大丈夫か？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1181
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_5d06bfbe:

    # rin "I couldn't say anything…"
    rin "なにもいえなかったよ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1183
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_b64b1686:

    # "Rin is still not looking at me, so I look away too."
    "琳はいまだに俺のほうを見ようとしないから、俺もそっぽを向く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1187
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_16b8f65c:

    # "The streetlights and colored neon signs twist my vision into a blur of near-blindness, forcing me to look back."
    "街灯やネオンサインが俺の視界をぼんやりと、盲目に近い状態にまで歪めてしまい、俺は仕方なく視線を戻す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1189
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_1a60359f:

    # "At least she talks, even if she's not directing her words to me."
    "少なくとも琳は話している。俺に向けてではないとしても。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1191
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_2ff399c8:

    # hi "What did you want to say?"
    hi "何を言いたかったんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1193
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_78de87e9:

    # "Maybe both of us can imagine that we are talking to an invisible friend."
    "俺たちのどちらも、目に見えない友達としゃべっていると想像すればいいのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1198
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4e7ade8d:

    # rin "I don't know."
    rin "わかんない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1203
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_a1c846a2:

    # rin "Something that would have meant something."
    rin "なにかの意味のありそうな、なにか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1205
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1207
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_7a537113:

    # "The silence lasts for a long time."
    "長い間、沈黙が続く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1209
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4eef4039:

    # "I don't feel comfortable being alone with Rin. I am not good at imagining things that don't exist, do… or that things that exist, don't."
    "琳と二人きりになるのは居心地が良くない。俺はその場にないものが存在する……あるいはその場にあるものが存在しない、という想像をするのは得意じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1211
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_28aa5a0b:

    # hi "We should go back in."
    hi "もう中に戻ろう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1213
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_4b5021f3:

    # hi "The guests Sae invited are in there, they probably want to meet you and talk with you."
    hi "さえさんが招待した人もいるんだ。きっとお前に会って話したいんだと思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1215
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_ccc3e9d3:

    # hi "You know, ask you questions and stuff. About those paintings you worked so hard for."
    hi "ほら、質問とかいろいろ聞いたり。お前があんなにがんばって描いた絵のことをさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1220
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_3304ddd5:

    # rin "I don't want them to ask me questions like that. I can never say the right things."
    rin "あんな風に質問してほしくない。正しいことなんて絶対言えないのに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1222
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_75fa03c0:

    # hi "What do you want then?"
    hi "じゃあ何がどうなればいいんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1224
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1231
translate jp a4_rin_the_scene_ef00f851:

    # rin "That someone wouldn't have to ask questions from me." nointeract
    rin "人が私に質問しなくてすむようになってほしい" nointeract

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1254
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1257
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d72a268b:

    # n "{vspace=60}Vacation, huh?"
    n "\n夏休みだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1259
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_329304f8:

    # n "Some people will stay at the school even over the holidays, some will go back to their families."
    n "休みの間も学校に残るやつはいるし、家族のもとへ帰るやつもいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1261
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_8784e275:

    # n "I probably should make the trip back home and report to my parents that I'm alive and well."
    n "俺も地元に帰って、俺がちゃんと元気にやってるって報告したほうがいいんだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1263
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a9ed5746:

    # n "{vspace=30}Not much to do at the school anyway, I suppose."
    n "学校に残ったって、大してやることもないだろうし。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1265
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_53975cd8:

    # n "Next trimester will be stressful. Everyone will have to seriously start thinking about what to do after graduation."
    n "次の学期はぴりぴりするだろうな。みんな卒業したあとのことを真剣に考えないといけなくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1267
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_dc5d6e2d:

    # n "{vspace=60}Including me…"
    n "\n\nそれは俺もだけど……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1271
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1277
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_ee4c3c2d:

    # "A look at my doodles convinces me to stop trying to salvage them. It's a mess of lifeless lines, a waste of paper if it wasn't the flip side of my exam."
    "自分の落書きを見て、それを取っておこうという気が失せる。生気のない線がぐちゃぐちゃに絡まっている。テスト用紙の裏でなければ紙の無駄でしかない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1281
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1284
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_7ea49f73:

    # n "{vspace=90}Maybe it's because I didn't really set out to draw anything in particular."
    n "\n\n\n特に何を描くつもりでもなかったからだろうか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1286
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_3a273586:

    # n "I just wanted to kill some time, so the drawing became exactly like I am."
    n "暇をつぶしたかっただけなので、絵もまさしく俺みたいになったんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1288
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_fb104aa5:

    # n "Without a direction to go to."
    n "どこへ向かうあてもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1290
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_bdb42e04:

    # n "{vspace=60}It'd be easier if I had some special talent, like Rin."
    n "\nもっと才能があれば簡単なんだけどな、琳みたいに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1292
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_e6acf50c:

    # n "She has it easy."
    n "あいつなら簡単だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1294
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_103f5a47:

    # n "It makes me kind of jealous."
    n "なんだかうらやましくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1296
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_f33578dd:

    # n "It pisses me off that she herself can't seem to be happy about it."
    n "それなのに琳はちっとも嬉しそうじゃなくて、腹が立つ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1300
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1307
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_0e057b53:

    # mu "Aaaand… time!"
    mu "よおし……それまで！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1309
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_e5356afe:

    # "Mutou's call for the end of the exam draws groans of displeasure from half the class."
    "武藤先生のテストの終わりを告げる声に、クラスの半分から不満のうめき声が上がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1311
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_3b0137b6:

    # "I don't blame them, the exam was kinda tricky."
    "無理もない、テストはなんだか難しかったからな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1313
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d8faab67:

    # "Mutou expects a lot from our class, even though he's not strict at all. I guess he'd like all of us to become scientists."
    "武藤先生はそんなに厳しいほうじゃないけど、俺たちのクラスには大きな期待を寄せている。俺たち全員が科学者になるのがお望みなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1318
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_9586a0ba:

    # mu "Put down your pencils and turn in your papers please."
    mu "鉛筆を置いて、回答用紙を提出するように"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1320
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_1457f049:

    # "The biggest groan comes from the desk to my side."
    "いちばん大きなうめき声は俺のすぐ横から聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1334
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_eb0752fd:

    # "Misha's despair is almost tangible."
    "ミーシャの落胆が手に取るようにわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1336
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a623fe97:

    # "The dark aura of lost hope emanating from her seat makes me simultaneously frightened of and sympathetic to her."
    "希望をなくした暗いオーラがミーシャの席から漂ってきて、俺は驚くと同時に同情する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1341
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_7a348718:

    # mu "Now then, there should be homeroom before you are free, but I only have a few announcements to make so this should be over quickly…"
    mu "さて、お前たちを解放する前にホームルームをしないといけないが、いくつか連絡事項があるだけだし、すぐに済むだろう……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1343
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_91fd800a:

    # "His announcements are never important, so I listen to him only with one ear."
    "先生の連絡が重要だったためしがないので、俺は片耳で話を聞くだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1345
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_cb89b0f0:

    # "Misha seems to be too down in the dumps to even pretend attentiveness."
    "ミーシャはあまりに落ち込んでいて、話を聞いているふりもできないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1347
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_239b2154:

    # "She slumps her head against the desktop, looking stricken."
    "打ちひしがれたように、机に頭を突っ伏している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1349
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_273b3860:

    # hi "Cheer up, Misha."
    hi "元気だせよ、ミーシャ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1351
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_5729ea2e:

    # hi "It's vacation! Don't worry about the test."
    hi "夏休みだぜ！　テストの心配はするなよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1356
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_f5ce562e:

    # mi "Thanks, Hicchan."
    mi "ありがと、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1358
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b6fb34fa:

    # "Her frown becomes a small smile, and a sparkle of excitement lights in her eyes."
    "渋い顔がかすかな笑顔になると、興奮の火花がその目にともる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1363
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6d2eb729:

    # mi "What're you going to do over your summer vacation, Hicchan?"
    mi "夏休みはなにするの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1368
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a16a5be9:

    # mi "I'm going to Shicchan's place, they have this awesome and super cool mansion! I'm so excited~!"
    mi "わたしはしっちゃんの家に行くんだ。こーんなすっごい豪邸なんだよ！　超楽しみ～！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1373
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6b4afc3d:

    # mi "I'm sure it'll be the bestest summer vacation ever~!"
    mi "最高の夏休みになること請け合いだね～！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1375
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a1a6f5e9:

    # "She seems to have forgotten all about her misery in a few seconds and bounces up and down on her seat as if to pump up her excitement."
    "ミーシャはたった数秒で自分の不遇をきれいさっぱり忘れ去ったみたいで、椅子の上で熱狂をかき立てるように上下に跳ねる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1377
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b725356d:

    # hi "I don't really have any plans, I guess…"
    hi "俺はなんにも予定なし、かな……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1382
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_afb19d07:

    # mi "Is that so~? Maybe you should—"
    mi "そうなの～？ ひっちゃんもさ――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1387
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_4c5bd624:

    # "A finger tapping her shoulder steals Misha's attention away from me."
    "ミーシャの肩をたたく指が、注意をそちらへと向かわせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1392
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_9e779258:

    # "Shizune points to Mutou, who is expectantly looking back at the two of them."
    "静音が武藤先生を指差していて、先生は期待するように２人を見返している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1397
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b24d56ea:

    # mi "Oops! Sorry, Shicchan, I didn't notice teacher finished already, ehehe~."
    mi "あれれ！　ごめんね、しっちゃん。先生の話、もう終わってたんだ、えへへ～"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1399
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6c3c9bf1:

    # "She clears her throat and takes a deep breath…"
    "ミーシャは咳払いをして、深く息をつくと……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1405
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_745cb1ff:

    # mi "Stand!"
    mi "起立！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1407
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6fe3f787:

    # "I stand up with everyone."
    "俺もみんなと一緒に立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1411
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1414
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6cc7d4ef:

    # n "{vspace=60}Since I came here, I've always wondered about something."
    n "\n\nここに来たときから、いつも不思議に思っていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1416
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_e7fa89db:

    # n "What do the wheelchair-bound students think about this daily tradition, being unable to do it 'properly?'"
    n "車椅子から離れられない生徒は、この毎日の習わしを『正しく』行えないことをどう思っているんだろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1418
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_26d00bbf:

    # n "Is it a faux pas to keep to this tradition in a place that bypasses many others for convenience?"
    n "利便のために他の多くの習わしを省略している場で、これだけを続けるというのは不作法というものだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1420
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_19bacfc2:

    # n "Even though I never asked anyone, during these short weeks here I've come to the conclusion that they definitely are not insulted."
    n "誰かに聞いたことは一度もないけど、ここに来てからの数週間のあいだに達した結論は、間違いなく彼らはそれを侮辱と感じていない、ということだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1422
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_c4785b31:

    # n "They understand."
    n "みんなわかってるんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1424
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_ef0629f8:

    # n "That's what I like about this school. Nobody is too uptight about anything, everyone is so… considerate and understanding of each other."
    n "この学校のいいところはそこだ。どんなことであれ、むやみに堅苦しいことを言うやつはいない。誰もが……お互いを理解し、思いやっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1428
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_bd48d49c:

    # n "{vspace=60}I wish the whole world could be like this."
    n "\n\n世界全体がそうなればいいのにな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1432
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1438
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_7b28a49b:

    # mi "Booooow!"
    mi "れぇーい！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1446
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6b23919b:

    # "I turn the page slowly, listening to the rustling sound the paper makes when my fingers grasp it."
    "紙を指でつまんだときに擦れる音を聞きながら、俺はゆっくりとページをめくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1450
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1453
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_86da4edd:

    # n "{vspace=30}I'm restless."
    n "じっとしていられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1455
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_675b692c:

    # n "It's the summer vacation."
    n "夏休みだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1457
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_411e7189:

    # n "No class, no homework, no art club meetings. Just free time to spend however I want."
    n "授業もない、宿題もない、美術部の集まりもない。なんでも好きなことをして過ごせる、ただただ自由な時間。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1459
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d7334c86:

    # n "It doesn't feel like anything."
    n "なにもする気がしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1461
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_04741731:

    # n "I tried to cheer up Misha, but I'm not feeling too cheery myself."
    n "ミーシャを励まそうとしたけど、俺自身、それほど元気がない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1463
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_bc409793:

    # n "To be honest, the free time is intimidating. It reminds me of the hospital and the long, meaningless days that had to be filled somehow."
    n "正直なところ、自由な時間というのには怖気づいてしまう。病院のことと、とにかくやり過ごすしかなかった長くて無意味な日々を思い出させる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1465
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_965a7f41:

    # n "The only difference is that there I was bound to the ward, guarded by the Cerberus-like nurses."
    n "唯一の違いといえば、俺は病棟に閉じ込められていて、地獄の門番のような看護婦に見張られていたということくらいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1467
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_12f67585:

    # n "Reading was a good solution back then, but the thought of spending my summer vacation reading books feels… nerdy."
    n "あのときは、本を読むことがいい気晴らしになったけど、夏休みをそれだけで過ごすというのはなんだか……ガリ勉みたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1469
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a98c4e1c:

    # n "That has nothing to do with the fact that I'm reading even now… I'm just killing time and trying to fight my anxiety."
    n "別にいま本を読んでいることとは関係ないけど……いまはただ時間をつぶして、不安を紛らわせているだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1471
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_ac10d3df:

    # n "Besides, my mind is on other matters, stretching in too many directions to make sense of any of them."
    n "それに俺の関心は他のことに向いている。でもあっちこっちに広がりすぎていて、そのどれも把握できていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1475
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_7:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1478
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_8860c35a:

    # "Thus, the book I've been on since Tuesday is progressing s{w=0.3}l{w=0.3}o{w=0.3}w{w=0.3}l{w=0.3}y{w=0.3}."
    "それでこの本は、火曜日からゆ{w=0.3}っ{w=0.3}く{w=0.3}り{w=0.3}と{w=0.3}読み進めているわけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1480
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_4e28a1bf:

    # "It feels like this book is taking me longer to read than it took the author to write."
    "作者がこの本を書くのにかかった時間よりも長くなりそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1482
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_a1425505:

    # "I try to put it down for a while, then read some again, start all over from the beginning, read each page twice."
    "しばらく読むのをやめたり、また少し読んだり、最初から読み直したり、同じページを２回ずつ読んだりする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1484
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_779fba11:

    # "Nothing works, I have zero concentration."
    "ダメだ。ぜんぜん集中できない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1486
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_3ab31011:

    # "Taking it with me just in case, I head out to get some fresh air and inspiration as to what to do."
    "念のためにこの本を持って、新鮮な空気と、暇つぶしのネタを求めて外に出る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1491
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_f77d067f:

    # "I make my way to the quad, passing by students heading for the gates."
    "校門へ向かう生徒たちとすれ違って、中庭に向かう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1493
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_1e743d52:

    # "The hastiest ones are leaving for their homes already, judging from the luggage some are dragging with them."
    "そのうち何人かがトランクを引っ張っているのを見るに、気の早いやつはもう家路につくみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1495
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_feb6c205:

    # "I guess that no matter how hospitable Yamaku is, home is still home. Still, I heard some people will be staying here over the vacation."
    "どんなに山久が居心地のいい場所でも、我が家は我が家なんだろうな。夏休み中、ずっとここに残るのもいるらしいけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1497
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b8936b45:

    # "The quad is big enough for its center to be shadowless no matter how high or low the sun is."
    "太陽の高さに関係なく、中庭はその中央に常に陽が当たるくらいの大きさがある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1499
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_61cf9b68:

    # "I stop in the middle and bask in the warmth."
    "俺は真ん中で足を止めて暖かさを体で感じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1501
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_62b8076d:

    # "The brightness makes me squint my eyes when I look towards the main building."
    "本校舎の方を見ると、まぶしさで目を開けていられないくらいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1503
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_56243082:

    # "It looks all but abandoned already."
    "もうほとんど人がいなくなってしまったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1505
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_ebb9ceb1:

    # "Yuuko wasn't at work today, so the next time I can get books from the school library is after vacation."
    "今日は優子さんはいなかったから、次に図書室から本を借りられるのは休みが明けてからだな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1507
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_62d933f8:

    # "There is a public library somewhere, I'm sure, but I'm feeling too lethargic to find out where it is."
    "どこかに公立図書館があるのは間違いないけど、面倒すぎてどこにあるのか探す気にはなれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1512
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b0a8f307:

    # "The hall is equally dead so I have to content myself with returning to the dorms, ending my leisurely walk sooner than I expected."
    "ロビーも同じくらい人の気配がなくて、俺はのんびりとした散歩を考えていたよりも早く切り上げて、寮に戻るはめになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1514
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_6b043fbf:

    # "Then again, I wasn't quite sure what I was expecting in the first place."
    "とはいえ、そもそも何を考えていたのかよくわかっていなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1519
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_460dd3b4:

    # "On a moment's impulse I enter the girls' dorm to see if Rin or Emi are there."
    "衝動的に、琳か笑美がいないかと思って俺は女子寮に足を運ぶ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1521
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d9d89bdb:

    # "Neither is, so I go back to my own room to dwell on my lethargy."
    "でも二人ともいないので、自分の無気力をくよくよと嘆くために部屋に戻る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1528
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_8:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1531
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_e38a9633:

    # n "{vspace=60}I should talk things through with Rin."
    n "\n\n琳としっかり話さないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1533
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_4a5e72e3:

    # n "She really bothers me."
    n "あいつには本当にイライラする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1535
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_809c916d:

    # n "{vspace=60}Defying the conceptual equivalent of gravity, she balances on the thin line zigzagging between insanity, incomprehensibility and instability."
    n "\n\n重力と概念的に等価な何かに逆らうかのように、琳は狂気や不可解さ、不安定さの隙間をぬうような、細いジグザグの線の上でバランスをとっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1537
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_5aad4976:

    # n "Rin affects me too. She challenges me in ways that I didn't know… or more accurately, didn't hope existed."
    n "琳は俺の心を動かしもする。俺が知らなかった……いや正確には、存在してほしくなかったような方法で俺を試す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1539
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_5efc5572:

    # n "{vspace=60}I've started to wonder whether these feelings are really love, or I was just fooling myself."
    n "\n\nこの気持ちは本当に愛なんだろうか。それとも俺が思い違いをしているだけなのか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1541
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_175d0cbc:

    # n "Surely, it would be insanity to consider that?"
    n "こんなことを考えるなんて、狂気に違いないよな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1543
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d46739d0:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}For the rest of the day, Rin, the hospital, Yamaku and vacation swirl through my head."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\nそれから一日中、琳や病院、山久や夏休みのことが頭を駆けめぐった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1547
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_f0f8a830:

    # n "{vspace=30}I can't concentrate even on concentrating."
    n "\n集中することにさえ集中できない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1549
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_71457912:

    # n "{vspace=30}Thoughts seem to come and go haphazardly, fragmented into too-small pieces of cognition."
    n "\n考えがでたらめに浮かんでは消え、小さすぎる思考のかけらへとばらばらに崩れていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1551
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_58a290e8:

    # n "{vspace=30}I pick up the book and manage to read a hundred pages, but I'm sure by tomorrow I'll have no recollection of what happened in the story."
    n "\n俺は本を拾い上げてどうにか１００ページ読み進めたけど、明日までにはどういう話だったのかきれいさっぱり忘れている自信がある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1553
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_3a7fa6e0:

    # n "{vspace=30}I try to clean up my room, but even that proves to be too bothersome, too time-consuming and requiring too much attention to detail."
    n "\n部屋を掃除しようとするけど、それさえわずらわしいことだった。時間がかかりすぎるし、細かいところにより多くの注意を払わなきゃいけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1555
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_554e90c4:

    # n "It's usually like this. When you have 'nothing to do,' you do nothing even if you could."
    n "いつものことだけど。『やることがない』というのは、やることがあってもなにもしないということなんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1560
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_9:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1566
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_61247b6a:

    # "As expected, mom calls me and I end up promising to see if I can get a train ticket for tomorrow, or failing that, the day after."
    "案の定、母親から電話があって、明日か、それがだめなら明後日の新幹線のチケットが取れるかどうか確認すると約束してしまった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1569
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_10:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1586
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_89cff40f:

    # n "{vspace=60}Maybe I'll go downtown tomorrow anyway. I could do some shopping or something."
    n "\n\nどっちにしろ明日は街に出る。買い物でもしよう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1588
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b24c0736:

    # n "It's not that I need anything, but maybe there are summer sales, and I could pick up… something."
    n "別に必要なものがあるわけじゃないけど、サマーセールをやってるかもしれないし、なにか……買ってもいいだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1592
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_5e03b606:

    # n "{vspace=60}…Why am I trying to force myself?"
    n "\n\nどうして自分に無理強いしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1594
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_ae2b6e01:

    # n "Before, I was content with having nothing to do, save for kicking the ball every now and then at the field."
    n "昔は、やることがなくたって何も不満に思わなかった。時々運動場でボールを蹴るのは別として。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1596
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b4d7f7eb:

    # n "Now it seems that I can't settle down at all."
    n "今は、どうにも落ち着いていられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1598
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_dce4c6f8:

    # n "{vspace=30}Is it because I have changed, or because my world has changed?"
    n "俺が変わったからなのか、それとも俺のいる世界が変わったのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1601
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_11:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1607
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_2d1d7ef9:

    # "By eleven, the darkness bids me to sleep."
    "１１時になると、暗闇が俺を眠りへと誘う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1625
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_d76e4f6d:

    # "The medication bottles are innocuously arranged on my night table, not at all beckoning, rather pointedly reminding me of the reality instead."
    "ナイトテーブルの上に薬の容器が当たり障りなく並べられている。まったく魅力的でないし、むしろ露骨に現実を突きつけてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1627
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_b9c7e988:

    # "It's evening so I have to open three bottles, extract one large oval-shaped one, two small round ones and one large flat that has to be cut into half, close the bottles and chug down the medications with a chaser of fresh tap water."
    "夜だから３つの容器を開けて、大きな楕円形の薬と、２つの小さな丸い薬、それから自分で半分に割る大きくて平たい薬を容器から取り出し、容器を閉めて、新鮮な水道水で一気に飲みこまないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1641
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_adcc9949:

    # "The water tastes metallic on my tongue."
    "水は金属の味がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1643
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_675cc894:

    # "I swallow it along with the pills anyway and head to the bathroom."
    "それでも薬と一緒に飲み込んで、俺はシャワー室へ向かう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1648
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_3e442dfc:

    # "The mindless job of brushing my teeth is fit for trying to sort my thoughts."
    "歯磨きという頭を使わない作業は、考えを整理するのにちょうどいい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1650
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_98aa888b:

    # "One emerges from the mass, clearly rising above the others."
    "塊の中から一つの思考が現れ、はっきりと他の思考の上にそびえ立っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1652
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_12:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1655
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_fe43f2c2:

    # n "{vspace=270}I want to see Rin."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n琳に会いたい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1657
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_950439c0:

    # n "I can't let my outburst of anger be the last thing between us before the vacation."
    n "怒って琳を怒鳴りつけたのを、休みの前の俺たち２人の最後にはできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1660
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_13:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1667
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_4215315d:

    # n "{vspace=240}I have to see her, tomorrow."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n琳に会わないと。明日には。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1669
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_9f609591:

    # n "Sleep overcomes my confused mind with more ease than it should."
    n "混乱した心は眠りにあっけなく打ち倒される。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1672
translate jp a4_rin_wavelength_76b2fe88_14:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1692
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_8d8a2921:

    # "Rain is falling on my summer vacation like an uncountable number of small bad omens."
    "数え切れないくらいたくさんの悪い予兆のように、雨が俺の夏休みに降り注いでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1694
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d0255cc1:

    # "Luckily I'm not superstitious, but the bad weather makes me downcast too."
    "幸い、俺は迷信なんて信じない方だけど、この悪い天気じゃこっちの気も滅入る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1696
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_198a7d03:

    # "It's been like this since morning and there is no end in sight."
    "朝からずっとこの調子で、やみそうもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1698
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_86398206:

    # "An impenetrable gray mass of clouds shadows the sky as much as it shadows my mood."
    "分厚い灰色の雲の塊が、空と一緒に俺の気分にも影を落とす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1700
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_28e7b6ce:

    # "In a bout of defiance, I finished cleaning up this morning, but after that was done I ended up staring out of the window in hope of the weather clearing."
    "ふと思い立って、朝のうちに掃除を終えたけど、その後は窓から空を眺めて晴れるのを願うだけだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1702
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_39a3b2a9:

    # "The incessant drumming of rainfall against the roof and the pavement is mesmerizing, a droning background noise to lose your mind into."
    "ひっきりなしに雨が屋根や道路を叩く音に聞き入ってしまう。単調な雑音が気をおかしくさせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1704
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1706
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_604cb789:

    # "… …"
    "…………"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1713
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_96f490b9:

    # "This won't do, I have to get a move on."
    "こうしててもはじまらない。行かないと。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1715
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_efd0c57f:

    # "Should I pack now, or later?"
    "今すぐ荷造りするべきか、それとも後にするか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1722
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0707f71c:

    # "I decide on the latter and make my way outside, pausing briefly at Kenji's door to listen to the odd clunking sounds from the other side."
    "荷造りは後にして外に出る。健二の部屋の前で足を止めると、ドスンという奇妙な音が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1726
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_74a05ef3:

    # "I don't dare to knock, out of the fear of finding out what he is doing."
    "あいつが何をしているのか知るのが恐ろしいので、絶対にノックはしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1734
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_154c5f79:

    # "Braving the rain from under my trusty umbrella, I cross the space to the girls' dorm."
    "頼りの傘を差して雨中に繰り出すと、女子寮に向かって空き地を横切る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1743
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c939dd20:

    # "Knocking on Rin's door yields no answer, but the door behind me opens instead."
    "琳の部屋のドアをノックしても返事はない。代わりに後ろのドアが開く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1757
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_69ba2711:

    # emi "Hisao? Hi!"
    emi "久夫くん？　こんちわ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1762
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_8fe0d634:

    # emi "Terrible weather. I even missed my morning jog."
    emi "ひどい天気だね。朝のジョギングも走れなかったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1764
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bec77409:

    # "She frowns, but I would be glad if I was her. Emi's morning jogs are anything but leisurely."
    "笑美は眉をひそめるけど、俺だったら喜びそうなものだ。笑美の朝のジョギングは気楽なものとはほど遠いからな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1766
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_46e17644:

    # hi "Oh, hi, I was—"
    hi "ああ、よお。俺――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1771
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6c727612:

    # emi "If you're looking for Rin, I don't think she is there."
    emi "もし琳を探してるなら、そこにはいないと思うよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1773
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6c0eb2c4:

    # hi "Have you seen her recently?"
    hi "最近あいつに会ったか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1778
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7028b2c1:

    # emi "Yeah, just this morning when I woke her up."
    emi "うん、ちょうど今朝起こしにいったときにね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1780
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_db78729a:

    # "The mention of waking up makes Emi yawn like a cat, and makes me feel silly."
    "起こしたことを話に出した笑美は猫のようにあくびして、俺はばかみたいな気分になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1782
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_45509f61:

    # "Of course she has seen Rin. Emi wakes her up and helps her get dressed on most mornings, even makes her lunch boxes every now and then."
    "そりゃ笑美は琳に会ってるに決まってる。いつも琳を起こして、着替えを手伝っているんだから。弁当を作ってやることだってある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1784
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_cb6e2bc7:

    # "They are like sisters, even though they seem to have nothing in common."
    "共通点なんてなさそうなのに、姉妹みたいだな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1787
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_78b4f0b5:

    # "I wonder which one is the elder sister? Probably Emi, against all odds."
    "どっちが姉だろう？　きっと笑美だな。全然そんな感じじゃないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1789
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7da774f5:

    # "She is really diligent, even though she gives the feeling of someone who would be a total airhead."
    "周りには間抜けだと思われてそうな雰囲気があるけど、笑美はほんとうに熱心だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1791
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2f5a5bea:

    # "Why does it feel odd that she is so dutiful under that cheery grin of hers?"
    "この明るい笑顔の裏で、こんなにもまっすぐであることが奇妙に思えるのはどうしてだろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1796
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d064ef9b:

    # emi "She left for the gallery a few hours ago… hey, are you listening?"
    emi "それで、何時間か前にギャラリーにいったよ……ちょっと、聞いてる？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1798
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_64dbce1d:

    # "Maybe I'm making a funny face or something, since Emi tilts her face quizzically, looking at me with her eyes round and inquisitive."
    "きっと俺は妙な顔でもしてるんだろう。笑美は不思議そうに顔を傾け、興味津々のまん丸い目つきで俺を見ている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1803
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_19972527:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "ねーえ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1805
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_e13a2526:

    # "Her innocent face seems to request my attention."
    "そのあどけない表情は俺の注意を引こうとしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1807
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_58c0300f:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm listening…"
    hi "ああ、聞いてるよ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1812
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4f68b1dd:

    # emi "Can I ask you a question?"
    emi "ひとつ聞いてもいい？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1814
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2541be0f:

    # hi "Yeah, of course."
    hi "もちろん"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1819
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0ce6898f:

    # "She furrows her brow, licking her lips as if to prepare for something."
    "笑美は眉間にしわを寄せると、なにかに備えるかのようにくちびるを舐める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1824
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_9474eb39:

    # emi "Why do you care so much about Rin?"
    emi "どうして琳のこと、そんなにかまうの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1829
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c748bc35:

    # emi "I mean, you probably hang around her more than I do, and we even slept in the same bed sometimes until, er, lately."
    emi "ていうか、久夫くんはあたしよりもずっと琳と一緒にいると思うんだ。琳とは一緒のベッドで寝たりもしてたんだよ、その、最近までは、ね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1831
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1d3b01d3:

    # hi "After she banned you because you ravaged her hair?"
    hi "あいつの髪をくしゃくしゃにして出入り禁止になったからだろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1836
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3cea227a:

    # "A shock of horror widens Emi's eyes at least twofold, making them seem even more saucer-like than usual, while a healthy blush rises on her cheeks and ears."
    "恐怖のショックで笑美の目が２倍は大きくなり、いつも以上にお皿のような形に広がる。同時に頬と耳はかなり真っ赤になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1841
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4814b0e8:

    # emi "She told?! Ohhh… I'm going to strangle that Rin or something other horrible…"
    emi "琳、話したの！？　うわあ……琳のやつ首絞めてやる、さもなきゃもっとひどい目に……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1843
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c0bbe1c9:

    # "I hold back my laughter, lest she direct her disdain at me."
    "笑美の軽蔑が俺に向かないように笑いをこらえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1848
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2f42f19e:

    # "Emi recuperates quickly from the embarrassment and seems to forgive Rin in the same instant, getting her focus back on me."
    "笑美はすぐに屈辱から立ち直り、同時に琳のことも許したみたいで、俺に視線を戻す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1853
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2d8d6cf8:

    # emi "Anyway, are you in love with her or something?"
    emi "とにかく、久夫くんは琳に惚れちゃったりしてるわけ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1855
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d887d4a8:

    # "Uh oh. This really feels like an elder sister questioning a suitor. Emi is kinda nosy, and not in a good happy way, if there even is one to begin with."
    "おっと。マジで求婚相手の姉に問い詰められてるような気がするぞ。笑美はなんだかおせっかい気味だ。あまりいい意味ではなく。そもそもいい意味でのおせっかいなんてありうるのかどうか怪しいけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1857
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_cc0d7719:

    # "She'd make a good partner for Misha, to be honest. The horror."
    "正直に言うと、ミーシャとなら似合いのパートナーになれるだろうな。恐ろしすぎる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1859
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6ce201a3:

    # hi "That's already your second question, so I don't think I have to answer."
    hi "もう２つ目の質問じゃないか、答えてやる必要はないね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1861
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1e558655:

    # "I try to conjure up a front made of pure, crystallized cool and uninvolvement."
    "俺は素早く、純粋なクールさと無関心さで固めた表情を作ろうとする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1863
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_16e3c11f:

    # "I wonder whether I manage to fool even myself."
    "俺自身の気持ちをごまかせているかどうかも怪しい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1868
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f8ba3511:

    # "At least Emi is waggling her eyebrows dangerously, with a nasty smirk on her lips."
    "少なくとも、笑美は眉毛を危なっかしく揺すっていて、口元は嫌味な作り笑いを浮かべている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1870
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5e48eea3:

    # emi "Is that a yes?"
    emi "それはイエスってこと？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1872
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d5dfe2a6:

    # hi "No, it's not a yes."
    hi "いいや、イエスじゃない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1877
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_9a9d7040:

    # "Obviously unsatisfied at my refusal to answer her way-too-intimate question, she has enough sense to back off."
    "立ち入りすぎたその質問に答えなかったことには明らかに不満なようだけど、諦めるだけの分別はあるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1882
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_37c97d73:

    # "Doesn't stop her from sticking out her tongue at me like a kid, and giggling again."
    "それでも子供のように俺に舌を突き出して、またクスクスと笑う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1887
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1c1021da:

    # emi "If that's your answer, I don't think I have to talk with you any more."
    emi "それが君の答えなら、これ以上話すことはないかな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1889
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c3144138:

    # "It's easy to see that she's not really angry."
    "別に怒ってるわけじゃないことはすぐわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1894
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a32de8d5:

    # emi "Besides, I have to go pack now. Mom will be worried if I miss my bus."
    emi "それに荷造りしないといけないしね。バスに乗り遅れたらママが心配しちゃう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1896
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_23b8a84f:

    # emi "Seeya!"
    emi "じゃあね！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1898
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4f28c382:

    # hi "Yeah, bye."
    hi "ああ、またな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1907
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3fe99f78:

    # "She retreats back into her room, leaving me alone in the hallway."
    "笑美が部屋に引き下がると、俺は廊下でひとりきりになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1909
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_044d7110:

    # "What's between me and Rin is not her business, right?"
    "俺と琳の間のことは笑美には関係ない、だろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1911
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7d0711e0:

    # "That's why I ended up not saying anything about our fight to Emi. Rin must have not said anything either."
    "だから俺はけんかのことも笑美には話さずじまいだった。琳も何も教えていないに違いない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1913
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_23e440a1:

    # "I guess… even though they are friends, there are things they don't talk about."
    "たぶん……友達同士であっても、話さないことはあるんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1915
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1917
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5f51b53c:

    # "So, if Rin is at the gallery, I'd have to go all the way there."
    "さて、琳がギャラリーにいるなら、俺もあっちまで足を延ばさないとな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1919
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5796dd87:

    # "Now that I managed to get out of my room, I suppose it's not that much of a bother to go downtown."
    "やっと部屋から出られたんだから、街まで出るのも大したことはないだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1921
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_35d8f7e3:

    # "I could go get a ticket, but the train back home will have to wait, at least until tomorrow."
    "切符を買いに行くこともできたけど、家に帰るのは後回しだ。少なくとも明日までは。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1923
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d5cfa695:

    # "No way I'm going to carry baggage to the train station in this rain, even if there's not that much of it."
    "この雨の中、荷物を抱えて駅までいくのはごめんだ。荷物っていったってそう多いわけじゃないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1931
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6e23fb6d:

    # "Rain makes all outlines seem very unstable, as if they were fading away."
    "雨はあらゆる輪郭をとても不明瞭にする。だんだんと消え去っていくかのように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1933
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6d9c9471:

    # "The townscape turns into a shapeless collection of various fuzzy tones of gray, instead of distinct forms of buildings and cars."
    "街の景色が、はっきりとした建物や車の形から、濃淡のはっきりしない灰色の、形を持たない集まりに変わっていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1935
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4cdb6f6a:

    # "Those poor souls who are forced into the downpour try to make as much haste as they possibly can, pitying each other for their shared misery."
    "土砂降りの中を歩く羽目になったかわいそうな人たちは、できるだけ急いで移動して、お互いの不運を哀れみあっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1941
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5e73aadb:

    # "I turn the final corner, the twenty-second corner so to say, and immediately feel stupid for being amused by my own pun."
    "最後の曲がり角、いわば２２番目の角を曲がる。こんな駄洒落に喜んでいるなんて馬鹿みたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1943
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1e586a06:

    # "The door beckons me with promises of warmth."
    "ドアは俺を暖かく招き入れてくれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1952
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b1ffb743:

    # "The rainwater dripping from my umbrella makes interesting, almost artistic patterns on the floor."
    "雨水が傘からしたたって、興味深い、なかば芸術的な模様を床に作っていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1954
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1a859d51:

    # "I am not wet, apart from my shoes that leave small puddles in my wake, completing the rainwater-artwork."
    "靴が俺の足跡に小さな水たまりを作って、雨水アートを仕上げているのを除けば、俺自身は濡れていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1960
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_976fb099:

    # "Nomiya is here too, chatting with Sae at the back of the gallery. Rin's nowhere to be seen, though."
    "野宮先生もいて、さえさんとギャラリーの奥で雑談している。でも琳の姿はどこにも見えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1962
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_e769e9e0:

    # "Maybe she's upstairs."
    "上にいるのかもな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1964
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_39a5be74:

    # "There are no customers though, which figures, considering the bucketloads of water dropping on the neck of anyone daring to brave the weather today."
    "来客は一人もいない。それもそうだろう、首にバケツをひっくり返したような雨をかぶってまで、この天気の中をわざわざやってくる人なんていやしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1969
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_477455a9:

    # sa "Welcome."
    sa "いらっしゃい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1971
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_dbbe0fc0:

    # hi "Hello. Sorry to interrupt…"
    hi "どうも。邪魔してすみません……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1976
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c387670f:

    # no "Ah, good afternoon Nakai."
    no "ああ、中井じゃないか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1981
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a80d47c7:

    # no "Came all the way here for a visit?"
    no "わざわざここまで会いに来たのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1983
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f5c395b7:

    # hi "Ah… no, I think it was just an impulse. I was around the neighborhood, shopping, and decided to stop by."
    hi "ええと……いえ、ただ思い立っただけです。このあたりをぶらついて買い物してて、それで立ち寄ろうと思って"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1985
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_df253efd:

    # "My reflexive reaction is a white lie, which surprises myself."
    "他愛のない嘘が反射的に出て、俺は自分に驚く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1987
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_99490866:

    # "Maybe I just don't want to say that I came specifically to see Rin, even though that much must be obvious."
    "琳に会いに来た、とはっきりとは言いたくないのかもしれない。どう見てもそうなのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1992
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_58fbae9f:

    # sa "My, you chose a bad day for shopping. Would you like some tea to warm you up?"
    sa "まあ、ずいぶんな日に買い物するのね。寒いでしょう、お茶でもいかが？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1994
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5aaebf04:

    # hi "Thank you but I'm fine, really."
    hi "ありがとうございます、でも平気です"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:1996
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_e62c76ae:

    # hi "The weather could be better though. Rain on the first day of vacations is a bit depressing."
    hi "でも確かに天気は良くないですね。夏休みの初日に雨っていうのはなんだか気が滅入ります"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2002
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f366b0d0:

    # no "Hahaha! Well, I'm sure it'll get better."
    no "はっはっは！　天気なんてそのうち良くなるさ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2004
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f924db9d:

    # "Nomiya offers his hearty laughter, bordering on abrasive."
    "野宮先生は元気よく笑い声をあげる。耳障りといったほうが近い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2006
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f53e863a:

    # hi "Rain doesn't get you down, teacher?"
    hi "先生は雨には落ち込まないんですね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2011
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_78963b55:

    # no "Well, I do prefer clear weather as well. I was actually leaving just now to meet someone, and I'd prefer not getting my jacket soaked. It's very expensive."
    no "まあ、晴れた天気も好きだがね。今から人に会うためにここを出るところだったのだが、ジャケットを濡らしたくなかったのでな。これはとても高いんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2016
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a20af79a:

    # no "But of course I'm in a good mood!"
    no "だがもちろん、気分はいいぞ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2021
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_60db5139:

    # no "What did you think about the exhibition? It was wonderful, wasn't it?"
    no "展覧会はどうだったかね？　すばらしかっただろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2023
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d62d902f:

    # hi "Yeah, it was very fancy."
    hi "ええ、とても凝ってましたね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2025
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b9fa781d:

    # "My unenthusiastic answer only spurs him to carry on, walking around the gallery while blabbering about the opening."
    "俺の適当な返事は先生をおだてるだけだ。ギャラリーの中を歩き回りながら、展覧会のオープニングについてしゃべくっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2027
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bc0f5784:

    # "He talks more and louder when he is moving. It's something I noticed at the club meetings too."
    "先生は動いているときのほうがよく話すし、声も大きい。部活の時もそうだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2032
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_9a424440:

    # no "We got to talk with many good people and make valuable contacts."
    no "もっとたくさんの良い人々と話をして、有益な付き合いを築いていかないとな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2037
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_53acf0d3:

    # no "One of Tezuka's paintings even got sold, to a collector from Osaka."
    no "なんと手塚の絵が１枚、大阪から来たコレクターに売れたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2044
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_39df7101:

    # "I follow his eyes to an empty space in the wall. I can't even remember which painting was hanging on that spot."
    "壁の空いたスペースまで先生の視線を追っていく。あそこにどんな絵がかかっていたのか思い出すこともできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2046
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a3764746:

    # "Well, it's gone now."
    "とにかく、今はもうなくなってしまった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2054
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_46494bcb:

    # no "It was lucky that she was all right despite that dizzy spell."
    no "手塚があのめまいの発作から回復したのは幸運だったな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2059
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a500c4ec:

    # no "She got a little quiet though, so I told her to rest well. Then again she's always been pretty shy."
    no "あの後、ちょっと口数が少なくなったので、よく休むように言っておいた。とはいえ、手塚は日ごろからかなり内気だったからな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2061
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_356770ba:

    # "Shy? Whatever, I just nod along with the teacher."
    "内気だって？　とにかく、俺はただ先生の話に合わせてうなずく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2066
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_e5ef1dfc:

    # no "The reception was very positive in general. I might be able to get one of my friends to write a little article on a magazine to—"
    no "反応はおおむね大好評だった。友人に頼んで、雑誌に小さな記事を書いてもらえるかもしれん――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2068
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_701959b0:

    # sa "Shinichi, your meeting. You're making Mr. Takahashi wait."
    sa "紳一、打ち合わせでしょう。高橋さんを待たせてるわ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2073
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0cbb9e1a:

    # "Sae's remark makes him stop in his tracks and check his watch."
    "さえさんの一言に先生は言葉を切り、腕時計を確認する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2075
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_71e02f13:

    # "Nomiya frowns in displeasure at the interruption to his tirade."
    "先生は演説を中断させられたことへの不満に顔をしかめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2080
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3515c2d3:

    # no "Oh, right. Yes, well, I'll be off then. We'll meet in September, Nakai."
    no "ああ、そうか。よし、では行くとするか。また９月に会おう、中井"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2082
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_361fdc97:

    # hi "Bye."
    hi "はい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2090
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_68b1a74e:

    # "Wow. Teacher really doesn't hold back when it comes to Rin's budding artist career."
    "やれやれ。始まったばかりの琳の芸術家稼業のことになると、先生は抑えがきかないな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2092
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7b2cdcc7:

    # "I guess it takes a lot to succeed, but I suppose his job would be easier if Rin was more cooperative."
    "成功するまでは長い道のりになるんだろうけど、琳がもっと協力的だったら、先生もここまで苦労しないだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2097
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2100
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b2628fcf:

    # n "{vspace=30}She's too indecisive even though she's doing just fine. Like that 'dizzy spell' from the night before."
    n "\n琳はうまくやっているときでさえ、優柔不断すぎる。あのときの『めまいの発作』みたいに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2102
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_9f131eba:

    # n "She just got freaked out or something, and I didn't do anything to help her."
    n "パニックか何かに陥ってしまったのに、俺はなにも手助けをしなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2104
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_aaa316ef:

    # n "{vspace=30}I sigh."
    n "俺はため息をつく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2106
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_cbf6d502:

    # n "It feels like the gap between me and Rin is only widening."
    n "これじゃ俺と琳の間の溝は広がっていくばかりだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2108
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_05ebc2df:

    # n "She's going to become something great while I'm still feeling like I'm bogged down, despite promising myself to try and make something of my life."
    n "琳はすごいやつになろうとしてるのに、俺は相変わらず泥沼にはまっているような気分だ。自分も何かを成し遂げるために努力するんだと心に決めたのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2110
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_899baf52:

    # n "On top of that, we had that fight and the longer we keep not talking, the harder the wounds become to heal."
    n "それに加えてけんかまでしてしまった。話をしない期間が長引くほど、仲直りするのも難しくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2112
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1c9d389d:

    # n "If that even is what we want. I never found out what Rin felt, and now I'm not sure what I feel myself."
    n "俺たちがそう望んだとしてもだ。俺は琳の思いが一度もわからなかった。今では自分の思いもよくわからなくなっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2114
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_038d7c50:

    # n "I wish I could understand her. But Rin is not very open for interpretation."
    n "琳のことを理解できたらいいのにと思う。でも琳は解釈できるようなそぶりをあまり見せない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2116
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_456caa70:

    # n "Not that she's hiding anything, she just seems to defy my attempts at making sense of what she is talking about on any given day."
    n "なにかを隠しているわけじゃない。ただどの日であろうと、琳の話を理解しようとする俺の試みを受け付けないように見えるだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2122
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2127
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_ef9162e6:

    # sa "Something on your mind?"
    sa "どうかしたの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2129
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_19a1ba7c:

    # "I realize I've been spacing out in the middle of the gallery for who knows how long."
    "俺はギャラリーの真ん中で、長い時間ぼんやりしていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2131
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_fe9dc336:

    # hi "Ahh… nothing special…"
    hi "あー……いえ、別に……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2133
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4b81de86:

    # "I pretend to study the closest paintings to distract her."
    "俺は近くの絵を見るふりをして、さえさんの気をそらす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2143
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6bbf3831:

    # "I've seen it before."
    "前にも見たな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2145
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_659d36c8:

    # "The now all-too-familiar strokes of color, twisting and melting into each other seemingly randomly still manage to feel like there is something happening behind the scenes, so to speak."
    "今となっては見慣れた色遣いだ。色がお互いにねじれ、溶け合って、一見すると不規則だけど、言ってみれば景色の裏でなにかが起きているような印象を与える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2147
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6dd8e5bc:

    # "Rin's style is so much like her. Abstract, incomprehensible, colorful."
    "琳のスタイルはほんとうに琳らしい。抽象的で、理解不能で、色鮮やかだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2149
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_82eaf5c1:

    # "Mysterious."
    "不思議だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2151
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5b5ddb02:

    # "I wonder if to understand an artist, one must understand art?"
    "芸術家というものを理解するには、芸術を理解しなくちゃいけないんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2158
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_57d5369c:

    # hi "Umm… I may have a question."
    hi "うーん……聞きたいことがあるんです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2163
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_cacde930:

    # sa "Oh?"
    sa "なにかしら？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2165
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6abbb1d0:

    # "She looks up from the magazine she was idly leafing through, seeming delighted at my display of unspecified interest."
    "さえさんはぼんやりとめくっていた雑誌から顔を上げる。俺がふと興味を示したことに嬉しそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2167
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_16f66972:

    # hi "How do you interpret art?"
    hi "さえさんはどうやって作品を解釈しているんですか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2172
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c5a8be80:

    # sa "What do you mean?"
    sa "どういうことかしら？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2174
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b0c698ee:

    # "Her eyebrows rise high into questioning arcs, as if the question was too complicated to even begin to answer without clarification."
    "その質問が説明なしでは答えることもできないくらい分かりにくいものだったかのように、さえさんの眉は高く上がり、尋ねるような孤を描く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2176
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b4f07c87:

    # hi "Sorry if I'm asking something stupid."
    hi "バカな質問だったらすみません"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2178
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6547df5c:

    # hi "I don't think I really understand art like the pros do."
    hi "俺はプロのようには芸術を理解できてないと思うんです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2183
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_e0ce30d7:

    # sa "Oh, there's no trick to it."
    sa "あら、何も難しいことなんてないのよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2185
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_af1350ce:

    # "Sae waves my question away with a simple but efficient flick of her wrist."
    "さえさんは俺の質問をシンプルだけど、わかりやすい手首の動きで払いのける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2190
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5ce0787f:

    # sa "Everyone interprets art as they will, and interpretation is as much in the eye of the beholder as in the intentions of the creator."
    sa "みんな好きなように読み取ってるのよ。解釈というのは作り手の意図次第であるのと同じくらいに、それを見る者次第でもある"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2192
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5875ce85:

    # sa "'Pros' have their own way, because there is this thing called art theory."
    sa "『プロ』はみんな自分なりの見方を持ってる。なぜかというと、美学というものがあってね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2194
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_453cf356:

    # sa "There are patterns in art, just like in everything, and we assume that it's possible to draw some conclusions from observing those patterns."
    sa "芸術にはパターンがある。なんでもそうね。私たちはそのパターンを観察して何らかの結論を導くことができる、と仮定しているの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2196
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6d031a38:

    # "Her voice is like a teacher's, lecturing and adding emphasis on random words to keep the listeners on their toes."
    "さえさんの声はまるで先生みたいで、聞き手の注意を保つために無作為に言葉を強調しながら講義をしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2201
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a6c2cfdd:

    # sa "In the end, I suppose it's pretty meaningless."
    sa "結局は、ものすごく意味のないことなんでしょうね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2203
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_acf4c476:

    # "She moves to musing seemingly to herself, muttering loud enough for me to clearly hear."
    "今度は物思いに沈みながら独り言をつぶやくけど、それは俺にも十分聞こえるほど大きい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2205
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_31fa8ff4:

    # sa "A good piece of art will make you feel something and that's all there is to it."
    sa "優れた芸術作品は、人に何かを感じさせる。ただそれだけのことね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2207
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7d678c9f:

    # sa "Feelings change and they affect the art we create and the art we see."
    sa "気持ちが変われば、作り上げる芸術にも、目にする芸術にも影響を与えるわ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2209
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b91d705c:

    # hi "But…"
    hi "でも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2214
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_aff67f9e:

    # sa "I'll tell you a story."
    sa "こんな話があるの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2216
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_36500938:

    # hi "Do you have to? The last one was depressing…"
    hi "またですか？　この前のには参りましたよ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2218
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2c333e8c:

    # sa "It's important. Listen…"
    sa "大事なことよ、聞きなさい……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2220
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_67359d64:

    # sa "About a hundred years ago a little known painter got news that his friend, a man called Casagemas, had committed suicide."
    sa "１００年ほど前、ほぼ無名の芸術家が、その友人のカサヘマスが自殺したという知らせを受けた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2222
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5414ed21:

    # sa "This happened while he was away and hadn't seen his friend for a while."
    sa "それは彼がその友人と離れていて、しばらく会っていないというときに起きた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2224
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_770733bf:

    # sa "So obviously he must have felt even more conflicted than you normally would after hearing of such a thing."
    sa "当然、そんな知らせを受けたら、普通よりもさらに大きな葛藤を感じたはずよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2226
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a15d1905:

    # sa "For four years after that, our main character did nothing but monochromatic paintings because he was so deeply affected by the news."
    sa "それから４年間、その知らせにあまりに影響を受けすぎて、この芸術家は単彩の絵を描くこと以外には何もしなかった"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2228
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_ecef6122:

    # sa "Whatever he did, he always kept returning to that same color until it let him out of its grasp."
    sa "何をするにしても、彼は必ずその同じ色に戻ってきた。その呪縛から抜け出すまでね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2230
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a4a66667:

    # "She takes a little pause to check whether I'm still following."
    "さえさんはしばらく言葉を切って、俺が話についてきているか確認する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2232
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_69bf7d08:

    # "I am, to an extent, so I give her the prompt that storytellers seem to live for."
    "ちゃんとついていってる。ある程度は。俺は語り手が生きがいにしているような、お定まりの相づちを打つ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2234
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_c85221a4:

    # hi "So…"
    hi "それで……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2236
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d0a57d48:

    # "It's hard to continue from that, as I can't seem to come up with the question she wants me to come up with."
    "さえさんが期待しているような質問が思い浮かばず、そこから言葉が続かない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2238
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a646deae:

    # "Like a half-baked Socrates, she thought she laid out all the tools for revelation in front of me."
    "半人前のソクラテスのように、さえさんは俺の目の前に啓発のための材料をすべて並べきったと思っていたようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2243
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3f4eff04:

    # sa "Don't you see the point yet?"
    sa "まだわからないの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2245
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_7da429ed:

    # "Only, her student proved to be too dense to get it."
    "ただ、この聴講生はそれを理解するには鈍すぎたということだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2250
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_92ae8521:

    # "She looks discontent at my slowness."
    "さえさんは俺の鈍感さに不満そうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2252
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_db9e06d8:

    # sa "Picasso's Blue Period is one of the most lauded in the history of art, but who knows what he felt when he worked on those masterpieces?"
    sa "ピカソの青の時代は美術史のなかでもっとも賞賛されたもののひとつよ。でもあの名作の数々を描いていたとき、彼が何を思っていたかなんて誰がわかるかしら？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2254
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b3ef9f66:

    # sa "Sadness? Longing? Regret?"
    sa "悲しみ？　慕情？　後悔？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2256
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_51a79c7c:

    # sa "Nobody can tell."
    sa "誰にもわからないわ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2258
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_74a940f2:

    # sa "If you now see one of his Blue Period paintings, you'd probably interpret it differently from before you knew about Picasso's friend Casagemas."
    sa "もし今、あなたが青の時代の作品を見れば、ピカソの友人カサヘマスのことを知る前とはまた違った解釈をするでしょう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2263
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3dcfcfb4:

    # sa "Experiencing art is always personal, only interactive by chance or circumstances."
    sa "芸術に触れるというのはいつでも個人的な経験であって、偶然や状況によってしか相互性は生まれないの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2265
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f4cd323a:

    # sa "There are a million explanations for any given piece of art, but it might be that none of them are what the creator intended."
    sa "どんな芸術作品にも無数の説明が存在しうるけど、そのどれも作者の意図するところじゃない、ということもあり得るかもしれない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2270
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_2921a328:

    # sa "No man is an island, you know?"
    sa "人は孤島ではない、はずなのにね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2272
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0eba98cb:

    # "I nod without understanding what that last remark meant."
    "俺は最後の言葉がなにを意味するのかわからないままうなずく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2274
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3baa71c1:

    # "What she said made sense otherwise, except for one thing."
    "さえさんのいったことは意味が通ってる。ひとつを除けば。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2276
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_aaf874d1:

    # "If art is communication like Rin said, but everyone is talking their own secret language like Sae said, what can anyone ever hope to communicate?"
    "もし芸術が琳の言ったようにコミュニケーションで、しかしさえさんの言ったように誰もが自分だけの秘密の言語を使っているのなら、人が意思を通じ合うことなんて望みようもないじゃないか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2278
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_319d0dbd:

    # "It seems so futile, and pointless."
    "あまりに無意味で、無駄に思える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2280
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_950ebfcb:

    # "Art really is not a thing for me."
    "芸術はやっぱり俺の分野じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2287
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_71ac2452:

    # "Sae returns to her art magazine, and I make a round in the gallery, trying to see what Rin can see in her own paintings."
    "さえさんはまた芸術雑誌を読み始める。俺はギャラリーを一周して、琳が自分の絵から何を見ているのか確かめようとする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2289
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_62b50f3a:

    # "A soothing mood takes hold of the gallery surrounded by the rainstorm, the big windows making the transparent isolation feel more comfortable."
    "大雨に取り巻かれたギャラリーは落ち着いた雰囲気で満たされる。大きな窓のおかげで、あからさまな孤独も多少は快適なものになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2294
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_1a3f4747:

    # "A tinkle of the bell disrupts the tranquil mood."
    "ベルの音が穏やかな雰囲気を破る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2304
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_da04f110:

    # "Rin pushes the door open with her shoulder and steps in."
    "琳が肩でドアを押し開け、入ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2306
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_addf6b79:

    # "I had almost forgotten that she was the reason why I came to the gallery in the first place."
    "そもそも琳に会うためにここに来たのをすっかり忘れていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2311
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_56f08f96:

    # rin "I think I'm ready—{w=0.3}{nw}"
    rin "用意できたと思いま――{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2316
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_476b888f:

    # "She pauses mid-sentence, noticing my presence."
    "俺がいることに気づくと、言葉の途中で固まってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2318
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a43a6b46:

    # "The needle-dropping silence lasts for exactly one and a half seconds, not enough for either me or Sae to open our mouths, but enough for Rin to react."
    "針の落ちる音さえ聞こえそうな沈黙はきっかり１.５秒続く。俺もさえさんも口を開くには短すぎたけど、琳が反応するには十分だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2323
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f2fc5ea0:

    # rin "I'm going for a walk."
    rin "散歩してくる"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2330
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_fbb3c86c:

    # "Heading back outside with a reckless pace uncharacteristic of herself, Rin seems to forget that it's still raining."
    "琳らしくない、向こう見ずな勢いで外に戻ってしまう。雨が降っていることも忘れているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2332
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_b53d4867:

    # "Without giving it any real thought, I grab my umbrella and hurry after her."
    "あまり考えることなく、俺は傘をつかむと急いで琳を追う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2342
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bfa7b72c:

    # "I catch Rin around the corner, open the umbrella and lift it above the two of us while still having to almost run to keep up with her."
    "角を曲がったところで琳に追いつき、傘を開いて俺たち２人の上に差す。その間もほとんど走っていないとついていけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2344
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0ea51acf:

    # "She doesn't protest me running after her nor me giving her shelter against the rain, eventually slowing her pace down so I can match it without an immediate danger of overexerting myself."
    "琳は俺が走ってついてきたことにも、傘を差してやっていることにも文句を言わず、やがて足取りも遅らせたので、俺も体を酷使しすぎるという差し迫った危険なしに追いつけるようになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2346
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_27ae3507:

    # "I relax from the rush, assessing the situation."
    "全力疾走から落ち着くと、状況を吟味する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2348
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bfa998d9:

    # "The last time I held my umbrella to guard both of us against the rain, I didn't think too much about it."
    "この前に、俺たち２人が雨に濡れないよう傘を差したときは、そのことをあまり深く考えはしなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2350
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_d01cb9bb:

    # "But now, all the things that happened since then are gathering into a freezing cold ball around my stomach."
    "でも今は、その時以来のあらゆる出来事が凍るように冷たい球になって、胃の周囲に集まっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2352
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_6a4cad7e:

    # "Being close to her makes me uncomfortable, and I feel myself flustering slightly."
    "琳の近くにいるのは居心地が悪くて、自分がわずかに動揺しているのを感じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2354
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_0252e53d:

    # "It's hard to get words out of my mouth, as it feels suddenly very, very dry."
    "突然、ものすごくのどが渇いた感じがして、言葉を発するのもままならなくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2356
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_66523d72:

    # "Still, it's not like I can back off."
    "それでも、後に引けるものじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2358
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bf29b048:

    # hi "Why do you keep running away?"
    hi "なんでそうやって逃げ続けるんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2363
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_27f8c077:

    # rin "I don't want to talk to you."
    rin "君とは話したくない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2365
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_3456971d:

    # hi "I want to talk to you."
    hi "俺は話したい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2370
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_4210074f:

    # rin "It hurts every time I do."
    rin "話をするたびにつらいんだ、いつも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2372
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_bc37a1a0:

    # hi "Sometimes it can't be helped."
    hi "時には仕方ないこともあるさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2377
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a992f22b:

    # rin "I don't want to hurt."
    rin "つらいのはいやだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2379
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_434553cb:

    # hi "Fine. We don't have to talk."
    hi "わかった。話すのはよそう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2384
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f9ed2b9a:

    # rin "What should we do?"
    rin "じゃあどうするの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2386
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_f01e297a:

    # hi "Let's just keep walking."
    hi "いいから歩こうぜ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2391
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_5f7e9809:

    # rin "Just walking?"
    rin "歩くだけ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2393
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_beb587ba:

    # hi "Just walking."
    hi "歩くだけだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2398
translate jp a4_rin_blue_period_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "わかったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2419
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_332df450:

    # "Our footsteps go 'splish splash' in the shallow puddles forming on the streets as we walk through the rainfall."
    "雨のなかを歩いていると、俺たちは通りにできた浅い水たまりを踏んでバシャバシャという足音を立てる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2421
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5e37c119:

    # "Rin, now walking beside me in her unhurried and relaxed manner, doesn't seem to be even a bit bothered by the fact that she is getting wet even though she needn't to."
    "琳はのんびりと、落ち着いた態度で俺の隣を歩いていて、不必要に濡れてしまっていることもまるで気にしていないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2423
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_55c8f7c2:

    # "She is partially out of the protective shelter of my umbrella, despite it being more than big enough for the two of us."
    "俺たち２人を覆うには十分な大きさなのに、琳は傘の下から少しはみ出している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2425
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4d73d9e1:

    # "It's as if she doesn't even notice the rain drenching her shirt."
    "袖がびしょ濡れになっているのに気づいてさえいないかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2427
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2429
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_292de573:

    # "Rin's demeanor always evokes mental images of meditative calm, even when she might be in inner turmoil."
    "心の中では動揺しているようなときでさえ、琳の立ち振る舞いはいつも瞑想的な落ち着きのイメージを連想させる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2431
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_96895670:

    # "But I don't think that is meditation. That is just getting soaked in rain."
    "でも今のこれは瞑想ではない気がする。単に雨に濡れているだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2433
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fdb5b079:

    # "I wish I could be more calm too."
    "俺ももっと冷静でいられたらいいのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2435
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b646bc5e:

    # "I've become too involved with Rin to retain my usual aloofness."
    "いつもの超然とした態度を保つには、俺はもう琳と深く関わりすぎてしまった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2437
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_67633efc:

    # "It feels like I have become one of those people who fool themselves into thinking they are objective, only to find out they are the worst kind of liars."
    "自分は客観的に物事を見ていると自分自身をごまかしておいて、結局自分が最悪の嘘つきだったと気づいてしまうようなタイプの人間になってしまった気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2439
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ae981667:

    # "Illusions to fool ourselves, what better way to make one feel like a good person?"
    "俺たち自身をごまかすための妄想か。自分がいい人間だと思い込むのにこれ以上いい方法なんてあるだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2441
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_62fa6d03:

    # "It might be better to lose that illusion."
    "そんな妄想はなくしたほうがいいかもな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2448
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_81068593:

    # hi "I'll be going back home for some time so I thought I'd come to see you before that."
    hi "しばらく実家に戻るんだけど、その前に会っておきたいと思ってさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2450
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5567e945:

    # "I could have thought of a better conversation opener, but Rin actively refusing to talk makes it hard."
    "もっといい話の切り出し方もあったんだろうけど、琳がはっきりと話をするのを拒んでいるのが、それを難しくする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2452
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2a52ae42:

    # rin "That's good. I might have thought that you'd have been kidnapped otherwise."
    rin "よかったよ。でなきゃ君が誘拐されたと思ったかもしれないから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2454
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_af1b1a87:

    # hi "You can't keep running away from everything. Not even from me trying to talk seriously."
    hi "そうやってずっと逃げていられると思ってるのか。俺が真面目に話そうとしてるのに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2456
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_033e6652:

    # rin "I'm always serious. Also I seem to be running very slowly right now."
    rin "私はいつも真面目だよ。それに今の私、すごくゆっくり走ってるみたい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2458
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_87c81773:

    # rin "Maybe I should take lessons from Emi."
    rin "笑美に走り方を教わったほうがいいかも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2460
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b88e0e80:

    # "It's futile. Like talking to a brick wall that randomly spouts sarcastic nonsense back at you."
    "無意味だ。やみくもに皮肉っぽくて意味をなさない言葉を垂れ流す、レンガの壁と話しているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2462
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6b4862b4:

    # hi "Think of your exhibition opening. What if you had run away?"
    hi "あの展覧会のオープニングのこと、考えてもみろよ。もしあのまま逃げちまってたらどうなったと思う？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2464
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_75f5f242:

    # "Rin doesn't answer to that, she just keeps walking. Or running slowly, escaping from me into her silence."
    "琳はそれには答えず、ただ歩き続ける。あるいはゆっくり走っている。俺の質問から沈黙のなかへ逃げ去ってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2466
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_635773a9:

    # "She has a knack for being alone in company, I've noticed."
    "以前から気づいていたけど、琳は人がそばにいても１人きりでいるこつを知っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2472
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_26f42f60:

    # "We head down the street, then turn left, then three times right, then left again."
    "俺たちは通りを下っていき、左に曲がる。今度は右に３回曲がって、また左に曲がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2474
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_84bcf04d:

    # "It's like that night from some time ago, we keep choosing directions randomly because it doesn't matter where we are going."
    "少し前の夜みたいに、俺たちは適当な方向に進んでいる。どこに向かっているかなんてどうでもよかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2476
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f8daf5f7:

    # "All that matters is walking and the sound of raindrops drumming against the umbrella."
    "大事なのは歩くことと、雨粒が傘を打ちつける音だけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2478
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1cc7befa:

    # "Water flows down from the roofs of the buildings and into the storm drains in wide rivers."
    "雨水が建物の屋根を流れ落ちて、雨どいから広い川になって流れ出てくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2480
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_edfcc32c:

    # "Even though I try to step over them, my feet are getting wet through my shoes."
    "それをまたごうとしても、俺の足は靴越しに濡れてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2482
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_076f37f9:

    # "We keep walking in silence that just begs to be broken again. I'm sure I am the only one feeling like this, though."
    "黙ったまま歩き続ける。この沈黙をまた破りたくなる。でも、そう感じてるのはきっと俺だけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2489
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e76b0f07:

    # hi "Why did you have the exhibition?"
    hi "どうして展覧会をやったんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2491
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_172269a2:

    # "Rin just shrugs sullenly and looks in the other direction. I give up at this point."
    "琳はただぶすっとして肩をすくめると、そっぽを向いてしまう。この時点で俺はさじを投げる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2499
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2502
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0dae1505:

    # n "{vspace=90}It's pointless."
    n "\n\n\nこんなの意味がない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2504
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5d37bd05:

    # n "{vspace=30}What did she want to accomplish? What she said at the night of the opening made me feel that there was something… something special she wanted."
    n "\n琳はなにを成し遂げたかったんだ？　オープニングの日の夜に琳の言葉を聞いたとき、琳はなにか……なにか特別なものを求めていたような気がした。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2506
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9ffa0137:

    # n "It felt to me that Rin hoped for something unattainable."
    n "琳は決して手の届かないものを望んでいたように思えた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2508
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c78dd15e:

    # n "She set the bar high and inside her own head she failed, no matter how much people liked her works."
    n "琳はバーを高い位置に掲げて、自分の頭の中でそれを飛び越えられなかったんだ。どれだけ他人が琳の絵を気に入っていても。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2510
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_60a233ec:

    # n "It's understandable to lack realism; most people do, even if not quite on the extreme level Rin takes it to."
    n "現実を受け入れられないというのは理解できる。ほとんどの人はそうだ。琳みたいに極端なレベルではないにしても。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2512
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3b02dc03:

    # n "{vspace=30}But it's not a reason to live in your private world that accepts no visitors."
    n "\nでも、それは誰にも邪魔されない個人的な世界に引きこもる理由にはならない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2514
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63cf5ae3:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=90}You can't bend the world to fit your twisted, megalomaniac cosmology where everything works just like you want."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n\nすべてが自分の思い通りになる、歪んだ誇大妄想めいた宇宙論にあてはまるように世界をねじ曲げることはできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2518
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bdadc52d:

    # n "{vspace=30}That's what frustrates me the most in Rin."
    n "\n琳のそういうところが一番イライラする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2520
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fe231760:

    # n "{vspace=30}She wants the world to live by her rules, disregarding everything that conflicts with those as irrelevant or unnecessary."
    n "\n琳は世界を自分のルールに従わせたいと思っている。ルールに合わないすべてのものは無意味だとか不要なものだとして無視している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2522
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ff42a06b:

    # n "I can't believe how anyone in Yamaku could not have the bare minimum perception to understand that the world can sometimes be very unfair."
    n "仮にも山久にいる人間が、この世界は時にとても不公平になりうる、ということを理解するためのほんの最小限の認識さえ持っていないなんて信じられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2524
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1581ca86:

    # n "I'm sure she's not the only one who wishes some things were different, but we can at least grasp the facts as they are."
    n "そうでないものもあってほしい、と願う人はきっと琳以外にもいるだろう。でも事実は事実として把握することはできる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2530
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2537
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63d1a98c:

    # "I take a sideways glance at Rin, who is looking up at our dome-shaped cover. It is a poor replacement for a real sky in its monochrome bleakness."
    "俺は横目で琳をちらりと見る。琳はドーム状の覆いを見上げている。わびしいモノクロームの、粗末なまがい物の空だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2539
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_971cdcdf:

    # "The rain just keeps falling."
    "雨はただ降りつづけている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2541
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_10b54f63:

    # "Just like the clouds today, Rin doesn't really give the feeling of wanting to be watched."
    "まるで今日の雲みたいに、見られたいという気持ちを琳はまったく表に出さない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2543
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8f57b2d9:

    # "She sulks, in unison with the sky that she loves so."
    "琳は大好きな空と同じように不機嫌になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2545
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_548676a9:

    # "I shouldn't have come. Her presence only reminds me of how angry I got because of these exact same reasons, and how those reasons probably can't ever change."
    "来るんじゃなかった。琳の存在は、まったく同じ理由で俺が激怒したこと、そしてその理由が変えようのないものであることを俺に思い出させるだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2547
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4a4dd5a6:

    # "Even though I want to say I'm sorry, even though I don't want us to break apart, I can't bring myself to say either of these things."
    "謝りたいとは思う。これで終わりにしたくないとも思う。でも、そのどちらも言葉に出すことができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2553
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f49fa71d:

    # "We keep measuring the rain-drenched streets one step at a time."
    "俺たちは雨に濡れた道路を一歩ずつ進む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2555
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3a3b6a41:

    # "Often, when you walk with someone else, your steps become synchronized as if through some weird subconscious pact."
    "誰かといっしょに歩いていると、しばしば歩調が潜在意識のなかで申し合わせたかのようにシンクロしてしまうことがある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2557
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6f47e9df:

    # "I noticed that ours never do."
    "俺と琳は決してそうならないことに気づいた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2566
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b5c742e3:

    # "Time passes, and the strikes against the drumskin of my umbrella fade as the clouds above slowly disperse to reveal a cerulean blue."
    "時間が過ぎていき、傘の帆を打ちつける雨は、上空の雲がゆっくりと散っていってセルリアンブルーの空をのぞかせていくにつれて弱まっていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2574
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_aa6eb418:

    # "Eventually the rain yields enough for me to close the umbrella, shaking the excess water off before I do."
    "ついに雨は傘を閉じられるほどに弱まってくれた。閉じる前に余計な雨水を振り落とす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2576
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c18ccb2a:

    # "While I wrestle with the mechanism, Rin stops so abruptly that I take five steps before realizing that she's not with me any more."
    "傘の開閉に手こずっていると、琳は突然足を止める。俺はもう５歩進むまで琳が隣にいないことに気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2578
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_caaac72a:

    # "Stupid umbrella seems to be jammed."
    "いまいましい傘はひっかかってしまったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2588
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e1cde282:

    # "When I turn around, I find her staring at me with an impassive face."
    "俺が振り向くと、琳が平然とした顔で俺を見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2590
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1450add9:

    # rin "I wanted someone to say 'I understand how you feel.'"
    rin "『君の気持ちがわかる』って、誰かに言ってほしかったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2592
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cbf075eb:

    # rin "Wouldn't that be great?"
    rin "そしたら最高だと思わない？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2594
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_59e0e773:

    # "Is that an answer to the question from before? I'm not sure."
    "今のは前に聞いた質問の答えなのか？　よくわからない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2596
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_23d487a5:

    # hi "Yeah… but why is it so important?"
    hi "ああ……でもどうしてそれがそんなに大事なんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2601
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0217691a:

    # rin "Because otherwise… I don't know if I can bear this."
    rin "だってそうじゃなかったら……耐えられないかもしれないから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2603
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ed14fd34:

    # "I was still in the middle of folding my umbrella so I just answered something to get the conversation going, but what she says now freezes my blood."
    "俺はまだ傘をたたむ途中だったので、会話を進めるだけのために適当な返事をした。でも今の琳の言葉に俺の血液は凍り付く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2608
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6f762f3c:

    # rin "If someone says a joke and laughs, you laugh with them, right? Because a joy doubled is a joy tripled, right?"
    rin "誰かが冗談を言って笑ったら、自分も一緒に笑うんでしょ？　だって２倍の喜びは３倍の喜びっていうでしょ、違う？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2613
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_909981a6:

    # rin "If someone is hurt and sad, you comfort and hug them, right? Because that way—"
    rin "誰かが辛くて悲しんでたら、励まして抱きしめてあげるんでしょ？　だって――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2615
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_879b98dc:

    # rin "…"
    rin "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2617
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_83b047f4:

    # "She pauses, her mouth still halfway open, then remembers to close it."
    "琳は固まる。口は半開きのままで、すぐに気づいて閉じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2622
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ca93fe8c:

    # "A gloom sets on her face and simultaneously on my heart."
    "陰鬱さが琳の顔と俺の心を同時に覆う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2624
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7b710278:

    # rin "I don't know why the right words never come out."
    rin "ぴったりの言葉っていうのが絶対出てこないのがどうしてなのか、わからない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2626
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_581f7d8b:

    # rin "I don't know why I can laugh only when I make myself."
    rin "自分で笑おうって思ったときしか笑えないのがどうしてか、わからない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2628
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_95a2d745:

    # rin "I don't know why everything stays only inside me, even when it feels like I'm going to burst."
    rin "自分が今にも爆発しそうなのに、どうして私の中から何も出て行かないのか、わからない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2630
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_66bf3f0f:

    # "Her flat, expressionless face does not waver even when she says that."
    "平然とした無表情の顔は、その言葉を口にしながら揺らぎもしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2632
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_18875c04:

    # "Her usual steady voice becomes only slightly quieter than normal."
    "いつもの落ち着いた声が普段よりわずかに小さくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2634
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_09d03f68:

    # rin "But who… who would ever want to feel like that?"
    rin "でも誰が……誰がそんな気持ちになりたいなんて思うの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2636
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cec8cfbb:

    # "Rin looks at me and I imagine the sadness reflecting from her eyes, whether it really is there or not."
    "琳が俺を見ると、本当にそれがあろうとなかろうと、俺はその目に映る悲しさを想像する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2638
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ae6f824c:

    # rin "I don't."
    rin "私はいやだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2640
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4998265c:

    # rin "I don't want to feel like that."
    rin "そんな気持ちになんてなりたくない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2642
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_56438df9:

    # "We stay silent for a little while after that."
    "それから俺たちはしばらくのあいだ黙り込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2644
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c2d35d33:

    # "Rin because she said all she has to say at once, I because I have no clue how to process what she just said."
    "琳はもう言うべき事を一息に言い切ってしまったから。俺は琳の言葉をどう解釈すればいいのか見当もつかないから。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2646
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a87c8b78:

    # "I don't understand what Rin is saying. Or I do, but I don't want to."
    "琳の言っていることがわからない。さもなければわかっていても、わかりたくないんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2648
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_464ca93e:

    # "For the first time both of these things happen, and it has to be simultaneously."
    "この二つのことが初めて同時に起こっている。しかも同時に違いない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2650
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4027b135:

    # "The irony is not lost on me."
    "その皮肉は俺にもわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2652
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_05baf856:

    # hi "I… think everyone wants to be understood. That's universal."
    hi "俺……誰だって理解されたいんだと思うぞ。みんなそうだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2654
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_10eb878c:

    # hi "But… that is impossible. Not only for me, but for anyone."
    hi "でも……それは無理だ。俺だけじゃなくて、誰にとってもだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2656
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c85f7b29:

    # hi "Sae said so too."
    hi "さえさんもそう言ってた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2658
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_43f6713f:

    # hi "You affect other people and are affected by them, but in the end, you see everything the way only you do."
    hi "誰でも他の人に影響を与えるし、逆に影響を受けもする。でも結局、人は自分だけの見方でものを見てるんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2660
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7a83d220:

    # hi "All people… are alone. We just use each other to alleviate that loneliness."
    hi "誰もみんな……独りぼっちだ。寂しさを和らげるためにお互いを利用しあってるんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2662
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7bfeda32:

    # "I wonder why I put it like that. It just felt that what Sae told me rang true, as if I had always thought like that without knowing it."
    "どうしてこんな言い方をしてるんだろう。さえさんの話が真実のように思えた。知らず知らずの間にいつもそう考えていたかのように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2664
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e08edf7e:

    # "It feels like she articulated my thoughts in clear, simple words and that stupid story about Picasso."
    "さえさんは俺の考えを明確でシンプルな言葉と、あのしょうもないピカソの話で説明してくれたように思えた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2669
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_32776b4f:

    # "Rin droops her head like a withering flower, letting her bangs fall in front of her eyes so that I can't see them."
    "琳はしおれた花のように頭をうなだれて、前髪を目の前に垂れ下げている。俺にはその目は見えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2671
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8462cffb:

    # rin "Why do you say that when you made me feel otherwise?"
    rin "私をそうじゃない気持ちにさせてくれたのに、どうしてそんなこというの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2673
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cb976a1a:

    # rin "It's unfair."
    rin "ずるいよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2675
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5fdefa48:

    # "The shaky voice that says those words does not belong to Rin."
    "その言葉を乗せた震える声は琳のものとは思えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2680
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5f2f6129:

    # rin "I really thought you could be different. That I wouldn't have to be alone."
    rin "君は違うかもしれないって本当に思ってたんだ。独りぼっちにならなくて済むかもって"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2682
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1da80edf:

    # "It's a bitter voice of disappointment, spoken through clenched teeth and a quivering chest."
    "噛みしめた歯と震える胸を通して伝わる、苦い失望の声。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2684
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6000cd34:

    # hi "I'm sorry…"
    hi "ごめんな……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2686
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_48be6363:

    # rin "If you are, why do you say something unfair like that?"
    rin "そう思ってるなら、どうしてそんなずるいこというの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2688
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_40e2a175:

    # "Her demanding tone invokes no particular feeling in me, apart from sadness that has been there since yesterday evening."
    "その厳しい声色は、昨日の夜からあり続ける悲しさを除けば、なんの感情も呼び起こさない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2690
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8cfc03b3:

    # "She doesn't intimidate me at all. Not any more."
    "もう琳のことは全然怖くない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2692
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_69772e59:

    # "Rin is not a prodigal art genius, nor an unpredictable idiot savant who could tear the logic lobe of my brain into shreds whenever she opened her mouth."
    "琳は奔放な絵の天才でもないし、口を開くたびに俺の左脳をずたずたにするような、予測のつかない『愚かな天才』でもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2694
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_80eff952:

    # "She is just a girl that I thought I loved, a loved one who wanted to be my friend, a friend whom I let down."
    "琳は俺が好きだと思っていた女の子だ。俺の友達になろうとした愛すべき人、期待を裏切ってしまった友達だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2696
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_dc671011:

    # hi "I say that, because saying otherwise would feel like lying."
    hi "違うことを言ったら、うそをついている気がするからだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2701
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d66e33b2:

    # rin "Why?"
    rin "どうして？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2703
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7b9192bc:

    # "Simple questions are the hardest ones. I have to close my eyes so I can focus my thoughts enough to answer her."
    "シンプルな疑問は一番答えづらい。俺は目を閉じて答えを探すのに集中しないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2705
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_30c0befa:

    # hi "I'm no artist. I can never be on the same level with you."
    hi "俺は芸術家じゃない。お前と同じレベルには絶対なれない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2707
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0030f0a3:

    # hi "There is a world only you can see, and to be part of it I would have to become you."
    hi "お前だけに見える世界があって、俺がそこに入り込むには、お前にならなきゃいけないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2709
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bdb58370:

    # hi "That's something I can't do, no matter how much you wish me to."
    hi "それは俺にはできない。お前がどんなに望んでも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2711
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_32e19661:

    # "Rin takes in my explanation without batting an eyelash."
    "琳は俺の説明をまつげひとつ動かさずに聞く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2713
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_70c4d36e:

    # rin "I'm not a real artist either."
    rin "私だってほんとの芸術家なんかじゃないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2715
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_29cb1b16:

    # rin "I just paint because it makes me feel like I can really feel something."
    rin "私はただ、何かを感じられるような気分になれるから絵を描いてるだけなんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2720
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a2ea179c:

    # "She holds her breath for a while before releasing it in a long, sigh-like flow."
    "琳はしばらく息を止めて、ため息のように深く吐き出す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2725
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a06d90bb:

    # rin "That's why I'll do it."
    rin "それが、やることにした理由"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2727
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9f0de06c:

    # rin "I have decided. I'll do it. If even Hisao says that, then that's what I will do."
    rin "私、決めた。やるよ。久夫までそんなこと言うなら、私はそうする"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2729
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f0418c62:

    # hi "Do what?"
    hi "なにをするんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2731
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce5fbd43:

    # "Rin starting a little shows that she had regressed into talking to herself again, but I'm glad I can snap her back even now."
    "琳はまた自分自身と会話するという小芝居を始めている。でも俺は今でも琳に言い返せていることがうれしい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2736
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_cdb6b300:

    # rin "Teacher and Sae have talked with someone who is a very important person. I got a scholarship for a big art school in Tokyo."
    rin "先生とさえさんが、大事なお客さんとしゃべってた。私、東京の大きな美術学校の特待生になったんだってさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2738
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3af27008:

    # rin "He said I could transfer there and start after the summer is over, if I wanted to."
    rin "私がそうしたければ、夏が終わったらそこに転校できるってその人が言ってた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2740
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_222b7f04:

    # rin "I don't really get why—"
    rin "どうしてかはわかんないけど――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2744
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5ccc20ae:

    # hi "Hold on, what? Why didn't you tell?"
    hi "待て、なんだって？　なんで言わなかったんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2749
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_89ac8615:

    # rin "I just did. You are the first one I told because I decided it just now."
    rin "今言ったよ。君が最初に言った相手なんだ、たった今決めたから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2751
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d43185c5:

    # "She keeps her cool, looking only mildly surprised at my shocked interjection."
    "動揺した俺の横槍に軽い驚きの表情を見せるだけで、琳は平静を保つ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2753
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b75b8aa9:

    # "It's ridiculous how easily she can say something so life-changing."
    "そんな人生が変わるようなことをあっさり口にするなんて、どうかしてる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2755
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1353e44e:

    # "I can't believe it. After what happened in February, I have had enough change for this year."
    "信じられない。２月の出来事以来、今年はありすぎるくらい変化があったというのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2757
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_bf32c6bd:

    # "Even if things are going badly right now, I don't want everything to change."
    "たとえ悪い方向に進んでいても、なにもかもが変わってしまうのはごめんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2759
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_63297b3a:

    # hi "But what about Yamaku? Don't you want to graduate with everyone?"
    hi "でも、山久はどうするんだよ？　みんなと卒業したくないのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2761
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_dd3fd004:

    # "My plea evokes no emotion."
    "俺の懇願はなんの感情も引き起こさない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2763
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6339218e:

    # rin "Everyone who?"
    rin "みんな？　誰のこと？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2765
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5b83c79a:

    # hi "Emi, me, everyone!"
    hi "笑美とか、俺とか、とにかくみんなだよ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2767
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fc9d34f8:

    # "I feel my pulse rising unnervingly, and my breathing becomes fast and shallow."
    "心臓が怖いほど鼓動して、息が浅く、速くなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2769
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6d5053e2:

    # "I don't want this to happen."
    "こんなのは嫌だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2771
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9475602e:

    # rin "Their life is not mine."
    rin "みんなの人生は私の人生じゃないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2773
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8fd58498:

    # rin "You just said that everyone is alone."
    rin "みんな独りぼっちだって、君が今言ったよね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2775
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6111e161:

    # hi "I didn't mean it like that—"
    hi "そんな意味で言ったんじゃ――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2777
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_72a13a46:

    # rin "You always said that you'd have to seize the day and start living your life."
    rin "君っていつも、今を楽しまなきゃとか、自分の人生を生きなきゃとか言ってたよね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2779
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5dcb8c2f:

    # rin "I have to live my life too."
    rin "私も自分の人生を生きないと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2781
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_960ce380:

    # "Rin is twisting my words to justify running away again. It makes me angry."
    "琳は俺の言葉をもっともらしく捻じ曲げて、また逃げようとしている。腹が立ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2783
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_443f95fc:

    # "Her ease, finality and seriousness in announcing this is unacceptable."
    "この話をする琳の気楽さ、確固とした態度、真剣さを俺は許せない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2785
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c7f719b2:

    # "As if changing your life is something you can do on a moment's whim! No!"
    "人生を変えることが、一瞬の思いつきでできるとでもいうのか！　冗談じゃない！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2787
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_47f0411b:

    # hi "How can you say that? Why don't you even try to belong?"
    hi "なんでそんなことが言えるんだよ？　どうしてどこかに属そうと努力もしないんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2789
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_db625628:

    # "The desperate accusation has no effect. It feels like I am once again out of weapons, that I can't reach through to her no matter what I try."
    "必死の非難も効果はない。また打つ手無しになった気分だ。俺がどう出ようと、琳には届かない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2791
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a0eaae9b:

    # "Rin is so frustratingly absolute in her own judgment that it might make me hate her if I didn't love her, even though I don't know which way I am feeling any more."
    "琳は腹が立つほど自分の決めたことを絶対視する。琳のことが好きでなければ憎んでいたかもしれない。でもどっちが俺の気持ちなのか、もうわからなくなってしまった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2796
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d5e62c37:

    # rin "Maybe I am that kind of a person. The kind that belongs only to herself."
    rin "私ってそういう人間なのかもね。自分自身にしか属さない種類の人間"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2798
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_53beb146:

    # hi "I won't accept that."
    hi "そんなの認めないぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2800
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8a5624cd:

    # "Her nonchalant eyes do not seem to care whether I accept her decision or not."
    "その無関心な目は、俺が琳の決意を受け入れたかどうかなんて気にも留めないようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2802
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2804
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_40b7767e:

    # "The pause lets me cool down, to find my sensibilities."
    "その沈黙に俺は冷静になり、理性を取り戻す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2806
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9a6da514:

    # "While I do, the parting rainclouds reveal a setting sun that still has time to shine its last few warming rays before calling it a day."
    "その間に雨雲が割れて、隠れていた太陽がのぞく。一日が終わる前に最後の暖かな光を照らす時間が残っていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2808
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_eb76af50:

    # "A mosaic of light and shadow spreads on the walls of the buildings, on the street and the fence circling a park on the other side of the street."
    "光と影がモザイク模様になって建物の壁や道路、通りの向こうの公園を囲うフェンスに広がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2810
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_57201433:

    # "Rin's shadow is long enough to reach my feet."
    "琳の影が俺の足まで届くほど伸びる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2812
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_254a5629:

    # "It's like one of those western movies, with two cowboys staring each other down, ready to sling their guns at each other."
    "カウボーイがお互いを睨み合って、今にも銃を抜こうとしている西部劇みたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2814
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_75bc3df4:

    # "The one who loses his nerve will eat lead."
    "怖気づいたほうが負けを喫する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2816
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7e45710c:

    # "I realize I would have the disadvantage because the sun is behind Rin, stinging my eyes."
    "琳が背にしている太陽が目に染みて、不利な立場にあることに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2821
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_956ad423:

    # rin "Do you hate me?"
    rin "私のこと、嫌い？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2823
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_11bdbe9f:

    # "She draws first and I have no counter."
    "琳が最初に切り出す。そして俺に反論はない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2825
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3b1d8348:

    # hi "I don't know."
    hi "さあな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2827
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ad8b8b19:

    # "Did I lose?"
    "俺の負けか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2829
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5a5c0a67:

    # hi "Even if I did, what would it matter?"
    hi "もしそうだとしても、それがどうしたっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2831
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4f4e1a70:

    # "I scramble for words, words that could salvage this. I find none."
    "俺は言葉を、この事態を救いうる言葉を必死に探す。なにも見つからない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2833
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fb7e1ba6:

    # hi "You are my friend, I promised you that. I am not the kind of guy who forgets about promises."
    hi "お前は友達だ、そう約束した。俺は約束を反故にするような男じゃない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2835
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_707e1298:

    # hi "I think that is the most important thing. We could try to—"
    hi "それがいちばん大事なことだと思う。俺たちはもっと――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2840
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2edda4e4:

    # rin "Don't say it."
    rin "言わないで"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2847
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_3623627b:

    # "Predicting what I was going to say, Rin throws herself into my arms, pressing her body against mine."
    "俺が言おうとしたことを予測すると、琳は俺の胸に飛び込んで、体を俺に押しつける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2849
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2736a4f0:

    # "I feel her rising to her tiptoes to match my height and snuggle closer."
    "琳が俺にすり寄るためにつま先立ちをするのがわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2851
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a4f3b77f:

    # "The scent of her hair is that of rain and paint thinner. Her body feels as cold as always. Her breathing against my neck is as hot as always."
    "髪から雨と絵の具用のシンナーの匂いがする。体はいつものように冷たい。そして首筋にあたる息はいつものように熱い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2853
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a0af7b9d:

    # "It's funny how all of those feel so familiar even though Rin, as a whole, does not."
    "その一つ一つにはとても親しみがあるのに、琳自身に対してはそんな気がしないのがおかしい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2858
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_a334318d:

    # rin "Are you sure you can't hate me?"
    rin "本当に私のことを嫌いになれない自信がある？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2860
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e54d1688:

    # "Rin whispers into my ear so close I can feel the movements of her lips against my earlobe."
    "琳が俺の耳元で囁く。唇の動きが耳たぶに伝わってくるくらい近い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2862
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d1a66320:

    # "It's teasing, taunting. If this was some other kind of situation I'm sure it would tickle tantalizingly and I would giggle even though I'm a guy."
    "からかっている。馬鹿にしている。これがまた別の状況だったら、欲情してしまうほどくすぐったく思うだろう。男の俺でもクスクス笑ってしまうだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2864
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7a4aa9a5:

    # rin "It would be easier if you did."
    rin "その方が楽になれるよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2866
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fbe64de4:

    # hi "Dunno. It's pretty hard when you are hugging me like that."
    hi "知るかよ。そうやって抱きつかれてたら難しいんだけど"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2871
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b9eaea40:

    # "I wonder if it's because of my sullen voice, but she takes a step back, looking wistfully at her short arms."
    "俺の不機嫌な声のせいなのかはわからないけど、琳は短い腕を物憂げに見ながら引き下がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2873
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_4b12741f:

    # "I wish she hadn't done that."
    "こんなことはして欲しくなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2875
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_658b4d83:

    # rin "I can't hug anyone, Hisao."
    rin "私、誰ともハグできないんだよ、久夫"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2877
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_7d52b351:

    # rin "I'm a bad person like that."
    rin "そういう悪い子なんだよ、私"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2882
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_29e24d1e:

    # rin "That's why I have to go."
    rin "だから行かないといけないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2884
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f2da7cf9:

    # "She disarms me completely with three simple sentences, rendering me unable to argue any more."
    "３つの短い言葉で、琳は完全に俺の戦意を喪失させる。もう異議を唱えることはできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2886
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d92b597d:

    # "And since I can't, Rin is free to continue as she wills, shifting her weight from one foot to the other before she does."
    "反論できないおかげで琳は自由に話を続けられる。その前に重心をもう片方の足に移す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2891
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c14dd8d3:

    # rin "I will learn to hug people in my own way."
    rin "私なりのやり方で人をハグできるよう勉強するよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2893
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_5a5e600a:

    # rin "I'm sure I can become a real artist."
    rin "きっと本当の芸術家になれると思う"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2895
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f734e332:

    # rin "But if I do… I might not be able to be me any more."
    rin "でもそうしたら……もう私ではいられなくなっちゃうかもしれない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2897
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_56bd51cc:

    # "The hint of a smile on her lips is a betrayal, a false sign of self-confidence in a future that even Rin can't foresee."
    "くちびるに浮かんだかすかな笑みは欺瞞だ。琳ですら予想のつかない未来に対する自信を示す偽りの兆し。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2899
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0aa77a3c:

    # "I'd want to interpret it as a sign of hope, but I know better."
    "希望の兆しと思いたいところだけど、俺にはお見通しだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2901
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_984cd297:

    # "Rin just keeps smiling that awkward, forced smile of hers."
    "琳はただ、あのぎこちない無理やりな笑顔を続けている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2903
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_35c122ed:

    # rin "That's why… please forget about me, and I will forget about you too."
    rin "だから……私のことは忘れて。私も君のこと、忘れるから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2905
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c893b703:

    # rin "I'm sure that—{w=0.5}{nw}"
    rin "そうすれば――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2910
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_766706de:

    # "She chokes in the middle of saying something I would never come to hear."
    "何か言おうとする途中で息を詰まらせ、俺は聞きそびれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2912
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c663fefa:

    # "I don't think I'd wanted to hear it anyway."
    "聞きたいような言葉じゃないんだろうけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2914
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_268c61ba:

    # "This is not fair."
    "こんなのは卑怯だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2916
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_1054418b:

    # "Rin is not joking. Rin is always serious. But I can't accept it, I can't."
    "本気なんだ。琳はいつだって真剣だ。でもこんなの受け入れられない。受け入れられるか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2918
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_b1787844:

    # "Forget about you? How could I ever…?"
    "忘れろだって？　そんなことできるわけ……？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2920
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_af6e097f:

    # "That's what I'd like to say. But I don't know how I would continue. I can't come up with anything good to say, so I have to challenge her."
    "そう言ってやりたい。でもどう続ければいい？　何もいい言葉が思いつけない。だから反論しないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2922
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8ec01e7b:

    # hi "How can you say such a thing?"
    hi "どうしてそんなことが言えるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2927
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_e068ae10:

    # "Rin raises her eyes to meet mine, they are serious and deep, a perfect image of the uncharted territory I always thought they were."
    "琳は目を上げて俺と視線を合わせる。深くて真剣な目だ。いつもそこにあると思っていた未知の領域の、完璧なイメージだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2929
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_8dd10a61:

    # "Even now, I can't read her emotions from those unblinking, jade irises that never could reflect what they saw."
    "この期に及んでさえ、そのまばたきをしない、そこに映るものを決して反射しないひすい色の虹彩から、俺は感情を読み取ることができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2931
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_0f93dbe1:

    # rin "It's easy. After all, I am good at forgetting things."
    rin "簡単だよ。なんだかんだで私、忘れるのは得意だから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2933
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2935
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_fc924da8:

    # "Her unfairness is choking my throat, but I manage to utter the question burning my mind."
    "琳のずるさに息が詰まりかけるけど、俺は自分の心を焼き続けている質問をどうにか声に出す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2937
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_edab4dd5:

    # hi "So, is this it? Is this goodbye?"
    hi "じゃあ、これで終わりなのか？　これでサヨナラかよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2939
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2941
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_445a5121:

    # "Rin kept looking at me gently, without answering my question."
    "琳は俺の質問には答えず、穏やかに俺を見続けていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2943
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_d9c22d49:

    # "From her eyes I could see that she didn't even need to say anything."
    "その目を見て、もう言葉を発する必要さえなかったんだとわかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2945
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_c9799485:

    # "There were no more words for us."
    "もはや俺たちの間に言葉は存在しなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2952
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_9324cd77:

    # "She turned around and walked off without looking back."
    "琳はきびすを返すと、振り向くこともなく立ち去った。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2954
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_91ab4a5f:

    # "All around me, the world kept changing, little by little, but I was left standing there."
    "俺の周囲では、世界は変わり続けていた。少しずつ。でも、俺はこの場に立ち尽くしていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2959
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_6c80a6b7:

    # "The sun dropped below the horizon, casting long and thin shadows across the street."
    "夕日が長く細い影を通りに落としながら、水平線に沈んでいた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2961
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_55bcdcc7:

    # "In the waning light, Rin's distancing back seemed to be like from a faraway dream."
    "薄れゆく光の中で、遠ざかる琳の背中は夢の彼方から来ているように見えた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2963
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_09b6a8a5:

    # "The gap between us grew slowly."
    "俺たちの距離が少しずつ開いていった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2965
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_2b6ec8f5:

    # "The ripples on the puddles she stepped on expanded until they met the limits of their tiny existence and disappeared without a trace."
    "琳が踏みつける水たまりのさざなみは、その小さな存在の限界を迎えるまで広がっていき、跡形もなく消えていった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2967
translate jp a4_rin_the_world_only_can_you_see_f4d5e348:

    # "Her words stayed frozen deep inside my heart."
    "琳の言葉は俺の心の奥深くで凍り付いたままだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2979
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2982
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_e96c8674:

    # n "{vspace=30}Vacation, huh?"
    n "\n夏休みだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2984
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_329304f8:

    # n "Some people will stay at the school even over the holidays, some will go back to their families."
    n "休みの間も学校に残るやつはいるし、家族のもとへ帰るやつもいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2986
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_77de5f7d:

    # n "I don't know what to do. I should go buy a train ticket for my trip back home, but I can't bring myself to do it."
    n "俺はどうすればいいかわからない。帰りの電車の切符を買いに行かなきゃいけないけど、そうする気分になれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2988
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_64e8f2ca:

    # n "I bet I'm going to get a call from home again. Mom's going to pester me about when I'm coming back, and I'm not going to know what to answer."
    n "多分実家から電話してくるだろう。母親にいつ帰ってくるんだとうるさく聞かれるし、俺もどう答えればいいか見当がついていないだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2990
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_8e72648f:

    # n "{vspace=30}This is really lousy. In the current state of things with Rin, it feels like I can't just bail out of here and pretend we are through."
    n "\nほんとにうんざりする。今の琳との関係を考えれば、ただここから抜け出して、ケリがついたふりをするなんてできないと思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2992
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cbef346b:

    # n "{vspace=30}And now, she has other problems of her own. I thought that the exhibition opening would give her a breather, but I was sorely mistaken."
    n "\nそれに今、琳は別の問題を抱えている。展覧会のオープニングはいい骨休めになると思っていたけど、それはとんでもない間違いだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2994
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a734eb67:

    # n "{vspace=60}The tangle just seems to thicken."
    n "\n\n話がどんどんもつれていっている気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:2998
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3003
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_bbc8465f:

    # "A sharp knock on the door interrupts the quiet but frantic mood of the last 15 minutes of the exam."
    "テスト終了１５分前の静かだけど慌しい空気に、ドアを叩く鋭いノックが割り込んでくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3010
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0de9b330:

    # mu "Come in."
    mu "どうぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3023
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0583d852:

    # "The opening door reveals the art teacher, who steps in with his jacket swirling around him as though in a gust of wind."
    "ドアが開くと、野宮先生が現れる。ジャケットの裾を風のようにはためかせながら入ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3025
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_1589bc1c:

    # "He glances at Mutou, who glances back at him."
    "武藤先生をちらっと見ると、先生も見返す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3033
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c1fcfe89:

    # "A frown spreads simultaneously on both of their faces as the men measure each other with their gazes."
    "お互いにその視線で相手を推し量る間に、渋い表情が二人の顔に同時に広がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3035
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_4f63ba5a:

    # no "Excuse me, could I borrow Mr. Nakai for a moment?"
    no "すみませんがね、中井君を少しお借りしたいんですよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3037
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_d060c84f:

    # mu "Excuse {b}me{/b}, Mr. Nomiya, but we are in the middle of an exam here."
    mu "ええ、{b}こちらこそ{/b}すみませんけどね、野宮先生。今テストの真っ最中でしてね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3039
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_b0ffeef2:

    # "A chilly atmosphere suddenly spreads in the middle of the summer afternoon as the two men try to stare each other down."
    "二人がお互いをにらみ倒そうとして、真夏の午後に突然冷たい空気が広がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3044
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_909b80ce:

    # no "This is urgent, and it seems that Nakai has already finished."
    no "緊急なんですよ。それに中井はもう解答を終えているようですが？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3046
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_de5f031f:

    # "Both men turn to look at me, staring at me like a pair of basilisks trying to petrify a tasty snack."
    "二人がこっちを向いて、うまそうなおやつを石にしようとしている二頭のバジリスクみたいに俺を見つめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3048
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_93f0744a:

    # "It's true that I've been idle for a good while now, so Nomiya is right, but…"
    "もうかなりの間ヒマにしていたのは事実なので、野宮先生の言うとおりだけど……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3053
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_2ce8ee7f:

    # mu "Nakai, would you like to check your answers one more time?"
    mu "中井、もう一度解答を見直してくれるか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3055
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_df9ba85a:

    # "Mutou speaks with an odd intonation, weighting certain words as if trying to send a message."
    "武藤先生は妙なイントネーションで、メッセージを送るかのように特定の言葉に重みをつけていう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3057
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_9f6ddf1d:

    # "The pressure from their stares makes me rapidly shake my head, which is apparently interpreted as an answer of some sort."
    "先生たちの視線のプレッシャーで、俺の頭が急激に揺れる。それがなんらかの解答として受け取られたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3064
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7b8ebea7:

    # mu "Very well. Nakai, go with Mr. Nomiya, if you please."
    mu "そうか。なら野宮先生と一緒に行くといい、中井"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3066
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_b7850a7f:

    # mu "Take your bag with you and bring your test paper to my desk."
    mu "かばんは持って行け。解答用紙は私のところに提出すること"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3071
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_2ea5b16f:

    # mu "You have a nice vacation."
    mu "いい夏休みをな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3073
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_3d7834a3:

    # hi "Umm. Er, you too, teacher."
    hi "あっ、ええ、先生も"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3075
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a6dff9e2:

    # "The entire world… well, at least the classroom seems to hold its breath just for me, putting the exam on hold until I stand up, collect my stuff and walk to the door."
    "世界全体が……いや、少なくとも教室内が、テストの手を止めて固唾を呑んで見守るなか、俺は立ち上がり、荷物をまとめてドアのところまで歩いていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3077
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_35f58f7c:

    # "I can feel the stares in the back of my neck. My classmates probably think I'm in for some detention or something, on the last day of the school before summer vacation."
    "首の後ろに視線を感じる。クラスのみんなは俺が居残りかなにかさせられると思ってるんだろう。夏休み前の最後の日に。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3079
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_e767c37c:

    # "I don't know what the teacher wants from me, but I can guess it probably is not detention and also that it probably has something to do with Rin again."
    "先生が俺に何の用事があるのか知らないけど、たぶん居残りではないだろうし、何か琳と関係のあることなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3089
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_9f1852b3:

    # "Nomiya doesn't take me anywhere, contenting himself with the hallway as it's completely abandoned."
    "野宮先生は俺をどこへ連れて行くでもない、全く人のいない廊下で十分だったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3096
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_1e354d89:

    # no "Do you know where Tezuka is?"
    no "手塚がどこにいるか知らないか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3098
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_8c4ea6f8:

    # "So she is trying to avoid the teacher… par for the course, probably."
    "琳は先生を避けようとしてたってわけか……そりゃそうだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3100
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_566d2aa5:

    # "I wonder if she realizes that she can't avoid dealing with this indefinitely."
    "いつまでも逃げ続けてはいられないってことに、琳は気づいてるのかな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3102
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_2d914b5b:

    # hi "I have no idea."
    hi "さあ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3104
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_f3678e70:

    # hi "You have probably asked in her homeroom next door."
    hi "琳のホームルームは隣ですけど、もう聞きには行ったんですよね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3109
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_389fb581:

    # no "Of course I have! I have searched every nook and cranny of this blasted school and the girls' dorm."
    no "当たり前だ！　このいまいましい学校の隅から隅まで探したぞ。女子寮もだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3111
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7f306d19:

    # no "You are the last one to see her since yesterday and you are her friend."
    no "昨日、手塚を見たのはお前が最後だ。それにお前は手塚の友達だろう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3116
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_82fbee90:

    # no "Work with me here. Aren't you worried?"
    no "お前も考えるんだ。心配じゃないのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3118
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cc663513:

    # "I am, but I don't know what I could do."
    "心配だけど、俺になにができるだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3120
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_502ebbdf:

    # "Rin did something incomprehensible yesterday, even for her."
    "昨日、琳は理解しがたいことをした。琳自身にとってさえもだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3122
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7a68094c:

    # "She seemed really confused."
    "本当に混乱しているみたいだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3124
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_15b583f7:

    # hi "Maybe she just wants some time to think then. I got the feeling that she had second thoughts about having that exhibition."
    hi "琳は考える時間が欲しいってだけかも知れませんよ。展覧会をやることについて考え直してたんじゃないかって気がします"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3126
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0a4398c3:

    # "Or something. She really didn't explain what was wrong."
    "違うかもしれないけど。何がまずかったかなんて、琳は全然説明しなかったし。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3131
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a6fe6193:

    # no "What second thoughts?"
    no "何を考え直したというんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3133
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_6e9b4029:

    # hi "I dunno. Just got that feeling."
    hi "さあ。そんな気がしたってだけです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3135
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7956358e:

    # "I am being a little dishonest with the teacher, but this is not something I should be meddling with."
    "先生相手にこの態度はちょっと不誠実だけど、これは俺が首を突っ込むべきことじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3137
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_e7e1c948:

    # "He came to me… yes, why? Maybe he thinks I'm some kind of confidant of Rin's, but I don't think I can help with this matter."
    "先生は俺のもとへ来た……そうだ、どうして？　俺が琳の親友かなにかだとでも思ってるんだろうけど、この件で俺が役に立てるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3142
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_67914ac7:

    # "The teacher huffs and scratches his head in confusion."
    "先生は機嫌を悪くし、困惑して頭をかく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3144
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_bc4932fe:

    # no "What's up with that girl? This is so unlike her, she's always been so goal-driven."
    no "いったいどうしてしまったんだ？　実に手塚らしくない、いつも目標に向かって邁進していたというのに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3146
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a698630c:

    # "'Goal-driven?' Those don't really strike me as words to describe Rin with."
    "『目標に邁進』だって？　琳を説明する言葉としては見当違いな気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3148
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_aae2da5f:

    # "To me, she always felt obsessive at best."
    "俺からすれば、よく言っても琳はいつも何かに追い立てられているようだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3150
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_b7db4b12:

    # hi "Er, I don't mean to be rude, but wasn't it you who pushed Rin to that direction in the first place?"
    hi "その、失礼なことを言うつもりはないんですけど、そもそも琳をそっち向きに後押ししたのは先生じゃないんですか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3155
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_5a0efb0a:

    # no "Her goal is my goal. That is a mentor's job."
    no "手塚の目標は私の目標だ。それが師のつとめというものだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3157
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c9e6b5c1:

    # hi "I guess so. I just don't know if painting can make her happy."
    hi "そうかもしれません。ただ俺は、絵を描くことで琳が幸せになれるのかわからなくて"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3162
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_88a7d18b:

    # no "That's pretty preposterous of you to say, Nakai."
    no "お前にそんなことを言う筋合いはないぞ、中井"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3164
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_d223337e:

    # "He suddenly sounds pretty irate. Did I say something stupid?"
    "先生は急に怒りで声を荒げる。何かまずいことでも言ったか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3169
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c6fd24d7:

    # no "You don't understand, do you? It is not a question of happiness. For every gain there is a sacrifice to be made."
    no "何もわかっていないな。幸福の問題じゃない。何を得るにしても、そこには支払うべき犠牲というものがあるのだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3174
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_458c5978:

    # no "There is no free lunch, but could I… would I let that girl waste away her talent if she has a moment of doubt? Never!"
    no "ただより高いものはない。しかし手塚が一瞬でも疑いを持ったせいでその才能を無駄にするなどということを私がしただろうか……許しただろうか？　そんなはずはない！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3176
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cc053d13:

    # no "Painting is work just like any other. Tezuka might make it look like child's play to you, but she works hard every day to make her art."
    no "絵を描くことも作業だ、他と何の違いもない。お前には手塚がやすやすと絵を描いているように見えるかもしれん、だが手塚は毎日懸命に取り組んでいるんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3178
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_de48fc4a:

    # no "To become extraordinary, one has to make an extraordinary effort."
    no "非凡であるためには、非凡なる努力を積み重ねなければならない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3180
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_5600875c:

    # "The more the teacher talks, the more I feel that Rin doesn't think like that, even though I have no idea how she thinks."
    "先生がしゃべればしゃべるほど、琳はそんなこと考えていないという気持ちが強くなる。実際にどう思っているのかなんて全くわからないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3185
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7a9b4bba:

    # no "I can very well understand why she would sacrifice her summer vacation and make up for the lost classes and exams to get a chance at showing her art."
    no "手塚がなぜ夏休みを犠牲にし、休んだ授業や試験を後から埋め合わせてまで作品を展示しようとしたのか、私にはよくわかるぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3187
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cbba8f9c:

    # no "This is the path she has taken, and to go all the way, that's not easy."
    no "これが手塚の選んだ道だ。それを最後まで進むのは容易なことではない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3189
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c59dea95:

    # no "I know she is young, and things are hard for her just like for all the kids here in this school, but that's no excuse."
    no "手塚は若いし、この学校の他の子たちと同じように苦労を負っているが、そんなことは言い訳にはならない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3191
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_80f7a08f:

    # "He is finished."
    "そこで話は終わる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3193
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_f2449dda:

    # hi "But—"
    hi "でも――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3198
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_24d8a14e:

    # no "Do you have anything like what art is to Tezuka?"
    no "お前には手塚にとっての芸術のようなものがあるのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3200
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0f269d05:

    # hi "No…"
    hi "いえ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3202
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0191c814:

    # "That's right. I have only vague ideas of my future, no goal to shoot for, no dream to blindly reach for."
    "そのとおりだ。自分の将来についてはあいまいな考えしかない。狙うべきゴールもない。がむしゃらに追い求める夢もない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3204
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_68bd3fa5:

    # "I joined the art club in search of something I could be interested in, to get inspired by."
    "俺は何か興味を持てそうなこと、やる気をかき立てられるようなことを求めて美術部に入った。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3206
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c57ea0ce:

    # "Did I find something like that?"
    "そんなものを見つけられたか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3208
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_c61de6a1:

    # "All I found in the end… was Rin."
    "結局俺が見つけたのは……琳だけだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3210
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_4f4dbaab:

    # hi "No, I don't have a passion like that."
    hi "いえ、俺にはあんな情熱はないです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3215
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_98ac8d70:

    # no "Then you can't understand."
    no "それでは理解できまい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3217
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cd6fc25f:

    # "His flat statement allows no counterargument."
    "先生はきっぱりと言う。そこに反論の余地はない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3219
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_01af5b29:

    # hi "But… she might not understand even herself."
    hi "でも……琳は自分でもわかってないのかも知れません"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3221
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_69301cc8:

    # "Still, I carry on arguing, out of spite if for nothing else."
    "それでも、俺は反論する。当てつけ以外の何物でもないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3226
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_3b9a8234:

    # no "How could she not? She's been at it so hard for the past few weeks that she put off even coming to school, not to say anything about attending class. Don't be ridiculous."
    no "理解していないわけがなかろう。この数週間ずっと授業を休むどころか、学校にも登校せずに展覧会に全力で取り組んでいたんだ。ばかげたことを言うな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3228
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_87e84184:

    # "I don't think I'm being ridiculous, but as I have no rebuttal, Nomiya seems to consider this one his win."
    "ばかげたことを言っているつもりはない。でも反論しなかったので、野宮先生は自分の勝ちと思ったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3233
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_7901202f:

    # no "At any rate, the opening was quite successful despite Tezuka hardly showing up."
    no "とにかく、手塚はあまり顔を出さなかったが、展覧会のオープニングは大成功だった"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3235
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0c222304:

    # no "Many people were interested in her work and one piece was even sold for a reasonable price."
    no "多くの人が手塚の作品に関心を持ってくれた。しかも一枚はそれなりの値段で売れたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3237
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_cb9cf776:

    # hi "Well, that's nice isn't it?"
    hi "へえ、それは良かったんじゃないですか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3242
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_d9a29ef8:

    # no "Yes, it's fantastic news! I hoped that Tezuka would come to her senses when she heard about this, but…"
    no "ああ、すばらしい知らせだ！　手塚もこれを聞いて目を覚ましてくれればと願っていたのだがな……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3244
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_b33e402c:

    # "He sighs and takes off his glasses, cleaning them against his jacket before putting them on his nose again."
    "先生はため息をつくと、眼鏡を外してジャケットで拭き、もう一度鼻にかけ直す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3249
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_0477d0e4:

    # no "At any rate, I should be going. There is this mess to be settled with Sae and everyone."
    no "とにかくだ、もう行かなくてはならん。さえや他の方々との間で、収拾をつけないといけない件があるのでな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3251
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_439f3294:

    # no "If you see Tezuka, please ask her to come see me. Otherwise, have a nice vacation."
    no "もし手塚を見たら、私のところへ来るよう伝えてくれ。それと、いい夏休みをな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3253
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_e5c8fee6:

    # hi "Thanks…"
    hi "どうも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3262
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_d10cffe6:

    # "After he has disappeared around the corner, I ponder where Rin could really be."
    "先生が角を曲がって見えなくなると、俺は琳が実際にいそうな場所をじっくりと考える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3264
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a985ab63:

    # "It feels like she has not one, but at least half a dozen of these 'secret places.'"
    "琳はそういう『秘密の場所』を一つどころか六つは知っていそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3266
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_a915d233:

    # "I balance between the desire to solve this tangle and to drop it for good."
    "この混乱を解決したいという気持ちと、これを最後に投げ出してしまいたいという気持ちとをはかりにかける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3268
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_337552a9:

    # "The disused classroom is just a few feet away."
    "使われていない教室がすぐ先にある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3270
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_da38e87f:

    # "What to do?"
    "どうしようか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3272
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3280
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_4a9e5232:

    # "As I push open the door, only the shadows greet me from the inside."
    "ドアを押し開けると、暗い影だけが俺を出迎える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3282
translate jp a4_rin_desperate_glory_f957c2b7:

    # hi "Hey there."
    hi "おーい"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3295
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ee3f73f1:

    # "She's standing in the middle of the sunlit room, peering through the gaps of the curtains out into the yard."
    "陽の差し込む教室の真ん中に琳は立っていて、はためくカーテンの切れ目を通して庭の方をじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3297
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8c7aaa2e:

    # "Like so often before, she doesn't start or jump, just calmly waits for me to make the first move."
    "今までと同じように、琳は驚きも飛び上がりもせず、ただ静かに俺が先に動くのを待っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3299
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_03a649fa:

    # "It's as if she is trying to become a permanent part of the furniture."
    "まるで教室の常備品の一部にでもなろうとしているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3301
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d59819a9:

    # hi "The teacher is looking for you."
    hi "先生が探してるぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3303
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_96f6b750:

    # "A blank look over her shoulder is all I get, accompanied by a cryptic nonexpression on her face."
    "肩越しにうつろな視線が返ってくるだけだ。その表情は不可解な無感情さをともなっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3305
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_85c360b3:

    # rin "Are you looking for me too?"
    rin "君も私を探してるの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3307
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_3642d3bc:

    # hi "Nah, I already found you, didn't I?"
    hi "いや、もう見つけた。違うか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3309
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6edd8a73:

    # rin "Did you?"
    rin "そうなの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3314
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b7f14a11:

    # "She furrows her brow, looking so puzzled that it makes me wonder if the question was asked in all seriousness."
    "琳は困惑したように眉根を寄せる。あまりに怪訝そうな表情で、今の質問が本気だったのかどうか疑いたくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3316
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fcda1a5e:

    # "Maybe it was."
    "本気なのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3318
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c077d5b0:

    # hi "Are you talking metaphorically now?"
    hi "今のはたとえ話か？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3323
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a3aa92a4:

    # rin "Do you mean like eels, caves and dark, stormy nights?"
    rin "ウナギとか洞窟とか、真っ暗な嵐の夜みたいにってこと？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3328
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8adb383e:

    # rin "I am bad at talking like that."
    rin "そういう話し方は苦手なんだけどな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3330
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3334
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0ec3e92f:

    # "The abruptly-ended greetings give me the chance to close the door behind me and sit down on a dust-covered desktop."
    "唐突に挨拶が終わったので、俺は後ろのドアを閉めて、ほこりの積もった机の上に腰掛ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3339
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e6a49020:

    # "Rin stays standing, but at least she turns around."
    "琳は立ち続けているけど、ようやくこちらを向く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3341
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_046e264a:

    # "I soon wish she didn't though, so oppressive is her expectant stare."
    "すぐにそうしないで欲しかったと思い直す。琳の期待に満ちた視線があまりに耐え難い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3343
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_755ef64b:

    # "This is her place and I'm an intruder, although a tolerated one. Despite that, she still waits for me to say something."
    "ここは琳の領域で、俺は大目に見られているとはいえ侵入者だ。それでも、琳は俺が何か言うのを待っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3345
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_3b3ea37a:

    # "If I only knew what."
    "何を言えばいいのかわかっていれば、だけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3347
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3349
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_04a59135:

    # "The sunlit silence presses me towards decisions."
    "太陽に照らされた沈黙が俺に決断を促す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3351
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_672af16b:

    # "I came here without really thinking what I would do, apart from delivering Nomiya's short message in case Rin was here."
    "琳がここにいた場合に野宮先生の短い伝言を伝える以外は、何をするかまったく考えずにここに来た。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3353
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_4150f5aa:

    # "She was, and now I don't know what else I want to say… what else I should say?"
    "そしたら琳はいて、俺は他になんて言いたいのかわからない……なんて言えばいい？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3355
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5d122f4b:

    # "I hover between my two options for a moment."
    "俺は２つの選択肢の間を行き来する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3357
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e9d74956:

    # "Rin being troubled troubles me too. It's a surprising revelation, almost as big as realizing that she really is troubled was."
    "琳が苦しんでいると、俺も苦しい。これは驚くべき発見だ。そもそも琳が苦しんでいる、という発見と同じくらい大きい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3359
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9ef1978c:

    # "Nothing I can do would probably help, and I might be partially to blame too."
    "俺に手助けできることはおそらくない。そしてある程度は俺のせいなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3361
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_33817fb1:

    # "Does it mean I should just wash my hands of her?"
    "それは、もう琳と関わるのをやめた方がいいってことか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3363
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_801d9523:

    # "Didn't think so."
    "そんなはずはないな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3365
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c7124952:

    # hi "So… what's wrong?"
    hi "それで……どうしたんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3367
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3372
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_be162ee9:

    # rin "Nothing."
    rin "別に"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3374
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_66076e58:

    # "She starts to turn away again, as if trying to physically exit a conversation she doesn't want to have."
    "琳はしたくもない会話から物理的に抜け出そうとするかのように、またそっぽを向いてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3376
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8a4478d7:

    # hi "Rin, stop trying to dodge me or I'll leave."
    hi "なあ琳、俺を避けるのはやめろよ。でないと俺帰るぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3381
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a61bcc4a:

    # rin "Okay."
    rin "わかったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3383
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b3376472:

    # hi "Do you want me to leave?"
    hi "帰ってほしいのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3388
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7a4f3897:

    # rin "Are you still angry?"
    rin "まだ怒ってるの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3390
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9f1fab98:

    # "It took us - or was it only me? - ten seconds to swamp the conversation into this."
    "たった１０秒で、俺たちは――いや、俺だけか？――会話をこのどん底に沈めてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3392
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1bf70863:

    # "I wish we could erase the past, or failing that, forget all about it."
    "今までのことを消し去ってしまいたい。それがだめなら、せめてなにもかも忘れてしまいたい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3394
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a5e21d72:

    # "I've wished for that more than once in the last few months."
    "この数ヶ月、そう願ったのは一度だけじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3396
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8e367d4b:

    # hi "Let's put that aside for the time being, all right?"
    hi "とりあえずその話は置いとこうぜ、な？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3401
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e787f564:

    # rin "If you say so."
    rin "君がそう言うなら"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3403
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1fc2aff8:

    # hi "I do. So… what's wrong?"
    hi "そう言ってるだろ。それで……どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3405
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_f071e6cb:

    # hi "Sae and Nomiya were not too happy that you just ran off yesterday."
    hi "昨日お前が逃げちまったもんだから、さえさんと野宮先生はあまりいい顔してなかったぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3407
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b7034cb6:

    # hi "You left them in quite a pinch, and I suppose the teacher wants some kind of an explanation."
    hi "相当なピンチのままでほったらかしにしたからな。先生も何かしら説明を聞きたがってると思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3409
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b87a1272:

    # hi "It seemed like you just threw out everything you had worked for. And I don't get why."
    hi "お前が今までがんばってきたことを全部放り出したみたいに見えたけど。理由がわからないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3414
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bcc87ff2:

    # rin "Did I make a mistake?"
    rin "私、間違ったことをしたの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3416
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b5b2603f:

    # "My reprimanding and her flat answer go so much against the usual expectations and presumed interactions that it might just as well be somebody else talking."
    "俺の叱責と琳の平坦な答えは、普通の期待や予想される対話とあまりに逆行していて、まるで別人が会話をしているのも同然だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3418
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23734b94:

    # "Neither of us is like we used to be, this stiff, constricting feeling I get every time I look at Rin nowadays seems to be mirrored in her own behavior."
    "俺たちのどちらも、今までの俺たちらしくない。琳を見るたびに感じる、このこわばった、束縛されるような感覚が、近ごろは琳自身の立ち居振る舞いにも移っている気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3420
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_db9eab9c:

    # "I hate things that go irreparably wrong. Ever since February, I have hated them."
    "取り返しのつかないほど悪い方向に進むのは嫌だ。２月からずっとそう思ってきた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3422
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_edbaad66:

    # "What can I say?"
    "俺はなんて言えばいいんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3424
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1456a0d8:

    # "Her question is trailed by a compelling, quizzical stare that makes me sigh and frown."
    "琳はその質問の後、切実でいぶかしげなまなざしを向ける。俺はため息をつき、顔をしかめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3426
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_57d59b05:

    # "Conversations nobody wants to have are the worst."
    "誰も望まない会話というのは最悪だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3428
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8dc8cb6d:

    # hi "I don't know. I mean, it's not the end of the world but it probably was pretty stupid."
    hi "さあな。というか、この世の終わりってほどじゃないけど、かなりバカなまねだったと思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3433
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23b82067:

    # "She responds with a sigh of her own, although hers is not nearly as heavy as mine was."
    "琳はため息で答える。でも俺のほど重々しくはない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3438
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_41f678a6:

    # rin "I just couldn't do it."
    rin "どうしてもできなかったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3440
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d773584d:

    # hi "But… why? What's wrong?"
    hi "でも……なんでだよ？　なにがまずかったんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3445
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d5db3a09:

    # "A pause, a furrowed brow, a quiet voice."
    "沈黙、寄る眉根、そして静かな声。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3447
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_813fbe53:

    # rin "Let it be, Hisao."
    rin "もういいでしょ、久夫"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3449
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_db6d9338:

    # rin "I don't think I can really explain it in a way that would make sense."
    rin "納得してもらえるような説明なんてできないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3451
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_03f39121:

    # "Yeah, Rin doesn't want to have this conversation either. That may be for the better."
    "ああ、琳もこんな話はしたくないんだな。そのほうが良さそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3453
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7e09a6bb:

    # "But how rare of her, to admit that even she has some kind of limits."
    "でも琳にしては珍しいな。自分にも限界というものがあると認めるなんて。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3455
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6e18c75e:

    # "I always thought Rin was all but ignorant of her tendency to get distracted, so much that she inadvertently obfuscates everything she says."
    "俺はずっと、琳は自分の注意散漫なところを全く自覚していないと思っていた。だから無意識に自分の言ったことを何もかもぼやかしてしまうんだ、と。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3457
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3459
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_646a5472:

    # hi "You never explain {b}anything{/b} in a way that would make sense."
    hi "お前って、本当に{b}どんなことでも{/b}他人にわかるように説明しないよな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3464
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6e44563b:

    # rin "Nobody else has ever asked me to."
    rin "だって他に誰も聞いてこなかったし"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3468
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3471
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_cafeb753:

    # n "I guess that's how it is."
    n "\n\n\nそんなことだろうと思った。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3473
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_23323e1b:

    # n "But I always wanted to make sense of you, to find out who you are."
    n "でも、俺はずっとお前を理解したいと思ってた。お前がどういう奴なのか知りたかったんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3475
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_c243b672:

    # n "I still want to, can't you see?"
    n "今もそう思ってるんだ、わからないのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3477
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_eabec665:

    # n "…"
    n "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3479
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5256755c:

    # n "I know you can't."
    n "\nわからないだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3481
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6625e57c:

    # n "But I do."
    n "でもそう思ってるんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3483
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_545e50c4:

    # n "Is that why I keep this up? It pains you as much as it pains me. It's unlikely to be of any use to either."
    n "\n\n\nだから俺たちはこんなことを続けるのか？　俺もつらいけど、同じくらいお前もつらいんだ。俺たちのどちらにも役には立ちそうにない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3485
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_300fc010:

    # n "We did things and said things that can't be undone."
    n "俺たちは取り返しのつかないことを言ったり、やったりした。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3487
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5c30b55f:

    # n "It's as if… you and me being close to each other just hurts us both, but we still deliberately keep doing it."
    n "まるで……俺とお前が近くにいるだけでお互いに傷ついてしまうのに、わざとそうし続けているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3489
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_7d209e62:

    # n "Isn't that silly?"
    n "バカみたいだよな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3491
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_2c4bc0a6:

    # n "Even now, I can see how you force yourself to respond even though you owe me nothing."
    n "今でさえ、俺に義理立てることなんかなにもないのに、お前が無理に返事をしているのがわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3493
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_2e0c4c6a:

    # n "Even if it's hard to talk about things like this."
    n "こういうことを話すのは大変なのに、それでもだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3495
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_651e1241:

    # n "Why?"
    n "\nどうして？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3500
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_28de4337:

    # nvl clear
    # hi "Why is it that you paint?"
    nvl clear
    hi "お前が絵を描く理由はなんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3507
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0bb0fa31:

    # rin "I… because I don't know what else I could do."
    rin "私……だって、他に何ができるかなんてわからなかったから"

