    # "Or am I the only one who feels burdened by being myself?"
    "それとも、自分らしくあることに辛さを覚えているのは俺だけなのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3737
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_5d7bd46a:

    # hi "No thanks."
    hi "やめとくよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3739
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_213b0650:

    # hi "But still, the times when I feel that I am on the same page as you are pretty rare."
    hi "でもまあ、お前と同じ事考えてるって思えることはかなり珍しいけどな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3741
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b4eb455a:

    # hi "It feels like… there is this huge gap and sometimes you just go to the other side, and I don't… have any way to reach to you from where I am."
    hi "なんだか……俺とお前の間に深い溝があって、お前はすっと向こう側に行っちまって、俺は……俺のいるところからは絶対に手が届かない、って感じがするんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3743
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_222dda68:

    # hi "It's like you are in some completely different place at times."
    hi "時々、お前が全然違うところにいるみたいなんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3745
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_d2a3094c:

    # hi "Even though you are right here."
    hi "確かにここにいるっていうのに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3747
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_112ac131:

    # "That's right."
    "その通りだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3749
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_13d325fb:

    # "There is an insurmountable discontinuity, an imaginary glass wall that blocks comprehension from happening."
    "絶対に乗り越えられない断絶がある。理解することを妨げる、想像上のガラスの壁だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3751
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_18f58ea5:

    # "There might be such a gap between any two people, but with Rin, it feels more tangible."
    "どんな人同士の間にもそういった溝はありそうなものだけど、でも琳が相手だと、それはもっと明瞭だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3753
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_6a8ac072:

    # "Rin does not react to my thoughts, not to the ones I uttered aloud nor the ones I did not."
    "琳は俺の考えには反応を見せない。俺が声に出していったことにもそうでないことにも。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3755
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_fba2ac6a:

    # hi "It's even worse with art."
    hi "芸術だったらもっとひどいぜ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3757
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_588ba655:

    # hi "I'm not very good at art, I admit it."
    hi "俺は芸術には疎いよ、それは認める"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3759
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_9359a0b9:

    # hi "I joined the art club 'cause I thought it could be interesting."
    hi "俺が美術部に入ったのは面白そうだと思ったからなんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3761
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_07a3eee5:

    # hi "And I guess it is. I like art, I like your art too, but just like with you, I can't comprehend it."
    hi "確かに面白いと思う。俺は芸術が好きだし、お前の絵も好きだけど、お前のことと同じで、芸術は理解できない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3763
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a90459f9:

    # hi "And I'm pretty sure nobody really can."
    hi "たぶん誰にも本当の意味では理解できないんだと思う"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3768
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_63627b63:

    # "This seems to worry her slightly."
    "今のは琳をわずかに不安がらせたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3770
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_b1e4b14a:

    # rin "Do you think so?"
    rin "ほんとにそう思う？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3772
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_ec0c608c:

    # hi "Yeah. I guess that art is meant to be interpreted, not understood. That's how I'd put it."
    hi "ああ。芸術ってのは読み取るものであって、理解するものじゃないんだと思う。俺に言わせれば"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3777
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_892c793d:

    # rin "That's a sad thought."
    rin "そんな考え方、悲しいよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3779
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_63321a7e:

    # hi "I guess it might feel like one."
    hi "そうかもしれないな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3781
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_178e1309:

    # hi "Does it make you feel sad for yourself?"
    hi "それでお前自身は悲しくなるのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3786
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_0db8c15b:

    # "Rin thinks about this for a while, and then shakes her head surprisingly vehemently."
    "琳はしばらく考え込むと、驚くほど熱烈に頭を振る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3791
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_e3bbb7e3:

    # "The first thing she focuses her eyes on afterward is me."
    "そのあと、琳が初めて俺に目の焦点を合わせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3793
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_931bfb86:

    # "Both of these things make me glad, and relieved."
    "俺はその両方が嬉しくて、そして安心する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3795
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_bd15c7c3:

    # hi "That's good, isn't it? Anyway, you should go see the teacher and apologize properly."
    hi "それっていいことだろ？　とにかく、ちゃんと先生のところに行って謝ってこいよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3797
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_1f693936:

    # hi "I think he is worried about you."
    hi "先生、心配してると思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3799
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_61ea2e1f:

    # hi "Can you do that?"
    hi "できるか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3804
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_a07805c3:

    # "This time, she nods her head."
    "今度は琳はうなずく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3808
translate jp a4_rin_problems_of_self_referential_logic_8f5ac796:

    # "Only, it's not as vehement."
    "ただ、さっきのような勢いはない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3818
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0a716e6b:

    # "The hallway is empty, almost intimidating."
    "廊下には誰もいない。恐ろしくなるくらいに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3820
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1bacdced:

    # "Nomiya's 'office' is the art classroom at the other end of the third floor hallway."
    "野宮先生の『事務所』は３階の廊下の突き当たりにある美術室だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3825
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_125fc35a:

    # "Our steps echo disturbingly. The atmosphere is unlike on a normal afternoon. It feels like the school knows that nobody will be coming back for a month, too."
    "俺たちの足音が不穏に響き渡る。空気がいつもの午後のそれと違う。学校も向こう１ヶ月、誰も戻ってこないのを知っているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3827
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_dbce099b:

    # "The door is open, but not very inviting."
    "ドアは開いているけど、あまり歓迎するような気配じゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3829
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_6aff6df4:

    # hi "I'll… um, wait outside."
    hi "俺は……ええと、外で待ってるよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3842
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_6dc07af5:

    # "Nodding barely noticeably, Rin strides in without stopping, and naturally, without knocking."
    "かろうじて分かるくらいかすかにうなずくと、琳は立ち止まらずに、そして当然だけどノックもせず、大股で中に入っていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3844
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_86657f4b:

    # "Maybe that's why it takes a few seconds before I hear the teacher's voice from inside."
    "中から先生の声が聞こえるまで数秒かかったのは、多分そのせいだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3846
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_fc6734c8:

    # no "There you are!"
    no "やっと来たか！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3848
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_811c5f41:

    # rin "Hello."
    rin "どうも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3850
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_2e34d48b:

    # "A conflict arises: should I stay here or go somewhere else?"
    "衝突が始まった。ここにいるべきか、別の場所へ行くべきか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3852
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5a13c96e:

    # "I'm not sure if I even want to eavesdrop on them."
    "盗み聞きしたいのかどうかさえ、自分でもわからない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3854
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3860
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e426c925:

    # "Manners lose to curiosity, and so I stay close enough to listen in."
    "好奇心に礼儀が負け、俺は近寄って聞き耳を立てる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3862
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4a190024:

    # "Their voices echo in the hallway, but no matter."
    "２人の声は廊下まで響いてくるけど、それはともかく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3864
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a48f9e1d:

    # "There is nobody around, save for me."
    "俺を除けば、周りには誰もいない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3868
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_7c75511a:

    # no "Dear girl, what on Earth were you thinking, leaving like that on the big night?"
    no "手塚よ、いったい何を考えていたんだ、大事な夜に姿をくらますような真似をして？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3870
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ba978e60:

    # rin "I couldn't say anything."
    rin "何も言えなかったんです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3872
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_de7a30cd:

    # "Compared to Nomiya's scolding tone, Rin sounds awfully quiet and withdrawn."
    "野宮先生のきつい口調に比べると、琳の声はひどく小さく、弱々しい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3874
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_bced366c:

    # "Her words seem to drown under his."
    "その言葉は先生の声に埋もれてしまいそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3876
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c5162c6d:

    # no "I have to say, I am very disappointed in you, Tezuka."
    no "言わせてもらうが、お前には非常に失望したぞ、手塚"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3878
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e3306e7d:

    # rin "It was no good at all."
    rin "全然よくなかったです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3880
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_35f4098e:

    # no "Never mind all the things I did for you, but what about Sae? What about all the guests who wanted to meet you?"
    no "今まで私がしてやったことはいい。だがさえはどうなる？　お前に会いたがっていた客はどうなる？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3882
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f107b085:

    # rin "There was nobody. Even Hisao…"
    rin "誰もいませんでした。久夫だって……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3884
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_04098c4e:

    # no "You have embarrassed us very badly, Tezuka."
    no "お前は我々にひどい恥をかかせたんだぞ、手塚"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3886
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1ccaed51:

    # no "Reputation is what counts, surely you know that?"
    no "評判こそが一番大事なんだ、そのくらいは分かっているんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3888
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1a57d6f6:

    # rin "It's all right. I don't need it."
    rin "大丈夫です。私には必要ないです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3890
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f52bc1ca:

    # no "'Don't need!' What do you think you know?"
    no "『必要ない』だと！　知った風な口をききおって！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3892
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_94db79fe:

    # "Rin's replies only seem to agitate the teacher more, his voice rising with every sentence."
    "琳の返事は先生をいら立たせるばかりで、その声も一言ごとに大きくなっていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3894
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_3a0f219c:

    # no "The path of an artist is a thorny one, I'll tell you that! Thorny!"
    no "芸術家への道は茨の道だ、私が請け合ってやる！　茨の道だぞ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3896
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_60478bcc:

    # no "You have to see the big picture! There will be bad times and good times!"
    no "全体像を見るんだ！　うまくいく時もあればそうでない時もある！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3898
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e566c382:

    # rin "Things are like they are. It'll be all right even—"
    rin "なんだってそうです。それでもいいんです――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3900
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_254659b4:

    # no "You might now think that it's oh so wonderful and easy, but how far would you have gotten without me?"
    no "絶好調で楽ちんだったと思っているのかもしれないが、私がいなかったらどれほどのことができたというんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3902
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_acbc9b1f:

    # no "I won't always be there for you!"
    no "私とていつまでもお前のそばにいてやれるわけじゃないぞ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3904
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5eb00a09:

    # no "When you lie on the floor of your minuscule room, your rent three weeks late, your mind blank for the fourth week straight, then you will wish that you had listened to old Nomiya a bit more."
    no "狭苦しい部屋に横になって、家賃を３週間も滞納して、４週目もずっと呆然としている時、お前はこの私の言ったことをもう少し聞いておけばよかったと後悔するぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3906
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0378543b:

    # no "When you keep measuring how the shadow of your chair becomes longer over the spring because that's all your lethargy allows, maybe that's when you will start caring about your career!"
    no "春を過ぎて、あまりの無気力に椅子の影がどこまで伸びるか計り続けることしかできない、その時になって初めてお前は自分の生業というものを考えるのかもしれんな！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3908
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_f1bae754:

    # rin "That doesn't matter."
    rin "そんなの関係ないです"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3910
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4de65275:

    # no "Your resolve is not enough."
    no "その程度の覚悟で足りるものか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3912
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_42cfea3b:

    # rin "I am not a resolved person."
    rin "私は覚悟のある人間じゃないから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3914
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_29e17732:

    # no "You are not a resolved person…"
    no "覚悟のある人間じゃない、と……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3919
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_7ae46f04:

    # no "Then tell me, why… why… WHY DID WE GO THROUGH ALL THIS TROUBLE IF IT AMOUNTS TO A MOSQUITO'S SHIT?"
    no "なら教えてくれ。なぜ……なぜ……蚊のクソほどの価値しかないなら、なぜわざわざあれだけの苦労をしたというんだ！？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3921
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_edfbf6aa:

    # "Oh dear, the teacher blew a fuse."
    "やばい、先生がとうとう切れた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3923
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_56a2d361:

    # "Him yelling at Rin makes me feel bystander's guilt. If I had gone with her, maybe he wouldn't have gotten so angry."
    "先生が琳に怒鳴る声を聞いていると、傍観していることへの罪悪感がつのる。もし琳と一緒に行っていたら、先生もあそこまで怒らなかったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3925
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a5adb09f:

    # "If I had not let her run away, he wouldn't have gotten angry in the first place."
    "もしあのとき琳を引き止めていたら、そもそも先生が怒ることはなかっただろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3927
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1e75dc9d:

    # "I still could go and save her… I don't think I can."
    "今ならまだ教室に入って琳に助太刀してやれるけど……できる気がしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3929
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_713fbfe8:

    # "I was the same. I yelled at Rin too, and I'm feeling all the more embarrassed about it now."
    "俺も同じだった。俺も琳を怒鳴りつけた。今はそれが恥ずかしくて仕方がない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3931
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5687b0c3:

    # "I felt justified to vent my anger at her face just because… just because I felt it was her fault that I was so frustrated."
    "琳に怒りをぶつけるのが当然だと思ったのは、ただ……ただ俺があんなにいらだっていたのは琳のせいだと思ったからだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3933
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_35f8da37:

    # "I was no more justified than the teacher is."
    "先生にも俺にも、そんな資格なんてなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3935
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3937
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_44dea617:

    # "A terrible silence sets upon the hallway."
    "ひどい沈黙が廊下を襲う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3939
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_2c47ca41:

    # "Rin does not have anything to say to Nomiya."
    "琳は野宮先生に何も言えないでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3941
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a79943d3:

    # "Whether she has run out of answers or she knows that arguing would only make him angrier is anyone's guess."
    "答えが尽きてしまったのか、それとも反論しても先生を怒らせるだけだと分かっているのか、どちらなのかはわかりようもない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3943
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_0862d794:

    # "The teacher has nothing more to say either, it seems, or maybe he just ran out of breath."
    "先生も言うべきことはもうないみたいだ。息が切れただけかもしれないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3945
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_a51bbc4a:

    # "For a moment, I imagine the two of them just staring at each other, one full of red-hot anger, the other full of… yes, what?"
    "一瞬、２人がお互いをただ見つめ合っている様子を想像する。片や猛烈な怒りで、片や……そういえば、なんだろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3947
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_54a036f9:

    # "I can't tell how Rin feels, not before, not now."
    "俺には琳の気持ちはわからない。昔も、今も。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3949
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_4f0fb537:

    # "Teacher seems to expect Rin to say something too, but since she doesn't he finally continues in a quieter, but not less angry voice."
    "先生も琳が何か言うのを期待してるんだろうけど、琳は黙ったままなので、最後には少し静かな、しかし怒りの収まらない声で続ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3951
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_3e8f651d:

    # no "What worth is there in doing so much work if the outcome is… nothing?"
    no "あれだけの労を費やした結果がゼロなら……いったい何の意味があると言うんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3953
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_cc6452f4:

    # "Still, Rin will not say anything."
    "それでも、琳は何も言わない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3955
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_fd187c3a:

    # no "I'm sorry. I shouldn't have gotten so excited."
    no "すまない。つい興奮してしまった"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3957
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_b4229233:

    # "He does not sound sorry at all. Rather, his tone is cold and sharp, like he was spitting the words out of his mouth."
    "ぜんぜん悪いと思ってるように聞こえない。むしろ口から言葉を吐き出すかのような、冷たく鋭い響きだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3959
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_55965a48:

    # no "It seems that I was expecting too much. You are not an artist after all."
    no "期待をしすぎていたようだな。結局、お前は芸術家ではなかったということだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3961
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_927c5f46:

    # "Yeah, not sorry at all."
    "本当に、ぜんぜん悪いと思ってないな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3979
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e79fa0b3:

    # "He storms out of the club room and down the stairs without noticing me."
    "先生は部室を飛び出すと、俺に気づくことなく階段を下っていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3981
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_faf1ce19:

    # "After he is gone, I peek carefully inside the classroom."
    "先生がいなくなった後、俺は慎重に中を覗き込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3987
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ebabbe35:

    # "Rin is left standing there, in front of the teacher's desk."
    "取り残された琳は先生の机の前で突っ立っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3992
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c880ca0d:

    # rin "I couldn't say I am sorry."
    rin "ごめんなさいって言えなかった"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3994
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c43e5a6e:

    # "She says it into the humid air of the classroom, not to me."
    "俺ではなく、教室の湿った空気に向かって言う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3996
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_311ce79f:

    # "But since the room won't answer her, I will have to."
    "でも部屋は琳に答えたりしない。俺が答えないと。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:3998
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_cf06bdb3:

    # hi "That was unfair of him… He was angry, but still…"
    hi "あれはフェアじゃないよな……先生怒ってたけど、それでも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4000
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_5f883ced:

    # "I can't decide how to end my sentence. Disdaining the teacher feels like disdaining my own behavior from two days ago."
    "どう言葉を締めようか決められない。先生を見下すのは、２日前の俺の振る舞いを見下しているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4002
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_b2363998:

    # "Stupid, but correct in hindsight."
    "バカだけど、今にしてみればその通りだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4007
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_e87bad7e:

    # "Rin won't answer, staying petrified where she stands, so I walk up to her."
    "琳は答えず、その場に棒立ちになっているので、俺は琳に歩み寄る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4009
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_040a94e2:

    # "She stood up for herself. In a way. I didn't expect that."
    "琳は立ち向かって自分の意見を貫いた。ある意味、それは予想外だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4011
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_01114343:

    # "I can't determine whether it's unbecoming or not, but either way, she did it."
    "琳らしいのからしくないのか、俺には何とも言えないけど、いずれにせよ、琳はやった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4013
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_c7fc8fb0:

    # "Against me, she never did."
    "俺に対しては一度もそんなことはしなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4015
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_98782b07:

    # "I sort of wish she had, maybe I would not feel this bad then."
    "してくれたならとも思う。そうすればこんなひどい気持ちにはならなかったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4017
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_ac23e748:

    # "Lately, it really seems that I've been wishing for all kinds of things."
    "最近の俺は本当に何でもかんでも願ってるな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4019
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_79b8b7de:

    # hi "Rin?"
    hi "琳？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4024
translate jp a4_rin_measuring_shadows_1149e5d6:

    # rin "Go away."
    rin "あっち行って"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4035
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a86f8847:

    # hi "Why… what are you saying?"
    hi "なんで……何言ってるんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4040
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_328e6f5e:

    # rin "You're angry with me too, right?"
    rin "君も私に怒ってるんだ、そうでしょ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4042
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_17a09b54:

    # rin "I thought you were my friend. I thought he was, too."
    rin "君は友達だと思ってた。先生のことも"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4044
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_10398a35:

    # "Her voice is unlike I've ever heard it, it's bitter, sharp like needles, and she keeps staring pointedly at her toes."
    "琳の声はこれまで聞いたことのないようなもので、苦々しく、針のように鋭い。琳はじっとつま先を見下ろしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4046
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_33b1994b:

    # hi "I don't think it's about that."
    hi "そういうことじゃないと思うぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4048
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a68d17f2:

    # hi "He wanted you to be something you are not. And…"
    hi "先生はお前に、お前じゃない別の何かになってほしいと思ってたんだ。それで……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4053
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b76c58e4:

    # "I take a deep breath and finally catch her eyes in my own, locking our gazes."
    "俺は深く息をつくと、ようやく琳の目をとらえて、お互いに見つめ合う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4055
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8581e44e:

    # hi "…I'm sorry. I wanted us to be something else too… more than friends."
    hi "……ごめん。俺も、俺たち二人が別の何かになれたらと思ってた……もっと、友達以上の何かに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4057
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_af8ee4ad:

    # hi "Maybe that's why I couldn't contain myself and became so frustrated, just like the teacher did."
    hi "だから俺は自分を抑えられなくてあんなにイライラしてたのかもな、先生と同じように"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4062
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6e9f3c4c:

    # rin "What more? There is nothing more to me than me, that's all I am. I don't understand that."
    rin "何がもっとなの？　私にはこれ以上の私はないよ、私はこれで全部。わけわかんないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4064
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_2f5449fc:

    # "Well… the answer should be obvious, right?"
    "ああ……答えはわかりきってる、そうだろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4066
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_eb839590:

    # "I remember myself, thinking of the purpose of friendship. To put up with everything and anything, to be there for your friend."
    "友情の意義を考えていたときのことを思い出す。友達を支えてやるために、どんなことでも全て我慢する、ということを。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4068
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_aed08c9f:

    # "Did I fail as a friend, thinking it could be a stepping stone for something else?"
    "友情が別のものへの足がかりになりうると考えていた俺は、友達として失格だったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4070
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d7849ebe:

    # "Maybe because of those thoughts, I didn't manage to put up with things, to keep it together."
    "そんな考えがあったから、俺は我慢を続けることが、友情をつなぎ止めることができなかったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4072
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d8455860:

    # "As outrageous as Rin is and was, I shouldn't have let myself get caught into that, especially when I started feeling the way I did towards her."
    "今も昔もこんなに琳は常識外れだけど、俺自身がそれに腹を立ててはいけなかった。琳相手にあんな感情を抱き始めていたならなおさらだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4074
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_451e526f:

    # "So, did I fail?"
    "で、俺は失格なのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4076
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3e4b8c69:

    # "That's what her eyes seem to ask."
    "琳の目はそう問いかけているように見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4078
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4080
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4edfc2ce:

    # hi "I'm sorry, Rin."
    hi "ごめんな、琳"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4082
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_77849431:

    # hi "I might not be able to be your friend."
    hi "俺はお前の友達にはなれないかもしれない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4084
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_fb09bfa5:

    # hi "I don't think I could ever be a good friend to you."
    hi "俺は絶対に、お前の親友ではいられないと思う"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4086
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_45f8c1f5:

    # "I say these things because they are true, not because one of us would like to hear them."
    "こんなことを口にするのは、それを俺たちのどちらかが聞きたいからじゃなくて、それが本当のことだからだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4088
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_08731ab3:

    # "But they are something that must be said."
    "でも、これは伝えなければいけないことだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4090
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_71028a93:

    # "The finality of my words creates a shaking silence, for what could either of us add to that?"
    "俺の決定的な言葉は、身震いするような沈黙を生む。なぜって、それ以上何を付け加えることがあるだろう？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4092
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4097
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_898bc629:

    # rin "Why? Why does all this happen?"
    rin "どうして？　どうしてこうなっちゃうの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4102
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0015c967:

    # rin "People are doing things I don't ask for and don't want and everyone keeps getting angry at me, I have no idea what is going on any more and can't stop feeling like I want to run away from everything…"
    rin "みんな頼んでもないのに、して欲しくもないことして、みんな私に怒ってて、もう何がどうなってるのか全然わからなくて、何もかもから逃げ出したい気持ちになるのを抑えられなくて……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4107
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8a8d11ae:

    # "She shuts her eyes tight and breathes out deeply, calmly."
    "琳は目をぎゅっと閉じると、深く、静かに息をつく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4112
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_9e0b5f21:

    # "When the eyelids open, all I can see is dark green desperation."
    "まぶたが開くと、そこに見えるのは深緑色の絶望だけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4114
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f56118e1:

    # rin "{b}I have no idea what's wrong with me!{/b}"
    rin "{b}私の何がおかしいのかわかんないよ！{/b}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4116
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a9fa7df7:

    # "Her frenetic outburst stupefies me for a moment, and for a heartbeat we just gaze into each other's face."
    "琳の狂乱した叫びは俺を一瞬ぼうぜんとさせる。そして一瞬の間、俺たちはお互いの顔を見つめ合う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4118
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6dd64e05:

    # "Seeing her confused eyes desperately looking for answers from mine only makes me sad, because I know I have none."
    "琳の困惑した目は、その答えを必死に俺の目に求めているけど、それを見て俺は悲しくなるだけだ。俺に答えられないことはわかっているから。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4120
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6bb4f611:

    # hi "I don't know either."
    hi "俺にもわからないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4122
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d7caf8fa:

    # hi "But you know, you yourself said that things are not right nor wrong."
    hi "でもな、どんなことだって正しくも間違ってもないって言ったのはお前だぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4124
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_400d49b1:

    # hi "They just are."
    hi "そういうものなんだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4126
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_02a828c3:

    # hi "You either accept them, work to change them or give up."
    hi "それを受け入れるか、頑張って変えていくか、諦めるしかないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4128
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c0932a9f:

    # hi "It's not that I hate you, or that teacher Nomiya does."
    hi "お前のことが嫌いなわけじゃないぞ。先生だってそうだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4130
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8aaa5d46:

    # hi "I just… think that I am the kind of person who gives up when he feels he can't go on."
    hi "俺はただ……もうだめだと思ったらそこで諦めちまうような人間なんだろうな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4132
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3c2a5195:

    # hi "And even if you hate it, this… this is… how things are."
    hi "もしそういうのが嫌だとしても、これが……つまり……現実なんだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4134
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_29d2ca31:

    # "I'm saying pretty cruel things but I can't stop myself, the words keep rolling off my tongue with slow, hard certainty."
    "俺はひどく残酷なことを言っているけど、自分でも止められない。言葉が舌からゆっくりと、動かしがたい確かさで転がり出る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4139
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_9cdb683d:

    # "I can see them hitting Rin almost like physical blows."
    "それがまるで本物の打撃のように、琳にぶつかるのがわかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4141
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f8ae645e:

    # "As the wetness gathers into the corners of her eyes, they are still wide with the shock of rejection."
    "その目の隅に水がわき上がるけど、拒絶されたショックで目は大きく開いたままだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4146
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ee8600d6:

    # "As the tears start rolling down her pale cheeks, she does nothing to stop them."
    "青白い肌に涙がこぼれ始めても、琳はそれを止めようとしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4148
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_11c5de7b:

    # "As they fall down on the floor one by one, she stands still, staring at me with a gaze full of hollow disbelief."
    "涙が一つ一つ、床にまで落ちていく間、琳は立ち尽くしたまま、うつろな不信感に満ちた目で俺を見つめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4150
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_879b98dc:

    # rin "…"
    rin "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4152
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_1e44f061:

    # "But reality catches up."
    "でもやがて現実が追いついてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4162
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d303f825:

    # "Rin slumps forward as if she was deflating, and buries her face as deep in my shirt as she can."
    "琳はしぼんでしまうかのように前に倒れこむと、俺のシャツに深々と顔をうずめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4164
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_05d6787e:

    # "Rin is heavy and featherlight when I support her weight."
    "俺が支えてやると、その体は重く、羽のように軽い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4166
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4eaad8de:

    # "She doesn't really sob or bawl, just leans against me, letting her tears burn through my shirt into the skin underneath."
    "琳は泣きじゃくりも、喚きもしない。ただ俺に寄りかかり、その熱い涙をシャツ越しに下の肌まで染み込ませる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4168
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_20566d5f:

    # "And I let her, bringing my hand around her shoulders in a clumsy hug that does no good to comfort her."
    "そして俺も琳のなすがままにさせ、手をその肩に回して、ぎこちなく抱きしめる。でも琳をなだめる役にはまるで立っていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4170
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_71466c97:

    # "I can feel Rin's vertebrae against my fingertips, like hard and jagged reminders of how messed up things are."
    "指先に琳の背骨を感じる。その堅いぎざぎざがこの状況の救いのなさを思い起こさせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4172
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e97643b3:

    # "Her slim shoulder quivering against my palm is a pitiable sight, and the hopelessness of being part of the cause for Rin's sadness keeps shredding my heart."
    "俺の手に触れる、その華奢な肩が震えているのは見ていてかわいそうだ。自分自身が琳の悲しみの理由の一部だったという絶望が、俺の心をずたずたにする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4176
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4179
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d368b86c:

    # n "{vspace=120}To make a girl cry is the most despicable thing to do."
    n "\n\n\n\n女の子を泣かせるのは一番卑劣な行いだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4181
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_aba60d25:

    # n "{vspace=30}Even Rin. Especially Rin."
    n "\nそれが琳であっても。琳だからこそ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4183
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4a1d6033:

    # n "{vspace=30}Behind that veil of aloofness, Rin is just a human being too."
    n "\n超然としているその裏では、琳もひとりの人間だったんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4185
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_cad5f2ab:

    # n "Just as confused, scared and lost as any of us is."
    n "戸惑い、恐れ、途方に暮れていた。他の人と同じように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4187
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_687c3d91:

    # n "Most of the time it seems that there is no rhyme or reason for what Rin does and says, but for once, I think I really understand how she feels."
    n "琳の行動や言葉には大抵の場合、道理も分別もないと思っていた。でも今だけは、琳の気持ちが本当に理解できる気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4189
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b4ed80bb:

    # n "{vspace=60}But no words can express it, and no words can make it better."
    n "\n\nでもそれを説明できる言葉も、慰める言葉も存在しない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4193
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4202
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d0080779:

    # n "{vspace=150}So wordless we stay, quietly waiting for her tears to run out."
    n "\n\n\n\n\nだから、俺たちは言葉もなく立ち尽くし、静かに涙が涸れるのを待っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4204
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_024094a7:

    # n "Time passes agonizingly slowly, even the lazy specks of dust floating in the air seem to pause into a standstill."
    n "時間が痛いほどゆっくりと過ぎていく。緩慢に空気中を漂うほこりの小片さえ、静止しているかのように見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4206
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_2254b4a9:

    # n "The obligatory wall clock is ticking distractingly from above the door."
    n "お定まりの壁掛け時計がドアの上からカチカチと鳴り、気分をかき乱す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4208
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e7e72875:

    # n "I decide against counting the seconds, because it would make them feel longer."
    n "俺は秒数を数えることにする。そうすればもっと時間を長く感じられる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4210
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_16d51601:

    # n "{vspace=60}…"
    n "\n\n……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4215
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4220
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b60b0732:

    # "Eventually Rin stirs a little and still smothering herself against my chest, mutters into my shirt."
    "やがて琳は少し体を動かし、まだ俺の胸に顔を押しつけたまま、シャツに向かってつぶやく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4222
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ed876ef2:

    # rin "Let me be here for a while."
    rin "もう少しここにいさせて"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4227
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_351c6e6c:

    # rin "Please, Hisao."
    rin "お願い、久夫"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4229
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a31911cf:

    # rin "Just give me a little while."
    rin "少しだけでいいから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4231
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6fef3343:

    # "A soothing deluge spreads into my consciousness, the knowledge that while being here for Rin is all I can do for her, that's all she wants right now, even after all we've gone through."
    "心地よいなにかが俺の意識に押し寄せてくる。あれだけいろんなことがあった後でさえ、俺には琳をここにいさせてやることしかできないけど、琳が今望んでいることはそれだけだ、という気づきが。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4233
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "ああ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4235
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3af3c03c:

    # "So she stays there."
    "かくして、琳はそこにとどまる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4237
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f04f3643:

    # "But I still can't bring myself to draw her closer so I could embrace her properly."
    "それでも俺は、きちんと琳を抱きしめるためにその身を引き寄せることができずにいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4239
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_93c1815a:

    # "It's because doing it would just make me so sad that I don't know if I could bear it."
    "そうしたらあまりに悲しくなってしまうに違いなくて、耐えられる自信がなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4243
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4246
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_2b137976:

    # n "{vspace=60}The realization that we might never really be able to become what we want to be for the other crystallizes into my mind as a diamond-hard enlightenment."
    n "\n\n俺たちは決して、相手のためにと自分が望んでいるような存在にはなれないかもしれない。そんな実感がダイヤモンドのように硬い悟りへと結晶化する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4248
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_dc129c07:

    # n "A pang surges through my heart like an electric shock."
    n "痛みが電気ショックのように心を突き抜ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4250
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_1ea11879:

    # n "It's painful."
    n "痛い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4252
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0804e70b:

    # n "This clarity… hurts."
    n "この確かさが……痛い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4254
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ecb7b8b8:

    # n "What can we be for each other? What meaning is there for us to desperately cling to each other even though it seems so futile?"
    n "俺たちはお互いにとってどんな存在になれるだろう？　どうしようもなく意味がなさそうなのに、必死になってお互いにしがみつくことに何の意味がある？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4256
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_81c3655e:

    # n "What should I say to Rin? How can I make her feel better?"
    n "琳になんて言えばいい？　琳を慰めるにはどうすればいい？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4258
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0493a82f:

    # n "I do not know any of those things, and I fear knowing them would only hurt more."
    n "俺には一つもわかりはしないし、恐らく理解していたとしてもさらに痛みをもたらすだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4260
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f8b35533:

    # n "Forcefully, I push all of that out of my mind because I don't want to be thinking of hurtful truths."
    n "この痛ましい事実を考えたくなくて、無理やり心を空っぽにする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4262
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3a4b7b00:

    # n "My thoughts calm down soon enough, the sadness disperses until all that is left is me and Rin and the tender feeling of her warmth and softness against my chest."
    n "思考はすぐに落ち着く。悲しみは散っていき、俺と琳、そして胸に当たる繊細な暖かさと柔らかさだけが残る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4264
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d938d1c3:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}When did I fall in love with her?"
    nvl clear
    n "\n俺はいつ琳のことを好きになったんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4268
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_64f7d26f:

    # n "I can't remember, but I'm certain it was way before the warm touch of her lips on my own, on that orange-colored afternoon when she was sick with cold and I went to see her because of unclear reasons."
    n "思い出せないけど、あのオレンジ色の午後、風邪を引いた琳をはっきりしない理由で見舞いに行ったときの、あの温かいくちびるの感触よりずっと前だったというのは確かだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4270
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6f5c9eeb:

    # n "Her carefree attitude, the air of otherness around her, all the things that make Rin herself… those things captured me with irresistible force."
    n "琳の気ままな態度、琳を取り巻く異質な雰囲気、琳を琳たらしめるすべてのもの……それらが圧倒的な力で俺をとらえた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4272
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3238220f:

    # n "The way she could take in anything and everything giving it only the value she herself placed, weighing all things fairly and without prejudice, seeing the world as she wanted."
    n "琳がありとあらゆるものを受け入れ、自分がそこに認めた価値だけを与え、あらゆるものを公平に偏見なく比較し、自分の望み通りに世界を見る、そのやり方。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4274
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_31a9f0ec:

    # n "This is something I could never do, and Rin was probably more of a muse to me than anything ever was to her."
    n "それは俺には決してできないことだ。俺にとっての琳はたぶん、琳にとってのどんなものよりも、強くインスピレーションを与えてくれる存在だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4276
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_cd935f1e:

    # n "She seemed so free to me, truly a free spirit. While I, constantly worrying about everything, seemed so inhibited that it was almost embarrassing."
    n "琳はあまりにも自由に見えた。まさに自由な精神だった。その一方で、あらゆることを絶えず不安がっている俺は、恥ずかしくなるくらい引っ込み思案に見えていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4278
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0e32f4d7:

    # n "Maybe that's why I latched so tightly on to Rin, trying to get inside her world that was so different from my own bleak life."
    n "だから俺は琳に強くしがみついたんだろう。俺のどんよりとした人生とはあまりに違う、琳の世界に入り込もうとして。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4280
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e5657d2b:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}Before I noticed it, that irresistible force had pulled me dangerously close to her, but it turned out to be way too alien for me."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n気づかないうちに、あの抗いようのない力が俺を危険なほど近くに琳に引きつけたけど、でも結局、それは俺にとって異質すぎるものだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4284
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_792d39a9:

    # n "And I had forgotten Newton, of all things."
    n "そして俺はよりによって、ニュートンの法則も忘れていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4286
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_23d2f7d9:

    # n "The gravitational force is inversely proportional to the square of the distance between the objects…"
    n "引力は物体間の距離の二乗に反比例する……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4288
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e04bb72e:

    # n "So if two people feel something for each other…"
    n "じゃあ、２人の人間がお互いに感情を抱いていたら……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4290
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ceccb846:

    # n "Heh."
    n "へっ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4292
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_770c0e91:

    # n "Even though feelings are not governed by the constants of the universe, I can't help thinking that for some time now I've been a satellite to Rin's brightly shining planet."
    n "感情は宇宙の法則に支配されていないというのに、俺はずいぶん前から琳という明るく輝く星の衛星になっていたんだと思わずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4294
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6e1b8abb:

    # n "{vspace=30}Planet Rin."
    n "\n惑星琳。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4296
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c32b9b24:

    # n "{vspace=30}The thought makes me almost laugh, she really does seem to be from another planet at times, minus green skin and possibly some tentacles."
    n "\nそんなことを考えて笑ってしまいそうになる。確かに、琳は本当に別の星から来たように思えることがある。緑の肌と触手はないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4301
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4306
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_5955a6a7:

    # "Perhaps because of my stifled laughter, Rin pulls away and I let her go, feeling the cold when her warmth goes away, and slight embarrassment for letting my thoughts run wild like that."
    "俺の抑えた笑いのせいだろうか、琳は体を引き離し、俺もそれを止めない。琳のぬくもりが消えたあとの冷たさと、あんな荒唐無稽な考えをめぐらせたことにちょっとした恥ずかしさを感じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4308
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_9a30057f:

    # "I credit that as Rin being a bad influence on me, while being glad at the same time that she can't read thoughts for real."
    "琳に悪影響を受けたせいだということにする。でも同時に、琳が実際には人の心を読めなくてよかった思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4310
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_19219675:

    # "Rin's bitter tears have dried up, and she looks a little more like herself again."
    "琳の苦い涙は涸れて、少しは琳らしい様子になる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4315
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_12e51051:

    # "The lost look in her eyes is still there though. Her gaze wanders around restlessly before stopping at me."
    "それでも途方に暮れた表情はまだ残っている。琳の視線は落ち着きなくあたりをさまよい、そして俺に留まる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4317
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_adacdb45:

    # rin "What happened just now?"
    rin "今のはなんだったの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4319
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0223cbca:

    # rin "Can you tell me?"
    rin "教えてくれる？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4321
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_87c4a6de:

    # hi "What? What do you mean?"
    hi "はあ？　どういう意味だよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4326
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a8947010:

    # rin "I cried."
    rin "私、泣いてた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4328
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ad8f6622:

    # "She says that hesitantly, as if not believing it herself."
    "自分でも信じられないかのように、おずおずという。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4330
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8a2b55c1:

    # hi "Yes…"
    hi "そうだな……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4332
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4334
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_cfc1f971:

    # "She keeps staring at me, as if pleading guidance so that she wouldn't have to feel so lost."
    "琳はこの深い戸惑いを感じずに済むような導きを請うかのように、俺を見つめ続ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4336
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_3:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4341
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d66e33b2:

    # rin "Why?"
    rin "どうして？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4343
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_349e3329:

    # hi "You were sad."
    hi "悲しかったんだろ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4345
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3f88c33e:

    # hi "Is that what you want me to say? But isn't that obvious?"
    hi "そう言ってほしいのか？　でもそんなのわかりきってるだろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4350
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_be7c1a33:

    # rin "I don't know. It feels weird to cry."
    rin "わからない。泣くのって変な感じ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4352
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_bf4cb129:

    # hi "What? I don't believe it. I mean, everyone does that. It's nor—"
    hi "なんだそれ？　そんなわけないだろ。というか、誰でもすることだぞ。それがふつ――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4354
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_52d15ee0:

    # "I bite my tongue before I finish my argument about normality."
    "『普通』と言い終わる前に俺は言葉を飲み込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4356
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_bf6a1b2a:

    # "Norms do not apply to the person I'm talking to."
    "今俺が話しかけている人物には、そういう基準は当てはまらない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4361
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_db33f92d:

    # rin "It always felt so wrong, different from what is in me. Like I couldn't really tell what I felt."
    rin "こんなのおかしいってずっと思ってたんだ、私の中にあるものと違うって。自分がどんな風に感じてるのかちゃんと説明できない、っていうか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4363
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8bf039d1:

    # rin "So I started thinking that maybe I don't know what I'm feeling. Maybe it's me who is wrong—"
    rin "だから、もしかしたら私は自分の感じてることがわからないんじゃないかって思い始めた。おかしいのは私自身なんじゃないかって――"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4365
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f27b9343:

    # rin "I thought those kinds of things."
    rin "そんなことを考えてた"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4370
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c406ac59:

    # rin "I thought… that painting was enough because it felt that I did at least that right."
    rin "私……絵を描くだけで十分だと思ってた。少なくともそれだけはうまくできると思えたから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4372
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4b28f38d:

    # rin "That all that is inside me could become a picture if I tried really hard. And it could."
    rin "頑張れば私の中にあるものはみんな絵にできるって思ってた。実際にできてたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4374
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8c7a520e:

    # rin "But it doesn't feel like it's enough any more. Because if nobody else can see that, I will still be alone."
    rin "でも、もうそれだけじゃ足りなくなってる。だって私以外の誰にも見ることができないなら、私はやっぱりひとりぼっちだから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4379
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b6c80e2a:

    # rin "Was it wrong to try? Everyone got really angry at me for that."
    rin "挑戦したのは間違いだったの？　あのせいでみんなすごく怒ってたから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4383
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8095eb63:

    # "I've rarely heard Rin say this much at once before."
    "琳が一度にこんなにしゃべるのはほとんど見たことがない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4385
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_29fdde40:

    # "Once she finishes, she simply shuts up, looking so neutral that it's hard to believe she just said what she did."
    "しゃべり終えると、琳はただ口を閉じる。その様子はあまりに当たり障りがなくて、たった今まであんなことをしゃべっていたのが信じがたい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4387
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a444f39f:

    # "I don't know what to think."
    "なんて考えればいいのかわからない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4389
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4391
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d23c6534:

    # "Rin was desperate for someone to look at her paintings, and somehow see right through them into her soul, to understand her feelings…"
    "琳は誰かに自分が描いた絵を見てほしいと、それを通じてどうにかして自分の本質を見抜いてほしい、気持ちを理解してほしいと思って必死になっていた……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4393
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_953b2b5c:

    # "Because… she felt she could not express them in any other way?"
    "それは……それ以外の方法では表現できないと思っていたから、なのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4395
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c0ba05f9:

    # "How can one say whether that is right or wrong?"
    "それが正しいとか間違ってるなんて、誰が言えるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4397
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_dd6ad7cf:

    # "Could it be that all this time she's been trying to reach out to me like I've tried to reach out to her?"
    "俺が琳に手を差し伸べようと努力していたように、もしかして琳も今までずっと俺に手を差し伸べようとしていたのだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4399
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4401
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_04c6ce66:

    # "I sit down on a desk to think, and to rest my legs that kept us both standing for a long while."
    "俺は考えるために、そして長いこと立ちっぱなしだった足を休めるために、机に腰掛ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4405
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_2c896449:

    # hi "You know, when I read a good book or look at a starry sky or whatever, sometimes I too feel something… profound, like a… shoot, I don't know how to describe it."
    hi "あのさ、面白い本を読むとか星空を眺めるとかしたときにさ、こう……深いものを感じるんだ。例えば……ああもう、なんて言ったらいいんだろう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4407
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6a9a2fd2:

    # hi "But the instant I try to put it into words I feel that I lose something, it doesn't feel as real, as true as it did inside my head."
    hi "だけど言葉にしようとした瞬間、何かが失われる気がするんだ。頭の中で思っていたのに比べて、リアルさとか正確さがなくなってしまうみたいな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4409
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_48a460c2:

    # hi "It feels a bit phony. Damn, even what I just said felt phony."
    hi "なんか偽物っぽい感じがするんだ。まったく、今言ったこともなんだか偽物っぽいな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4411
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e682e6a2:

    # "I offer a smile that is meant to be between funny and self-deprecating, but Rin doesn't react."
    "俺はおかしいのと、自嘲の中間くらいの意味で笑みを浮かべるけど、琳は反応を見せない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4413
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b054bfeb:

    # hi "Anyway…"
    hi "まあとにかく……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4415
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_107c4e75:

    # hi "It might be that nobody can ever express their true feelings so that others understand."
    hi "自分の本当の気持ちを他人にわかってもらえるように表現することなんて、誰にもできないのかもしれないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4417
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_9b1b6d9c:

    # hi "Reality has no chance of living up to what someone has inside their head."
    hi "現実なんて、人が頭の中で考えてることには絶対に比べようがないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4419
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6a9bf8c7:

    # hi "Nothing can match that. Not even your paintings, except maybe for you."
    hi "比べられるものなんてあるわけがない。お前の絵だってそうだ。お前にとっては違うのかもしれないけど"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4421
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_34fe76fc:

    # hi "But I suppose you can't keep everything inside, you'd explode for real then."
    hi "でも、何もかも頭の中にしまっておけるわけじゃないよな。そんなことしたら本当に爆発しちまう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4423
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ee6be804:

    # hi "What I'm trying to say is… I don't think it's wrong to express your feelings, even if you use painting as your conduit."
    hi "俺が言いたいのはさ……自分の気持ちを表現するのは間違ってるとは思わないってことさ。絵をその手段にしたとしても"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4425
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ef735d30:

    # hi "You just can't expect people to understand you any better than they would if you did it any other way."
    hi "ただ、それ以外の方法で表現するよりも、他の人によく理解してもらえるなんて期待はしない方がいい、ってだけだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4427
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8a82649e:

    # hi "In fact, you can't expect people to understand you at all."
    hi "というか、そもそも人に理解してもらうなんて無理だよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4429
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_02f41c2d:

    # hi "It's because everything is so subjective. You see the world the way you do, but it's different from everyone else."
    hi "物事はなんでもすごく主観的だからさ。お前はお前の見方で世界を見るけど、それは他の人の見方とは違うんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4434
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6448d5be:

    # rin "But isn't that terrible?"
    rin "でも、そんなのってひどいよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4436
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d7aeaf20:

    # hi "I guess it is, in a way."
    hi "そうかもな、ある意味では"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4438
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_6:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4443
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3e9cf840:

    # "She frowns, looking probably as stricken as she can. Which is not much, but it's enough for me to understand that Rin is not particularly happy."
    "琳はできるだけ打ちひしがれたように顔をしかめる。それでもそれほどじゃないけど、琳があまりいい気分でないのを理解するのには十分だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4445
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e87bd7d2:

    # rin "I think it might make me sad after all."
    rin "そんなの、やっぱり悲しくなっちゃうな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4447
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6845161a:

    # hi "Yeah. I know."
    hi "ああ、そうだろうな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4449
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6c4db884:

    # hi "I wish I could do something to help it."
    hi "俺にできることがあればよかったんだけど"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4451
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_413175ba:

    # "I don't think I sound bitter, even though I am, a little."
    "苦々しくは聞こえないよう言ったつもりだけど、俺自身は少しだけ苦い思いをしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4453
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8bee9134:

    # "This is my problem. I cannot be what Rin wants for her. And for the same reason, she can't do the same for me either."
    "これは俺の問題だ。俺は琳の望むようにはなれない。同じ理由で、琳も俺の望むようにはなれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4455
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_7:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4460
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3b349d31:

    # "She makes a difficult face, carefully trying to pick the words she wants to say."
    "琳は難しい表情をすると、慎重に言葉を選んでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4462
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d42dc0de:

    # "So Rin has times when it's hard to say anything, too."
    "琳にも何かを口にするのが難しいときがあるんだな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4467
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_87c9fe2f:

    # rin "It can't be helped, I think."
    rin "しかたないんだろうね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4472
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_99177fda:

    # rin "…but… if you say that…"
    rin "……でも……君が言うなら……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4477
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_dd4a67b1:

    # rin "It makes me feel a little better."
    rin "少しは気が晴れるかな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4479
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ce617998_8:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4481
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_019de7b4:

    # "It's funny how some seemingly irrelevant things are the most significant ones at times like this."
    "こういうとき、一見どうでもいいようなことが一番大事なことだったりするのがおかしい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4483
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a64f84b7:

    # "Like how Rin's voice is very very small, barely audible when she says that."
    "今の琳の声がとても小さくて、かろうじて聞き取れるくらいだったこととか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4485
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a2c417aa:

    # "And how even her short bangs can cover her eyes when she looks downwards."
    "琳が下を向くと、その短い前髪が目を覆ってしまうこととか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4490
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_5751c244:

    # "And how they can't cover the deep red color rising on her cheeks and all the way to the tips of her ears."
    "そして、それが琳の頬から耳の先まで真っ赤に染まっているのを隠せていないこととか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4492
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_59a25684:

    # "They turn into a very interesting shade of red."
    "とても興味深い、濃い赤に染まっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4494
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_549bdf94:

    # "A deafening silence follows."
    "水を打ったような静けさが後に続く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4496
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_3d3c20fc:

    # "It's very awkward, as if I saw something that wasn't meant to be seen, even if it wasn't on purpose."
    "見てはいけないものを見てしまったみたいで、かなり気まずい。わざと見たわけじゃないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4498
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c6c92ca9:

    # "I don't know what to say to that, but I keep feeling like I should know."
    "何と言ってやればいいのか分からない。でも分かっていなきゃいけないはずだという気がしてならない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4500
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c0e8f418:

    # "She doesn't either."
    "琳もわかってはいない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4502
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_1038150c:

    # "Still, it feels like there is no momentum to lose even if we keep silent."
    "それでも、こうして黙り込んでいても、失われるような勢いはない気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4504
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_52d28473:

    # "Like we have some weird, wordless connection that would hold even so."
    "そんな状況であっても切れることのない、奇妙な無言の関係で俺たちがつながっているかのように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4509
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_557cc958:

    # "Rin keeps shifting her weight from one foot to the other restlessly, looking everywhere around the room except at me."
    "琳はしきりに体重を足から足へ移動させながら、部屋中を見回している。俺を除いて。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4511
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0a7e78aa:

    # "She is the one who finally breaks the spell."
    "最後にこの空気を破るのは彼女だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4516
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0b2a8ec0:

    # rin "Can we go? I don't want to stay here."
    rin "いこっか？　もうここにはいたくないや"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4518
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_1f756dac:

    # hi "Oh, yeah, of course. Where?"
    hi "ああ、そうか、そうだよな。どこに行く？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4520
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_53ce0290:

    # "My reply is covering my nervousness as badly as her question is covering hers."
    "俺の返事も琳の提案と同じくらいに、緊張を隠し切れていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4525
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0218adc5:

    # rin "You can go wherever you like. I want to sleep. I haven't really slept for a few weeks."
    rin "好きなとこに行っていいよ。私、寝たいんだ。もう何週間も満足に寝られてなかったから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4530
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_73997863:

    # rin "It feels like there is a flock of light blue butterflies inside my head. It makes it hard to think properly."
    rin "頭のなかでライトブルーの蝶々がたくさん飛んでるみたいなんだ。だからうまく考えられなくてさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4535
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_b2ffe712:

    # rin "The kind that you think is too blue to really exist, like Emi's panties this morning."
    rin "そこまで明るいブルーの蝶なんて存在しないと思うけどね、今朝の笑美のパンツみたいに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4561
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_476897b1:

    # "She shakes her head, and I almost expect a couple of ultramarine-colored Morphos to pop out of her ears."
    "琳が頭を振ると、俺はウルトラマリン色の蝶が琳の耳から飛び出してくるんじゃないかと身構える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4566
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_1ed49f2d:

    # "A small smile tugs upwards the corners of her mouth."
    "小さな笑みが琳の口元を引っ張りあげる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4568
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_2350ff9c:

    # rin "That reminds me. The blue, not the panties."
    rin "それで思い出した。青のことだよ、パンツじゃなくて"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4573
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_38a3db9d:

    # rin "The word for a flock of butterflies is a swarm. I looked it up."
    rin "たくさんの蝶は『群れ』って言うんだね。私、調べたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4575
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4ed50446:

    # "That makes my eyebrow rise into a questioning arch."
    "それを聞いて、疑問で俺の眉はつり上がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4577
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e18b1573:

    # hi "Why don't you use it then?"
    hi "じゃあ、どうしてそう言わないんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4582
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_dd415c81:

    # rin "I like the other word better."
    rin "他の言い方のほうがいいんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4584
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_28e0f0ee:

    # "Why look it up in the first place, then?"
    "じゃあ、どうしてわざわざ調べたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4586
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8fa37f5c:

    # hi "Then you should use it, right?"
    hi "じゃあそう言えばいいだろ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4591
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_0a07eb38:

    # "She nods and falls silent, her gaze escaping mine to the side, attracted by the dark orange sunlight refracting from the windows."
    "琳はうなずいて口を閉ざす。俺と向き合っていたその視線は、窓越しに屈折する濃いオレンジ色の日差しに引っ張られて脇にそれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4593
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4ff98111:

    # "We stay like that for a little while: me silently looking at her silently looking out of the window."
    "そのまましばらく、俺たちはそうしている。琳が窓の外を黙って見ているのを、俺が黙って見ている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4595
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a3c26168:

    # hi "Hey… you all right now?"
    hi "おい……大丈夫かよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4600
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_cfdd5168:

    # "She glances at me from the corner of her eye, looking wistful again. The sunlight's reflection doesn't betray any more of her inner feelings."
    "琳は目の端で、また何か言いたげに俺を見る。反射する日の光も、それ以上琳の本音を明らかにはしない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4602
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_5e2df80d:

    # rin "I'll need to think about that."
    rin "それは考えないといけないね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4604
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_e5b3dad1:

    # "I want to continue this conversation, grasping at those straws that she finally revealed to even exist."
    "ついに琳がさらけ出した、存在さえ知らなかったこの手がかりにすがる思いで、この会話を続けたいと願う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4609
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_4b4035a8:

    # "But Rin is looking out of the window so absentmindedly that I know she won't be responsive in any way that would make sense."
    "だけど琳は上の空で窓の外を見ていて、いずれにせよ意味のある返事をしそうにないのはわかりきっている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4611
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_029ac659:

    # "It's like some kind of defense mechanism of hers, to avoid being sensible."
    "これは琳の防御機構みたいなものだ。筋が通った思考を避けるための。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4613
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d2c707f8:

    # "Her mind is like a butterfly in itself, always fluttering somewhere away whenever it's stirred."
    "琳の心はそれ自体が蝶のようで、高揚したときはいつもどこかを飛び回っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4615
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_8e04dc58:

    # "Just when I thought I could see behind her veil, she jumps out of my reach again."
    "琳のベールの裏側が見えたと思ったとたんに、琳は俺の手の届くところから飛び出してしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4617
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_f7df2706:

    # "Maybe that's just how Rin is."
    "これが琳なんだろうな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4619
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_84b3b28c:

    # "Maybe that's something I should just accept to get some peace of mind."
    "俺が安心できるようになるには、とにかくこれを受け入れるべきなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4621
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "わかった"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4623
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_5ff982ec:

    # hi "I'll walk you back to the dorms then."
    hi "じゃあ部屋まで送るよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4628
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_a0d0eacd:

    # rin "Thanks."
    rin "ありがと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4633
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_d88922f3:

    # rin "Really."
    rin "ほんとに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4640
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6c3b0809:

    # "The empty hallways of the school devoid of its students feel very lonely."
    "生徒の姿がない、無人の学校の廊下はとても寂しげだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4642
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6000513c:

    # "Less than one hour after the summer vacation began, the building seems to be deserted, and all that intrudes on the stillness of the hallways are our footsteps."
    "夏休みが始まって一時間も経ってないのに、建物は打ち捨てられたように見える。この静けさに割って入るのは俺たちの足音だけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4644
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_6905c3de:

    # "The change is sudden, but it shows how the building is just an empty shell, dead without its students and teachers."
    "この変化は突然だけど、それは生徒と先生のいない学校が、死に絶えた空っぽの殻でしかないことを表している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4646
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_adbfa89c:

    # "It's as though the school has become a private world for only the two of us, a desolate place filled with silence and chalk dust."
    "まるで学校が、荒れ果てて静寂とチョークの粉で満たされた、俺たち２人だけのプライベートな世界になったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4652
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_28b47659:

    # rin "I think I have to change."
    rin "私も変わらないといけないね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4654
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_c8a91802:

    # "She says it out of the blue while we walk down the staircase from the third floor, still managing to feel like she is mirroring what I was thinking just before."
    "３階の階段を降りながら、琳は出し抜けに言う。俺がついこの間考えていたことを正確に繰り返している気がする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4656
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_72471f0d:

    # hi "That's what people must do, sometimes."
    hi "時には、人は変わらなくちゃいけないのさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4658
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_5:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4661
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_ae118e0e:

    # n "{vspace=240}That's the last thing we say to each other that day, even though there would be so much to talk about."
    n "話せることはもっといっぱいあったけど、それがその日俺たちがお互いに言った最後の言葉だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4663
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_dfb8e2b0:

    # n "And even those words drown in the all-encompassing silence, disappearing into the stagnant air as if they were never said."
    n "その言葉さえすべてを包み込む静けさに沈み、まるで会話などなかったかのように、よどんだ空気の中へ消えていった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4665
translate jp a4_rin_raison_detre_76b2fe88_6:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4685
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c1dc1f90:

    # "The first day of summer vacation is a disappointment."
    "夏休み最初の日にはがっかりだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4687
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_83c1e36f:

    # "I woke up. Water came down from the leaden sky in Biblical proportions."
    "目を覚ましたら、鉛色の空から聖書に出てきそうな大雨が降っていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4689
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_02317591:

    # "I was optimistic at the time."
    "そのときの俺は楽観的だった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4691
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b9437469:

    # "A quick summer shower, I thought. Torrents of rain for a few minutes, then it's gone."
    "夏のにわか雨だろうと思っていた。数分のうちにザーッと降って、それで終わりだと。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4693
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ed6bb294:

    # "No such luck."
    "そんな都合良くはいかなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4702
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_be4e215c:

    # "Rainwater is relentlessly pouring down from the blue-gray sky outside, streaming down the glass of my window in small brooks and rivers and gathering together to form miniature ponds on the walkways."
    "雨水は絶え間なく青灰色の空から降り注いでいて、窓ガラスを小さな川になって流れ落ち、寄せ集められて遊歩道に小さな池を作る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4704
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0167ac62:

    # "Just like it has done for the past two and a half hours."
    "その様子は２時間半前から全く変わっていない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4711
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d88ef36c:

    # "So I've been half-assedly cleaning up in between half-assedly reading a book, packing my stuff on the side when I get bored of the first two."
    "そこで、俺はぐずぐずと掃除をしたり本を読んだりして、それに飽きたら荷物をまとめたりする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4713
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_df831c42:

    # "The weather drags my spirits pretty down too, making it harder to do anything properly."
    "この天気のおかげで気分もひどく沈んでしまい、何をするにもきちんとやるのが大変だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4717
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_22b52622:

    # "Something bumping quite loudly against my door rouses me from my apathy."
    "何かがひどく大きな音で部屋のドアにぶつかって、俺を無気力から呼び起こす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4719
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c552a4ad:

    # "I hope it's not Kenji and his crazy indoors bowling alley."
    "健二がバカみたいな屋内ボウリングでもやっていないことを祈ろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4721
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4723
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b844a4f7:

    # "I hear no more sounds from the corridor until I walk to the door and open it."
    "ドアのほうまで歩いていって開けるまで、それ以上廊下からはなにも聞こえてこない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4733
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e1d2edbf:

    # "Rin."
    "琳だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4735
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ab3de4e6:

    # "I wish seeing her would evoke some more emotion in me, but for one, I'm too surprised that she came to see me and for two, she is soaking wet."
    "その姿を見て、もう少し嬉しい気持ちになれたら良かったんだけど。でも琳が俺に会いに来たことに驚いてそれどころじゃなかったし、それに琳はずぶ濡れだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4737
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1c628974:

    # "Her uniform shirt is drenched and she is standing in a self-created puddle."
    "制服のシャツも水浸しで、体中からしずくが垂れて足下に水たまりを作っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4739
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a4ac716a:

    # "Droplets of rainwater are dripping from her short bangs and sliding down her nose until they fall down from the tip."
    "雨のしずくが短い前髪から滴り落ちると、今度は鼻を滑り降りて、鼻先から落ちていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4741
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d3ae6300:

    # "One.{w=0.7} By.{w=0.7} One."
    "ひとつ。{w=0.7} また、{w=0.7} ひとつ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4743
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9abb5df8:

    # hi "Umm… hi."
    hi "あー……よお"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4745
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c65cf440:

    # hi "How are you feeling?"
    hi "気分はどうだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4750
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_79478467:

    # rin "Medium normal."
    rin "普通の『中』かな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4754
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bc7af2e4:

    # "The relative questionability of her statement aside, she sure doesn't look too good."
    "どういう意味なのかわからないその言葉は置いておいて、琳は間違いなく調子が良くなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4756
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4451b91a:

    # hi "You're all wet."
    hi "ずぶ濡れじゃないか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4761
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8de3af21:

    # rin "It's because I come from the outside. Do you know it?"
    rin "外にいたからだよ。知ってた？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4763
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_251d293f:

    # hi "Why'd you be outside? It's raining buckets out there, if you haven't noticed."
    hi "なんで外にいたんだよ？　気づいてなかったのかも知れないけど、外は大雨だぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4768
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bcc78a0a:

    # rin "I haven't. It's raining pretty hard though. I was on a walk."
    rin "気づいてなかった。確かに大雨だね。散歩してたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4770
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4e2d34b6:

    # hi "Is this what you call 'wallowing in self-pity?'"
    hi "それがお前の言う『自己憐憫に浸る』ってやつなのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4775
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9567d639:

    # rin "Do you think I'm pitiful?"
    rin "私ってそんなに憐れかな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4777
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ddb58c5d:

    # hi "No, I implied that you think you are."
    hi "いや、お前がそう考えてそうだって言ったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4782
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d04f0b0b:

    # rin "I'm not, and rain is not a sad thing."
    rin "考えてない。それに雨は悲しいものじゃないよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4787
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_02779218:

    # rin "Don't you ever walk in the rain?"
    rin "雨の中を歩いたことないの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4789
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a13a35de:

    # hi "I do, but only with proper equipment, like an umbrella."
    hi "そりゃああるよ。ただ、それなりに用意をしてだぞ、傘とかさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4794
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ef730b2d:

    # rin "You just need to imagine you have a blue umbrella with white stripes."
    rin "青と白のしましまの傘を持ってるって想像すればいいんだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4796
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_43056c15:

    # hi "It might be tough when rain is falling on my head."
    hi "雨が頭に当たってるときにそれは難しいんじゃないか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4801
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e5c65b99:

    # rin "Just imagine harder."
    rin "もっとちゃんと想像して"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4803
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4805
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_25700211:

    # "Yeah, she definitely is back to normal."
    "ああ、確かにいつもの琳に戻ってる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4807
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_73ba8a99:

    # "Those half-sarcastic, inconsiderate remarks that really push my buttons even though she doesn't mean it, that vacant, spaced-out stare that always expects more than it gives."
    "本人にそんなつもりはなくても本当に頭にくる、嫌味半分のぶしつけな言葉。こちらに見えるよりも多くのものを求めてくる、うつろでぼんやりとした視線。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4809
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9b78fc7d:

    # "It's so… very much like her."
    "本当に……すごく琳らしいな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4814
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9cbab9a8:

    # rin "I may need to come in. I need some help with this water and clothes I'm wearing."
    rin "入れてもらわないとだめかも。この濡れてるのとか、服とかどうにかしないと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4816
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_932b2747:

    # "My brain quickly solves this equation, and I stumble with my words, a stark display of contrast against Rin's easygoing self-invitation."
    "脳がすぐにその意味を理解して、言葉に詰まってしまう。琳がやすやすと踏み入ってくるのとはまるで対照的だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4818
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bbcd449a:

    # hi "But, Emi…"
    hi "それなら笑美に……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4823
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_409c511a:

    # "Rin shakes her head vehemently, causing water to sprinkle everywhere."
    "琳は激しく頭を振ると、水しぶきをあたりにまき散らす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4825
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c8c9c35a:

    # rin "She left."
    rin "もう帰っちゃったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4830
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b7457483:

    # rin "Besides she would just worry and fuss until she could not worry or fuss any more, which always takes a troublesomely long time."
    rin "それに笑美、これ以上心配したり大騒ぎできなくなるまで心配したり大騒ぎするからね。そうなるまでいつも時間がかかってうっとうしいし"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4835
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3894ffc0:

    # rin "It's in fact longer than I want to hear her fussing, and I thought you probably are not the fussing kind."
    rin "はっきり言うと、私が聞いてられるよりも時間かかるんだよね。で、君は世話焼きってタイプじゃなさそうだと思ったから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4851
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8d352ed3:

    # "She slumps down on my desk with a squishy sound."
    "琳はベシャっという音を立てながら、俺の机の上にどっしりと座り込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4853
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6f478650:

    # "Her soaked clothes are making the desk and everything on it wet but she doesn't care."
    "ずぶ濡れの服が机の上のものを濡らすけど、琳は気にもとめない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4855
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4857
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_86c397ea:

    # hi "Okay. Fine. I'll help you out."
    hi "わかった。いいよ。手伝うよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4859
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f2442de3:

    # hi "I have a towel somewhere. Do you want dry clothes? Is a uniform fine? I'm taller than you, but…"
    hi "どっかにタオルがあったな。乾いた服に着替えるか？　制服でもいい？　お前のより大きいけど、でも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4864
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ef494bfa:

    # rin "Everything is fine."
    rin "おまかせするよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4869
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e5074b89:

    # "With a little searching I find a fresh uniform and a fluffy towel from the depths of my closet."
    "少し探すと、使っていない制服とふかふかのタオルがクローゼットの奥から出てくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4874
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_507a5528:

    # "The towel in one hand and the uniform in the other, I turn to face Rin again, uncertain of the next step."
    "片手にタオル、もう片方に制服を持って、次にどうすればいいのかわからないまま琳のほうに向き直る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4876
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2e80a3cc:

    # "There is something wrong with me, a normal guy would just—{w=1.0}{nw}"
    "どうかしてるな、俺は。普通の男だったら間違いなく――{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4881
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b1d5d5de:

    # rin "Stop worrying. It is not a problem."
    rin "心配するのやめて。なんでもないんだから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4883
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_07c04b46:

    # "She probably could see right through my hesitant demeanor."
    "きっと俺の怖じ気づいた様子がはっきり見てとれたんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4885
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7d48a506:

    # "As if I was completely transparent to her."
    "まるで、琳には何でもお見通しみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4887
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cfdf9dbf:

    # "I push my anxiety away and concentrate on the eight buttons lined on her shirt, just like mine has."
    "俺は心配を押しやると、俺のシャツと全く同じように、琳のシャツに並んでいる８つのボタンに集中する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4889
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_611ba244:

    # "Only the first button is an obstacle, and after getting it over I undo the others with slightly less shaking hands."
    "一番上のボタンだけは手こずったけど、それを乗り越えた後は、少し震えのおさまった手で他のボタンを外していく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4900
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ebf3ed8f:

    # "Throwing the soaked shirt aside, I reveal Rin's pale upper body, shrouded only in her light blue brassiere which instantly reminds me of her saying it's her favorite color."
    "濡れたシャツを横に放ると、琳の青白い、ライトブルーのブラジャーに覆われただけの上半身が露わになる。好きな色だと言っていたのをすぐに思い出す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4902
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1229aacd:

    # "I try not to think too much about… stuff, but it's hard not to look at her body with what I can only think of as mixed feelings."
    "あまり……余計なことは考えまいとする。でも琳の体を、この複雑な気持ちとしか呼びようのないもので見ないようにするのは無理がある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4904
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3564b3a0:

    # "I don't know what to think of this, so I just watch her. Rin looks… brittle."
    "それをなんて思えばいいのかわからなくて、俺はただ琳を見る。琳は……もろく見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4906
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a79d2366:

    # "She is like a shell, a fragile thing just barely holding together."
    "まるで貝のようだ。辛うじて形を保っている、今にも壊れそうな存在。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4908
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_24eacbe1:

    # "Her ribs, each of them visible under her pale skin, are moving up and down in the rhythm of her breaths."
    "一本一本の肋骨が青白い肌の下に見えて、呼吸に合わせて上下に動いている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4910
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b912e64d:

    # "Rin always struck me as quite thin, but I realize now that the manic creative period before the exhibition opening might've caused her to lose weight."
    "琳はとても華奢だと普段から思っていたけど、展覧会のオープニングの前の熱に浮かされたような制作期間のせいで体重が減ったのかもしれないと思い至る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4912
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4c0f9d7f:

    # "Did she eat properly and enough? Definitely not and probably not."
    "ちゃんとしたものを、十分に食べてたんだろうか？　絶対まともな食事なんてしてないだろう。量も多分足りてない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4914
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_512d4945:

    # "This ugly, yet beautiful bare minimum of a human body that belongs to someone I care about is a contradiction of aesthetics in itself, oddly becoming of her."
    "俺が好意を抱いている子の、醜いけども美しい、人としてのぎりぎりの水準しか満たしていないこの肉体は、それ自体が美学と矛盾していて、それが奇妙なほど似合っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4916
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fa911beb:

    # "My eyes follow her collarbone to her shoulder and down her arm until the abrupt end."
    "俺の目は琳の鎖骨から肩をたどって、その腕が突然途切れるところまで降りていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4918
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f62cfa24:

    # "No, it's less than the bare minimum, I think with a passing pang of sadness and some guilt for thinking like that."
    "いや、ぎりぎりでさえない。そう思うと悲しくて胸が痛むし、そう思ったことへのやましさも感じる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4926
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2e2886ad:

    # "Her arms, degenerated into almost nothing but bone and skin due to lack of use, look very short now that the long sleeves of her uniform are not covering them:"
    "使われていないせいで、琳の腕はほとんど骨と皮の状態まで退化していて、制服の長い袖に隠れていない今はとても短く見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4928
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b6b1f8af:

    # "My lack of any negative reaction makes me think that I've actually grown pretty accustomed of the various physical abnormalities of my schoolmates."
    "俺がネガティブな反応を示さなくなったのは、学校の仲間たちが色々と身体的に普通でないことに、大体慣れてしまったということなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4930
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3f77f8ae:

    # "I always wondered why Rin keeps her shirt sleeves long, only tying them in a simple knot at where the elbow would be."
    "どうして琳が袖を長いままにしておくのかいつも不思議だった。ただ肘があるはずのあたりを簡単に縛っているだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4932
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a2392e3a:

    # "It seems a bit impractical, but then again she is not exactly the pinnacle of practicality."
    "あまり実用的には見えないけど、そもそも琳は実用的という言葉からはほど遠いやつだった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4934
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ae1daa83:

    # "Maybe she likes it, maybe it is somehow important to her. Maybe there is no deeper meaning to it."
    "琳はこれが気に入っているのかもしれないし、それがとにかく重要なのかもしれない。特に深い理由はないのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4936
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c45528be:

    # "I feel like asking, and almost do, but Rin's miserable state requires a higher priority of my attention."
    "理由を聞いてみたくなって、もう少しでそうしかけるけど、この琳の惨状を先に世話してやらないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4943
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1fb4ce3e:

    # "She's stopped talking too, after we ran out of spiky greetings."
    "互いにとげとげしい挨拶の言葉が尽きてしまってから、琳は口をつぐんでいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4945
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd0c5c06:

    # "I guess there is no need for chitchat then."
    "じゃあ雑談する必要はなさそうだな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4950
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7a3f1c40:

    # "I pick up the towel from the bed and wrap it around her head, rumpling it all over her hair until most of the rainwater is hopefully soaked into the fabric."
    "俺はベッドの上に置いたタオルを手に取ると、琳の頭にかぶせて、雨水が大体取れたと思えるまでくしゃくしゃと髪を拭く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4955
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_322e26f2:

    # "She peeks from below the towel at me, looking up with impassive eyes."
    "琳はタオルの下から無感情な目で俺をのぞき見る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4957
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8dd0858a:

    # "It looks like she wants to say something without saying it."
    "言葉もなく何かを訴えようとしているように見える。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4959
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f5174080:

    # "It's that kind of a look."
    "そういう感じの目だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4961
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_71051f20:

    # "But I can't read what she is thinking about from her face, so I just keep on fussing with the towel around her shoulders and hair."
    "でも琳の考えはその表情からは読み取れなくて、ただタオルで肩や髪の毛のあたりを拭き続ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4963
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d7dbf791:

    # "The silence is oppressive, terrifying."
    "沈黙が恐ろしくて、耐え難い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4965
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7263a715:

    # "Communication between us has suddenly been reduced to the movements of my hands and the towel, and Rin swaying her body to and fro."
    "俺たちのコミュニケーションは突然、俺の手とタオルの動き、それから前後に揺れる琳の体の動きだけになってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4967
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bf17d8b0:

    # "My jagged breathing and her quiet breaths, trying to find a common rhythm that just is not there."
    "俺の途切れ途切れの息と琳の静かな息が、共通するリズムを探り合うけど、そんなものはここには存在しない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:4969
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b1731e57:

    # "I think I can hear her heartbeats, or maybe they are just mine redoubled."
