translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1e2eef89:

    # "I stand up to remove the last piece of clothing Rin has."
    "俺は立ち上がって琳が着ている最後の衣服を脱がせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5175
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1539ab33:

    # "She leans against me to catch her breath, tickling me with warm air exhaled into my shirt."
    "琳は息をつくために俺のほうにもたれかかる。シャツの内側に吐き出された暖かい空気が俺をくすぐる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5177
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_428c5dfb:

    # "Blindly, I reach behind her back to feel my way below her shoulder blades, to find the contraption that fastens her bra."
    "手探りで、俺は琳の背中から肩甲骨の下に手を回して、ブラジャーの留め具を探す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5179
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2d295887:

    # "It opens more easily than I thought, falling to the floor somewhere."
    "それは思っていたよりも簡単に外れて、そのまま床のどこかに落ちる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5188
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4232dc2a:

    # "Her bare skin against me is a sensation so wonderful that I want to have more of it, and I do, embracing her."
    "俺に触れる琳のむき出しの肌の感触がたまらなくて、俺はもっとそれを味わいたくなり、そのまま琳を抱きしめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5190
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_dcc1063d:

    # "Rin's hair smells of rain, and I realize that I'm not hearing the sound of rainfall any more."
    "琳の髪は雨の匂いがする。俺は雨音が止んでいることに気づく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5192
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fc569c5d:

    # "It's a sobering thing. The cushion that enveloped us into a reality of our own is now gone, and I realize more clearly what is happening."
    "俺は我に返る。俺たちだけの現実を覆っていたクッションはもうなくなってしまい、今起きていることをよりはっきりと理解する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5197
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4bd05e8c:

    # hi "You know, this really is not what friends should be doing."
    hi "なあ、友達同士でこういうことはするもんじゃないぜ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5199
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d6494819:

    # "I whisper, once again noticing how such a simple matter as talking can be overbearingly difficult at times."
    "会話というごく簡単な行為が、時には圧倒的に難しくなることもあるんだと再認識しながら、俺はささやく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5204
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d816abff:

    # rin "Will you stop being my friend?"
    rin "私の友達、やめちゃうの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5206
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_deb37c77:

    # "That wasn't what I meant, but her serious tone and the layers of connotations behind Rin's question give me pause."
    "そういう意味じゃない。でも琳の真剣な声色と、その問いの裏で幾重にも重なった含意に、俺は言葉を詰まらせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5211
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_974c322b:

    # hi "Nah."
    hi "いや"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5216
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2559cfc1:

    # rin "I… think it might be all right. Even if you did."
    rin "私……それでもいいと思うんだ。もしそうなっても"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5218
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_008c6c91:

    # "I hug her and smile into her hair, understanding Rin perfectly for once."
    "俺は琳を抱きしめると、その髪に微笑みかける。今度だけは琳の言っていることが完全に理解できる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5223
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_666c25bb:

    # rin "You are wet."
    rin "君、濡れてる"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5225
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0571641c:

    # "The remnants of water on her skin have drained into my shirt."
    "琳の肌に残っていた水気が俺のシャツに染み込んでいた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5227
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6683f306:

    # "Somehow, even her statements of the obvious make me glad right now."
    "なんだか、わかりきったことを言う琳の言葉も今の俺には嬉しい。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5232
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7027cd75:

    # hi "You're right. I am. But that's your fault."
    hi "そうだな。濡れてる。お前のせいだぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5237
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_350e4c5d:

    # rin "I want to see you."
    rin "君が見たいな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5244
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_21881e75:

    # "I comply, standing back to open the buttons of my shirt, much more quickly than when I undid Rin's buttons."
    "言われたとおりに、俺は後ろに下がってシャツのボタンを外す。琳のときよりもずっと早く済む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5246
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2d91b7ea:

    # "A sudden sense of haste strikes me, spurring me to rush forward."
    "突然急かされているような気分になって、俺は急いで手を進める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5248
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_435c8b50:

    # "Every second I'm not touching Rin is a second wasted, a chance lost."
    "琳に触れずにいる一秒一秒が時間の浪費だ。チャンスの無駄遣いだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5250
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_733ce239:

    # "My belt buckle proves an obstacle despite my ability to open it in an eyeblink under normal circumstances."
    "ベルトのバックルが邪魔をする。いつもなら一瞬で外せるのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5255
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c415f634:

    # "While I fumble with it, I don't notice Rin bringing her foot up between us until she starts tracing my chest with her toe."
    "手こずっていると、気づかないうちに琳が足を持ち上げて、つま先で俺の胸をなぞり始める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5260
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ee0d6ee6:

    # "I look down to see what she's looking at…"
    "俺は琳が見ている部分を見下ろす……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5262
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f8375736:

    # hi "My heart…"
    hi "心臓……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5264
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e3509c53:

    # "I reflexively flinch back, covering the scar tissue in the middle of my chest."
    "俺は反射的に胸の中央の傷跡を押さえて後ずさる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5266
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_875587e7:

    # "The shallow mark that the surgery following my heart attack left on my body has healed already but… well, it's not a particularly pretty sight if not overly repulsive either."
    "発作の後に受けた手術の浅い傷口はもう治っているけど……まあ、ひどく不快とまではいかなくても、あまりきれいなものじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5268
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_af71731a:

    # "It's barely noticeable, but she does have an eye for detail. Is this why she said she wanted to see me?"
    "ほとんど目には見えないけど、琳は細かいところによく気が付く。琳が見たいって言っていたのはこれが理由なのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5270
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_718f6e3e:

    # "I had sorta forgotten about this because of all this mess with Rin, but now all the unpleasant things connected to my condition surface at once, rushing through my mind like a flash flood."
    "琳にちょっかいを出していたせいで、このことを忘れていた。でも今は体のことに関わる不愉快なことが一気に浮かんできて、鉄砲水のように心を突き抜けていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5272
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_fba91042:

    # "And oh God all the stories about old guys getting heart attacks when having sex, what if…"
    "やれやれ、それに年を取ったおっさんがセックスの最中に心臓発作を起こす話を山ほど思い出してしまった。もしも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5277
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_aa95e2ab:

    # rin "Hisao."
    rin "久夫"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5279
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce617998_4:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5281
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8c1f9dd0:

    # "Realizing that I might just have spoiled the mood, I stumble to explain myself."
    "雰囲気を壊しかけたことに気づいて、つっかえながら言い訳をする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5286
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd4cb466:

    # hi "Ah… sorry, it's just that…"
    hi "ああ……悪い。ちょっとな……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5291
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2fda4de3:

    # rin "Let me touch you."
    rin "触らせてよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5293
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3c0633da:

    # "Her eyes are sultry, inviting as she sits there bare naked without an inkling of shame. I never thought Rin could look like that."
    "艶やかな、誘うような目だ。少しも恥じらうことなく、一糸まとわぬ姿で座っている。琳のこんな格好を見ることになるなんて思ってもみなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5298
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5301
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_37e3fa9f:

    # n "{vspace=60}Yeah, I know this is not how it should go."
    n "\n\nああ、わかってる。こんなことになるなんて間違ってる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5303
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c340a88e:

    # n "Even though Rin is right here, even though there should be no more questions, no obstacles, not this maddening feeling that something is constantly wrong…"
    n "琳がここにいるのに、もう聞くべきことも、邪魔なものも何もないのに、何かがずっとおかしいという気の狂いそうな感覚が……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5305
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_9d5c454f:

    # n "The same feeling that clutched my heart yesterday makes its appearance."
    n "昨日、俺の心臓を捕らえたのと同じ感覚がまた現れる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5307
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5df195c9:

    # n "We are together. In a way that is difficult to define, it eludes description as stubbornly as it evades change."
    n "俺たちは一緒だ。具体的にどこがどうとは言いづらいけど。とにかく説明しようとしてもとらえどころがないし、変化もしないからだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5309
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_aae9885e:

    # n "{vspace=30}Would a relationship like this be all right? Could we ever change to become closer?"
    n "\nこんな関係はうまくいくのか？　俺たちはもっと親しい関係へと変われるんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5311
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c736497f:

    # n "Even though we would stay together for all of eternity, we might never find our mutual understanding."
    n "たとえこれから永遠に一緒に過ごしたとしても、決してお互いを理解しあうことができないかもしれないんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5313
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1bfb78bc:

    # n "But there is no such thing as eternity. This may mean that we will not be together forever."
    n "でも永遠なんてそもそもありえない。俺たちもずっと一緒にはいられないかもしれないってことだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5315
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_42f296c7:

    # n "If not our differences, then the flow of time will pull us apart with irresistible force."
    n "俺たち二人がお互いの違いを乗り越えられたとしても、時の流れは俺たちを容赦なく引き裂くだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5317
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4a6f1880:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}Rin is a creature of the moment, of whim and of impulse."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\n琳は瞬間、気まぐれ、そして衝動の生き物だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5321
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a34c7f98:

    # n "{vspace=30}I am nothing of the sort."
    n "\n俺とは似ても似つかない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5323
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f86d998b:

    # n "{vspace=30}This is a fact that I can understand very clearly."
    n "\nこれははっきりと理解できる事実だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5325
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c60b0d90:

    # n "If for no other reason, for this reason I should grasp this moment. Even if it's the only moment we will ever have, I should not let myself spoil it."
    n "何よりも、他ならぬこの理由のために、俺はこの時をものにすべきだ。たとえ俺たちにはこの一瞬しかないのだとしても、それを無駄にしてはいけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5327
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d14b3d69:

    # n "Even if I can't escape myself. Rin can't either, I know it now."
    n "俺自身、逃れることはできないとしても。琳にもできない。今ならそれが分かる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5329
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7acd07de:

    # n "{vspace=30}We both have things we can't let go, things we can't not think."
    n "\n俺たちには手放すことのできないもの、考えずにはいられないものがある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5331
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7a5647e5:

    # n "Feelings we can't not feel."
    n "感じずにはいられない感覚が。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5333
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_bfe9e23d:

    # n "But she allows herself to want me without any restraint. Here and now."
    n "でも、琳は何のためらいもなく俺を求めようとしている。今ここで。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5338
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5344
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_958f974a:

    # hi "I'm sorry, you know…"
    hi "ごめんな、俺……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5349
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_80257f6b:

    # rin "Hisao, you really have to stop worrying."
    rin "久夫、心配するの、本当にやめたほうがいいよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5351
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_66c913b3:

    # "Rin interrupts me before I get further, which is good because I don't know what I could have said."
    "俺がそれ以上しゃべる前に、琳が割って入る。助かった、そのまま続けていたら何を口走っていたか、わかったものじゃない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5353
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b5e01e11:

    # "Her voice, void of its usual spaciness, scolds me softly, without an edge."
    "いつもと違って現実味のある琳の声が、角を立てることもなく俺を優しくたしなめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5358
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_0d8874a2:

    # rin "You really have to learn to let go."
    rin "もっと楽にならなきゃだめだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5360
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2f3ea9c1:

    # "She scans me calmly, almost calculatingly."
    "琳は淡々と俺を分析する。抜け目ないと言っていいくらいに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5362
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_72a0073f:

    # "I wonder what I look like through her eyes."
    "琳の目に俺はどう映っているんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5364
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_03b55d8f:

    # "Damn. They are so green it almost hurts."
    "くそ。緑色がきつすぎて痛くなってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5366
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_a02c9829:

    # "I always was so enchanted by her eyes, those mysterious, captivating eyes that always were too restless for their own good."
    "琳の目にはいつも惹きこまれてしまう。いつもそれ自身のためにせわしなく動き回っている、不思議な、虜にされてしまいそうな目だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5368
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_6bce045d:

    # "But I was also always intimidated by them."
    "でも同時に、俺はその目を恐れていた。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5370
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_11809855:

    # "Yeah. Rin is intimidating, on more than one level and especially right now."
    "そうだ。琳はいろんな意味で怖い。今は特にそうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5372
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3dd90fee:

    # "She is frighteningly lucid, the goosebumps on her skin giving away that she is cold, or scared too."
    "琳は恐ろしくなるくらい分かりやすい。その肌には鳥肌が立っていて、琳が寒がっていて、そしておびえているのが見てとれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5374
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_662e69fb:

    # "Either way, I steel myself and step back to Rin, embracing her to feel her in my arms again and to banish my doubts."
    "どちらにせよ、俺は身を引き締めると、琳から一歩離れてもう一度抱きしめ、疑いを払いのける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5376
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2da63880:

    # "The sight of her gentle, loving eyes seems to melt those doubts away like the last snow of winter."
    "優しく、愛に満ちたその目を見て、俺の疑念はまるで冬の終わりの雪のように溶かされていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5381
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_da91b700:

    # "She presses her head against my shoulder, seeking a place to rest herself in, leaning against me like I lean against her."
    "俺がそうしているのと同じように、琳は俺にもたれかかると、休まる場所を探して、こちらの肩に頭を押し当てる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5383
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_729935a4:

    # rin "Let go."
    rin "楽になって"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5385
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ce147a6b:

    # "Yes."
    "そうだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5390
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_00f01785:

    # rin "You should forget about stuff like future and past, it's not like you can change those kinds of things."
    rin "過去とか未来とか、そんなことは忘れようよ。そんなの変えられるものじゃないんだから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5392
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7fef17d3:

    # "I wanted to say something to her, but I have lost my voice so I just mumble something unintelligible at her."
    "琳に何か言いたかったけど、声を失った俺は曖昧なことをぼそぼそと言うだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5394
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_37f57e6c:

    # rin "You should just be with me now."
    rin "今は私と一緒にいて"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5396
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d0ac6a2d:

    # "Maybe she understood what I wanted to say even if I didn't."
    "言わなくても、琳には俺が言いたかったことが分かったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5398
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_03987e9d_1:

    # rin "Come here."
    rin "こっち来て"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5400
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_26125840:

    # hi "I am here."
    hi "ここにいるじゃないか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5405
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5f1303fe:

    # rin "Come closer."
    rin "もっと近く"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5407
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1ff0ae96:

    # "My entire body is thinking only in positives now so I do, hugging her more tightly."
    "全身が前向きの思考しかしていない俺は、その言葉に従い、琳をより強く抱き締める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5412
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c6716819:

    # rin "Closer."
    rin "もっと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5414
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_b4d2a415:

    # "I press my lower body against hers."
    "下半身を押しつける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5416
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_8cf7b162:

    # "She tenses a little. Just a little."
    "琳は少し強張る。本当に少しだけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5421
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c6716819_1:

    # rin "Closer."
    rin "もっと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5423
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c298c05f:

    # "Her final plead is more like a prayer."
    "最後の嘆願は、もはや祈りに近い。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5425
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e7c44892:

    # "There is only one way to be any closer than this."
    "これ以上近づくには、方法は一つしかない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5427
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3e55b3e3:

    # "I reach down between us and guide myself, sinking myself into her."
    "俺は琳との間に手を伸ばして、手を添えながら自分自身を琳の中に潜り込ませていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5432
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4f772e29:

    # "Every muscle in Rin's body stiffens at the same time."
    "琳のあらゆる筋肉が一度にこわばる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5437
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_504839b3:

    # "She doesn't say anything, or wince, so I push deeper, eventually moving out."
    "琳は何も言わず、表情も変えない。だからさらに奥へと進み、そして後ろに下がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5439
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_49748624:

    # "And again. And she moves with me."
    "再び前へ。琳も俺に合わせて動く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5441
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_2b0cca68:

    # "Our movements melt together into one continuous string of back and forth, in and out."
    "俺たちの動きは一つの連なりへと融合する。前と後、中と外。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5443
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4dc35e48:

    # "All sensations become sharper, amplified tenfold."
    "すべての感覚が鋭敏になり、１０倍にも増幅される。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5445
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_601c4c52:

    # "My brain gave up interpreting all this stimulation ages ago, and now I am left with no choice but to feel all of this with my entire body."
    "俺の脳はこの興奮を理解するのをとうの昔にあきらめていて、今はその全てを全身で感じることしかできない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5447
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_c5f9a3ed:

    # "It's like that for Rin too, I know it. I can see it. I can feel it."
    "琳も同じだ、俺には分かってる。見てとれる。感じとれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5449
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_63cfdfe6:

    # "She breathes sharply in and out, losing all composure and grace, breathes warmly against my shoulder."
    "琳の呼吸が速くなる。落ち着きも優雅さもすっかり失い、温かい息を俺の肩に吹きかけている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5451
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_11411736:

    # "Between those fragile breaths, she sometimes kisses me tenderly, gently, as if she was unsure how to do it properly."
    "か細い息遣いの合間に、琳は時折俺に優しく、そっとキスをする。まるでちゃんとしたキスの仕方が分からないかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5453
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_1a5de89a:

    # "But there is no hesitation."
    "でも、そこにためらいはない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5455
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_aa486ee6:

    # "Desperately clinging to me, drawing me closer so that I can fill all of her, she moves against me, around me so that it's hard to say where I stop and she begins."
    "俺が一番奥まで入るように、琳は必死に俺にしがみついて、引っ張り寄せる。琳は俺に向かって、俺の周りを動くので、どこからが俺でどこまでが琳なのかわからなくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5457
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_94393f9d:

    # "We take it slowly, excruciatingly slowly, as if we had all the time in the world even though we have only this moment and nothing beyond that."
    "俺たちにあるのは今この時だけで、そこから先にはもう何もないのに、まるで時間なんて無限にあるかのように、俺たちはゆっくりと、耐え難いほどゆっくりと続ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5459
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_dc3ca1ab:

    # "That feeling is—{w=0.7}{nw}"
    "この感じはまるで――{w=0.7}{nw}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5464
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_886e7c0a:

    # rin "Wait…"
    rin "待って……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5466
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3ac2e6dd:

    # "I stop moving, slightly alarmed."
    "俺はわずかに警戒して動きを止める。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5468
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_4cc669aa:

    # "Maybe it hurts, or…"
    "痛んだのか、それとも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5473
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_615746d3:

    # "She looks at me in a way that I can't really begin to interpret."
    "琳は俺を解釈のしようのない目で見る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5475
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_24603c9e:

    # rin "Is this it?"
    rin "こういうことなの？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5477
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5d79aa7b:

    # hi "…Huh?"
    hi "……なんだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5479
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_30d988dc:

    # rin "You said I don't have to be alone."
    rin "私はひとりぼっちにならなくてもいいんだって言ったよね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5484
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_50cbf646:

    # "Her eyes are full of an innocent, fuzzyheaded confusion that makes me chuckle a little and pet the back of her head."
    "その目は純粋さとぼんやりとした混乱に満ちていて、俺は小さく笑うと、頭をなでてやる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5486
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_3f8ce92c:

    # hi "Yeah. This is what I meant."
    hi "ああ、そういうことだな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5488
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_075a6638:

    # hi "That you have someone you can come to when you get soaked in a rain."
    hi "雨に降られたときに頼れる人がいるってこと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5490
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_f5c30628:

    # hi "It means you are not alone."
    hi "それはつまり、お前は独りじゃないってことだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5492
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_ac625991:

    # hi "If there is such a person for you."
    hi "お前にそんな奴がいればの話だけどな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5497
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_99614c14:

    # "She answers with a kiss, reminding me that we have stopped moving for no real reason."
    "琳がキスで答えると、俺たちは大した理由もなしに動きを止めていたことを思い出す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5499
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd557e60:

    # "So we start from the top, almost at the same time, each mirroring the rhythm of the other."
    "俺たちは最初からやり直す。ほとんど２人同時に、お互いの動きをリズミカルに真似ながら。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5501
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_e896411a:

    # "I move faster, faster in and out of her, my sweat mixing with hers, glistening on our shared skin like diamonds and pearls."
    "俺はより速く動いて、琳に出入りする。汗が琳の汗と混ざりあい、繋がりあった肌がダイヤモンドと真珠のようにきらきらと光る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5509
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_972ccab8:

    # "She moves faster, grinding herself against me in the throes of our desire."
    "琳ももっと速く動く。この欲望の王座で、俺に体をこすり付ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5511
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5493bdc5:

    # "The intoxicating scent of her lust, the mind-blanking feeling that connects our bodies, the sense of all rational thought draining from my mind."
    "酔いしれるような琳の情欲の香り。俺たちの体を繋げる、心が空っぽになるような感覚。心からあらゆる理性が吸い上げられる感覚。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5513
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_7e959875:

    # "All those burn my consciousness just like the compelling feeling in my body burns my instincts."
    "その全てが俺の意識を燃やし尽くす。身体の中の切実な気持ちが、俺の本能を焼くのと同じように。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5515
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_cd8ed96a:

    # "As those feelings grow, Rin makes no signs of stopping."
    "その感覚が強まっていき、琳も止まる気配はない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5517
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_5beb3699:

    # "She curls her feet behind my lower back, forcing me to drive myself inside her as deep as physically possible, each millimeter sending waves through my spine."
    "琳は俺の腰に足を回して、俺に肉体の限界まで奥に進ませようとする。１ミリ進むたびに波が背骨を駆け抜けていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5519
translate jp a4_rin_wb_and_ws_d6045af8:

    # "My mind blacks out as the world erupts into a flash of bright white blindness."
    "白い輝きが世界を埋め尽くして何も見えなくなり、俺の意識はブラックアウトする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5539
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_c55baf0d:

    # centered_b "Present{fast}" with Dissolve(4.0)
    centered_b "今{fast}" with Dissolve(4.0)

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5541
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_dae2c000:

    # nvl clear
    # nb "'Present' is a fleeting and vague concept at best."
    nvl clear
    nb "『今』なんて、あやふやですぐに過ぎ去ってしまうものだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5545
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_00f851bb:

    # nb "The moment between the past and the future?"
    nb "過去と未来の間にある瞬間？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5547
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8c328169:

    # nb "That doesn't really mean anything."
    nb "そんな説明に大した意味はない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5549
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_261964ab:

    # nb "Thinking too much about things that don't make sense is a waste of time."
    nb "無意味なことを深く考えすぎても時間の無駄だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5551
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7f3c8d99:

    # nb "That's why living through the present is always the best option."
    nb "だから今を生き抜くことはいつでも最高の選択というわけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5553
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_9eca2067:

    # nb "Besides, for us who can't foresee the future and who forget the past too easily, present is really the only proof of our existence."
    nb "第一、未来を予測することもできず、過去も簡単に忘れてしまう俺たちにとって、今というのは唯一の存在の証明だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5555
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_a1f16ab2:

    # nb "Even though existence will go on even if you forget about it for a while, it's good to seize the day at least every once in a while."
    nb "しばらくそのことを忘れていても、存在することには変わりはない。でもたまにはその一瞬を楽しむのもいいものだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5557
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_115223a8:

    # nvl clear
    # centered_b "That way… you can confirm that you are, in fact… {color=#fff}alive.{/color}"
    nvl clear
    centered_b "そうすれば……確かめられるんだ……{color=#fff}生きている、と。{/color}"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5579
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7460cbe0:

    # "I am pretty sure that the girl who is standing there half-naked, staring out of the window of my room, has a much better grasp of 'present' than I do."
    "そこに立っている、半裸のまま俺の部屋から窓の外を眺めている女の子のほうが、俺よりもよほど『今』をよく理解しているに違いない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5581
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0964a88a:

    # "As for me… well, right now I'm somewhat confused by my present state, since I should try to locate my shirt and not stare at Rin's butt."
    "俺はといえば……まあ、今のところ自分の状況にちょっと戸惑っている。琳の尻をじろじろ見るんじゃなくて、自分のシャツを探さないといけない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5583
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_bc77f0a9:

    # "But I just can't stop looking at her."
    "それでも、琳を見るのをやめられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5590
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_67970a7c:

    # "She is so close to the glass that her nose is probably going to leave a mark."
    "琳は窓ガラスにかじりついている。たぶんガラスに鼻の跡が残るだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5592
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_66ab547f:

    # "At least her breathing does, when it condenses on the rain-cooled window glass before quickly disappearing again."
    "少なくとも、琳の吐息は跡を残している。雨で冷えた窓が曇っては晴れてを繰り返している。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5594
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b9343c60:

    # "My shuffling around to get dressed doesn't rouse Rin from her contemplation, which is fine, really. I don't mind the silences as much as I used to."
    "服を着ようと足を引きずって歩いても、考えにふける琳の集中は乱れない。でもそれで構わない。前よりもこういう沈黙が気にならなくなった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5596
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_11af94eb:

    # "Only after I'm almost finished with buttoning up my shirt does Rin say something, still without turning to look at me."
    "シャツのボタンを留め終えるころになって、琳が俺のほうを向かないまま口を開く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5601
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8f8ebc5c:

    # rin "Let's go somewhere."
    rin "どっか行こうよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5603
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_804bb8e8:

    # hi "Where?"
    hi "どこにだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5605
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_599351a4:

    # "I can only assume she is inviting me and not the windowsill, but it's a fair guess."
    "琳は窓枠じゃなくて俺を誘っているんだろう、と推測するしかない。でも多分そうだよな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5610
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b1f1c9df:

    # rin "I know."
    rin "わかってる"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5612
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5617
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_2e4fe64a:

    # rin "Help me get dressed."
    rin "服着るの、手伝って"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5622
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_956b0ce8:

    # rin "I think today is the day."
    rin "今日がその日なんだ、きっと"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5627
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d2aa1f25:

    # rin "Come on, clothes."
    rin "早く、服"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5629
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_eb4226ad:

    # "Clothes, clothes… what an impatient tone."
    "服、服って……なんてせっかちな声だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5631
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_dfece63c:

    # "I crouch down to pick up her bra from the floor where it had fallen, discarded in the haste of undressing and forgotten there."
    "俺はしゃがみこんで、脱ぎ捨てられ、忘れられていた琳のブラを床から拾い上げる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5633
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f0f01aba:

    # "Hanging it from between my fingers like a dead fish, the same hesitation that grasped me when I was undressing Rin is creeping inside my head again."
    "死んだ魚のように指の間にそれを挟むと、琳を脱がせるときに感じた、ぞっとするようなためらいにもう一度襲われる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5635
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d1ebecd8:

    # "Is intimacy really something this difficult for me to handle?"
    "親密になることは、俺にとってこんなに手に負えないことなんだろうか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5640
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_3876b379:

    # rin "Come on, you got it off just fine. This is the same but the other way around. It's like talking backwards."
    rin "ほら、脱がすときはすぐできたでしょ。それとおんなじだよ、反対なだけで。逆さにしゃべるようなものだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5645
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_170923fa:

    # rin "Ysae s'ti tub, drah smees."
    rin "よだんたんかもで、どけだうそしかずむ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5647
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7bd112e1:

    # "Perplexed by her sudden and prodigious display of mental processing capacity, I forget to attempt reversing her gibberish back."
    "突然な、そして並外れた琳の頭の回転の速さに唖然として、その意味不明な言葉を逆に読み取るのを忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5649
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f983896b:

    # "I'm pretty sure I couldn't switch to talking backwards that fluidly even with some practice."
    "もちろん練習したところで、あんなに滑らかに逆向き会話に切り替えられるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5651
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_881c13a4:

    # hi "Umm, could you repeat that?"
    hi "うーん、もう一回言ってくれないか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5656
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_170923fa_1:

    # rin "Ysae s'ti tub, drah smees."
    rin "よだんたんかもで、どけだうそしかずむ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5658
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5660
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_008979ce:

    # hi "Got it. Fine, I'll give it a try."
    hi "なるほど。わかった、じゃあやってみる"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5662
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_c1e3d7c4:

    # "Rin was right, the locking mechanism is simple enough, and I get the little plastic hooks right on the third attempt."
    "琳の言うとおりだった。留め具の構造は簡単で、３回目の挑戦で小さなプラスチックのフックがカチリとはまる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5664
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_bd6fd538:

    # hi "There."
    hi "よし"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5669
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_91a2f43e:

    # rin "Ti tsujda ot evah uoy won."
    rin "てしおなはぎつ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5671
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8dfe0930:

    # hi "What? Please stop that, I don't speak backwardese."
    hi "なに？　それやめてくれよ、俺は逆さ語は話せないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5676
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_1e9fa4f1:

    # "She shakes her head as if needing to banish the backwards way of thinking with a physical gesture."
    "体の動きで逆さま思考を追い出すかのように、琳はかぶりを振る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5678
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_dc719f51:

    # "I know a few people who could benefit from that kind of ability."
    "そういう能力があれば役に立ちそうな人には何人か心当たりがある。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5683
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7bc86513:

    # rin "I got stuck. Now you have to adjust it."
    rin "突っかかっちゃった。次は直して"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5685
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_a4f872d1:

    # hi "Adjust?"
    hi "直す？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5690
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d40b3e97:

    # rin "That's what I said."
    rin "そうだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5692
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0ec38f07:

    # hi "No, I asked what you meant."
    hi "いや、どういう意味かって聞いたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5697
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0f74b2a9:

    # rin "You know, so that they are… fine."
    rin "そりゃあ、その……きちんとなるように"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5699
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0245740c:

    # "Oh. Fine, you say?"
    "きちんとってなんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5701
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998_1:

