    # "It petrifies me too, the shock of the incomprehensibility of this situation."
    "状況のあまりの不可解さにショックを受けて、こっちまで固まってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5991
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_992f1cf2:

    # "I just don't know what is happening any more."
    "もう何が起きているのか、俺には理解できない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5993
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_66375617:

    # hi "Rin? What's wrong?"
    hi "琳？　どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:5995
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_6d1989e6:

    # rin "I…"
    rin "私……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6000
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_e8ee8c0b:

    # "She shakes her head in confusion, stumbling to get the words out of her mouth."
    "琳は困惑して頭を振る。なかなか言葉を発することができない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6005
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_458ca1c2:

    # rin "Sorry…"
    rin "ごめん……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6007
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b36ee50c:

    # rin "I might be a little afraid of you."
    rin "君のことが怖くなってきちゃったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6009
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_688baf88:

    # "The words are muttered slowly, with a small voice that is as disbelieving of what it's saying as I am."
    "琳はゆっくりとつぶやく。自分の言っていることが信じられないというかのように小さな声だ。俺にも信じられない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6011
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d650e2c8:

    # hi "What? Why?"
    hi "なんだそれ？　どうしてだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6016
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_bdeaba1d:

    # rin "I don't know. Saying that just made me feel like that."
    rin "わかんない。そう言ったらそんな気持ちになったんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6021
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_782f7f55:

    # rin "People cry when they are afraid, right?"
    rin "人って怖いときは泣くんでしょ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6026
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_01ca1509:

    # rin "See? I can do it too."
    rin "ね？　私も泣けるんだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6028
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_4421aa89:

    # "She's averting her gaze now, deliberately not looking at me. It bewilders me, at least as much as what she is saying."
    "琳は視線をそらして、わざと俺を見ないようにしている。その仕草も、今の言葉も、同じくらい俺を戸惑わせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6033
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_03e51ec3:

    # rin "I… I sometimes, with you, want to run away so badly but I can't move it's like my legs turn into lemon panna cotta pudding and my heart feels like it's going to explode and…"
    rin "私……私さ、君といると時々、すごく逃げ出したくなっちゃうんだけど、でも動けないんだ、足がレモンのパンナコッタになっちゃったみたいで、胸が破裂しそうで……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6038
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_db15cc53:

    # "She slumps her shoulders melancholically."
    "琳は意気消沈したように肩を落とす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6040
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_db2b73fb:

    # rin "Has a thing like this ever happened to you?"
    rin "君にはそういうこと、あった？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6042
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7481a787:

    # "…I remember the leaden sky above the frozen forest and the sound of the leafless branches clacking against each other."
    "……凍りついた森を覆う鉛色の空と、葉の落ちた枝ががさがさと擦れ合う音が思い浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6044
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_004dc9b0:

    # "It's like a memory from another life."
    "まるで別の人生の記憶みたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6046
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_30b5d4ca:

    # hi "Yeah. Once."
    hi "ああ、一度な"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6048
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_661cd1ac:

    # hi "My heart hurt a lot back then, too."
    hi "俺もあのときは胸がすごく痛かったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6053
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ba43c420:

    # rin "But I thought your thing was not contagious."
    rin "でもそれって人にはうつらないんじゃなかったの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6055
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_510b69cb:

    # "I shake my head and a tiny, slightly forced smile rises on my lips."
    "俺は頭を振る。口元に少しだけ、作り気味の笑みが浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6057
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_60be4f85:

    # "The other ailment of my heart could very well be contagious and I wouldn't care a bit."
    "俺がかかっているもう一方の胸の病は、それこそ人にうつるものだろう。それなら大歓迎だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6059
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b391119b:

    # hi "What are you afraid of? I never thought I was scary."
    hi "なにを怖がってるんだ？　俺は自分が怖いやつだなんて思ったこと一度もないぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6064
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ca3241ba:

    # "Rin shakes her head desperately, as if knowing that the tangle inside her mind won't be undone with just that."
    "心の中のもつれはそんなことでは解けないとわかっているみたいに、琳は必死に頭を振る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6066
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8ea99569:

    # rin "You make me feel that I should be someone else than me."
    rin "君といると、私以外の誰かにならなきゃって気持ちになるんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6071
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b53e326b:

    # rin "It's a scary thing."
    rin "これって怖いことだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6076
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0cf72bce:

    # rin "It happens when you are being nice to me. Like yesterday."
    rin "君が優しくしてくれるたびにそう思うんだ。昨日みたいに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6078
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_9dd65f28:

    # rin "I never know what to do at times like that. It's hard."
    rin "そういうとき、どうすればいいか全然分かんないんだ。大変なんだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6080
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_68a783da:

    # "Her voice is barely audible, a whispered admission of something that is too embarrassing to even think, not to mention to say aloud."
    "琳のかすかな声がかろうじて聞こえる。そのささやきは、口に出すどころか考えるだけでも恥ずかしすぎることの告白だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6082
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_29fded1b:

    # "Rin has never been one to be embarrassed so she does utter it aloud, only timidly as if by instinct."
    "琳は恥ずかしがるようなタイプじゃないから言葉に出したんだ。本能に従うかのように怖々とではあったけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6087
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_4f3fe0a2:

    # rin "But I want to do something. But I don't know if this me can."
    rin "でもどうにかしたいんだ。でもこの私にできるかわからないんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6089
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_93e843ab:

    # "For a moment, we just stare at each other as if waiting for the other to say something."
    "少しの間、俺たちはお互いに何か言い出すのを待っているかのように見つめあう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6091
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998_5:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6096
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_e9c67197:

    # hi "You are so stupid."
    hi "ほんとに馬鹿だな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6101
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8543f31f:

    # "Rin's lips taste salty and scared against mine."
    "琳の唇は塩っぽくて、俺に怯えている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6110
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_30bfda0f:

    # "As I grasp her into an embrace, I feel my heart thumping in my chest painfully."
    "琳を抱き寄せると、心臓が痛いほど高鳴る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6122
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6125
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_fcc6a40d:

    # n "{vspace=60}Even though I am glad that she can say things like that, they make me sad after all."
    n "\n\n琳がそんなことを言える、ということが嬉しくはあるけど、やっぱり俺は悲しくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6127
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b396a056:

    # n "Rin's spirit, her passion, her strength. All those things that I hold dear are the ones I don't want to change."
    n "琳の精神、情熱、強さ。みんな俺が愛しいと思っているもの、そして変わって欲しくないと思っているものだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6129
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_df8f61f5:

    # n "How should I treat them? Where are they headed to? Is that future irrevocably different from mine?"
    n "それをどう受け止めればいい？　どこに向かっていくのか？　その未来は俺の未来と決定的に違うのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6131
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b8565158:

    # n "That anxiety will never loose its grip on my heart, but I think I could learn to live with it."
    n "そんな不安が俺の心臓から離れることは決してないだろうけど、それを受け入れて生きていくことはできると思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6133
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_29a6b7fb:

    # n "Slowly, the pain in my heart dies out, and it settles into the same rhythm as Rin's."
    n "ゆっくりと心臓の痛みは消えていき、琳の鼓動と同じ速さになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6135
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_6b3de1e1:

    # n "{vspace=60}We listen to that for some time."
    n "\n\n俺たちはしばらくの間、それに耳を傾ける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6137
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_eabec665:

    # n "…"
    n "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6144
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6149
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_e9d6a185:

    # "After our lips break apart, it takes a while for either of us to realize that we can say something now."
    "唇が離れると、もう話をしてもいいんだと気づくまでにしばらく時間がかかる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6151
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998_6:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6156
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_8df36035:

    # rin "See?"
    rin "ほらね？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6161
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ceccb903:

    # rin "You are a really kind person, even when you are not."
    rin "君ってほんとうに優しいよ。そうでないときでもね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6163
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_269538d0:

    # rin "It's the most scariest thing ever."
    rin "それがいちばん怖いんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6168
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d500678a:

    # rin "I think… that all I was ever afraid of is your kindness."
    rin "私……ずっと君の優しさだけが怖かったんだと思う"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6170
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998_7:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6172
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ae4b5795:

    # hi "Is it bad? Even if you are afraid?"
    hi "なにがまずいんだ？　怖くたって"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6177
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_cfbf1adf:

    # "She thinks about this for a while, furrowing her brow as though this was some kind of hard math problem."
    "琳は難しい数学の問題でも解くかのように眉間にしわを寄せて、しばらく考え込む。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6182
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_3861dc5c:

    # rin "No. I'm all right with it. It's fine, if it's you."
    rin "ううん。もう大丈夫。君なら平気"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6184
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ac87dbcf:

    # "Like a weight lifted from my chest, her words elate my heart, filling it with… I don't know, happiness?"
    "重しが胸から外れたかのように、琳の言葉が俺の心臓を高鳴らせる。俺の心を満たすのは……なんだろう、幸せか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6186
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_654ce13e:

    # "What else could it be?"
    "他になにがあるっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6188
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f251778b:

    # "This time my smile is genuine."
    "今の俺の笑顔は本物だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6194
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_deb62200:

    # "Rin steps back, still smiling gently at me like I do at her."
    "俺と同じように、優しく微笑み返しながら、琳は後ろに下がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6210
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ab2df5c7:

    # "While she wipes her face on her shoulder, I pick up a round, plump dandelion clock and bring it to my pursed lips."
    "琳が肩で顔をぬぐうあいだ、俺は丸くふっくらとした綿毛坊主を拾い上げ、口元に持ってくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6215
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_3a146420:

    # "Pfff…"
    "ふうぅ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6217
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b8a93731:

    # "They spread out into the wind that picks them up to carry them to a new home."
    "綿毛が風のなかに広がって、新たな場所へと運ばれていく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6219
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_55a80952:

    # "To think, only a few short weeks ago they were so different."
    "つい２、３週間前、あれは全然違う姿だったのに。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6221
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_cb439a12:

    # "This is change."
    "これが変わるってことか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6223
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ce617998_8:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6238
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_fafb6d5d:

    # hi "Hey, so the flowers became what they were meant to become, like you said the last time."
    hi "なあ、あの花はあるべき姿に変わっていったんだな。お前がこの前言ったみたいに"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6240
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7d645e63:

    # hi "What about you? Did you become a true artist? Or did you not, because you ran away?"
    hi "お前はどうだ？　本当の芸術家になれたのか？　それともなれなかったのか？　逃げ出しちまったせいで"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6245
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_a80c04ab:

    # "She pauses for a while to ponder my question…"
    "琳はしばらく固まって考え込むと……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6250
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_257994b8:

    # "…and shrugs her shoulders."
    "……肩をすくめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6252
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_701fa751:

    # "It almost makes me laugh."
    "それを見て俺は笑ってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6254
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_36306071:

    # "The carefree easiness of her gesture is a lovely thing, a sign of how Rin can, truly and really, without any restraints whatsoever, shed the entire weight of the world from her shoulders, should she will so."
    "琳の気楽で落ち着いたしぐさが愛おしい。そうしたいと思えば、琳は言葉通り、本当に、何の遠慮もなく、その肩にかかる全世界の重みを捨て去ることができるんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6256
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f1df82a8:

    # "She is, in every possible and probably a few impossible ways… free."
    "琳は、ありうる全ての意味で、そしてありえないいくつかの意味でも……自由だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6258
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_a91e845d:

    # "And I think I might love her for that."
    "だからこそ、俺は琳を愛しているんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6263
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_6ec9972e:

    # rin "I don't think it matters."
    rin "どうでもいいと思うな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6268
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_ab94e78e:

    # rin "Let's just watch the clouds for today."
    rin "今日は雲でも見てようよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6287
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_5a9bcd03:

    # "She takes five steps to climb on a large rock so she can rise as high as it's possible here, and stands on tiptoes."
    "琳は５歩進んで大きな岩の上に登り、つま先立ちする。そこがこの原っぱで一番高い場所だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6289
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_e3cea480:

    # "When you reach for the clouds, every inch counts."
    "雲をつかもうとするなら、１センチでもおろそかにはできないから。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6291
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_fa1d5ae8:

    # hi "Sure, let's watch the clouds. It's good to do something you really want to do, every now and then."
    hi "そうだな、雲を見よう。時には本当にしたいことをするってのもいいよな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6293
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_185ec3c3:

    # rin "Yeah. You are probably right."
    rin "うん。そうだろうね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6295
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_d5c4a5ec:

    # "I glance upwards at the blue sky opening high above us."
    "頭上高くに広がる青い空を見上げる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6297
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_4631b68d:

    # "It's a deep, cerulean vastness that spreads to fill my entire field of vision and beyond."
    "深い、紺碧の広大な空が視界いっぱいに、そしてその向こうまで伸びている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6299
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_262911d4:

    # "Yet Rin stays on her rock, peering at the distant horizon where the rain clouds are drifting farther away from us."
    "でも琳はまだ岩の上にいて、地平線の彼方で雨雲が遠ざかっていくのを見つめている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6301
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_86bc64cd:

    # rin "I have decided something."
    rin "私、決めたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6303
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_28a01829:

    # "That dreaming voice of hers, spoken to the wind that carries it to my ears, is lacking resolve in tone but is full of it in meaning."
    "琳の夢見心地の声が、風に乗って俺の耳に届く。口調からは決意を感じないけど、その言葉の意味は決意に満ちている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6305
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_e02da6ea:

    # rin "It's all right to be me after all."
    rin "結局、私でいるのがいいんだね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6310
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6313
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_711725db:

    # n "{vspace=90}It's all right? Her decisions always seem to be pretty… far out."
    n "\n\n\nいいだって？　琳の決めることはいつもこう……型破りだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6315
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b15198a8:

    # n "Well, I suppose that is an important realization."
    n "まあ、それに気づくのは大切なことなんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6317
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_35f1365e:

    # n "Coming to terms with oneself, accepting yourself, being fine with what you are."
    n "自分自身と折り合いをつけて、自分を受け入れる。自分のありかたを良いと思う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6319
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_4e0a0991:

    # n "A simple resolution of heart that for some people is overbearingly hard to do, if not impossible."
    n "単純な気の持ちようだけど、それができないとはいかなくても、ひどく苦労する人もいる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6321
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_524d52d2:

    # n "I do realize well enough that I might also be one of those people."
    n "俺もそんな人間の一人かもしれない、ということは十分わかってる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6323
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f26147d8:

    # n "Rin too… "
    n "琳もだ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6325
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_fcf64c52:

    # n "Maybe we are not that different after all."
    n "結局俺たちはそんなに違わなかったのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6327
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_939c1acd:

    # n "Maybe to accept someone else, you must first accept yourself."
    n "他の人を受け入れるためには、まず自分自身を受け入れないといけないのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6329
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_34f1076f:

    # n "Maybe that is a necessary step, which we didn't take until now."
    n "それが俺たちもまだ踏み出せていない、必要なステップなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6335
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_04d21395:

    # nvl clear
    # "Looking at her standing on that rock, I believe that she can find whatever she is looking for."
    nvl clear
    "岩の上に立つ琳を見て、琳なら探しているものを見つけられると確信する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6339
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_9f0b1364:

    # "And so can I."
    "そして俺も。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6346
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_82835758:

    # "The wind catches her hair and clothes, and Rin spreads her short arms into an embrace that is so very very tiny, but as wide as she can ever do."
    "風が琳の髪と服をとらえる。琳は短い腕を広げて、とても小さな、でも琳にとってはこれ以上ないくらい大きな抱擁をする。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6348
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_db7f0eed:

    # "For a moment it looks like she herself might take flight, and I have to hold myself back to not reach for her shoulder, to not drag her back to me."
    "一瞬、琳が空へと飛びだすかのように見えた。琳をこちらに引っ張り戻そうと、その肩に手を伸ばしそうになる自分を抑えないといけなかった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6350
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_b8499f43:

    # "But this picture is something I can only watch, it is something for me to remember."
    "でも、この光景は見ていることしかできないもの、記憶にとどめるべきものだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6352
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_9b19a246:

    # "Rin's sleeves are flapping freely in the wind, her hair wildly tousled by it, her skin touched by the setting sun."
    "琳の袖が風に吹かれて気ままにはためき、髪もひどく乱れている。沈みゆく太陽がその肌に触れる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6354
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_493bb41b:

    # "Her sleek form that I've come to adore is quivering in the cool wind that carries the small white specks past her, each a beginning of a new flower."
    "俺がいつのまにか大好きになった、琳のなだらかな姿が、冷たい風に吹かれて震えている。風は白い小片を運び、その一つ一つがやがて新しい花を咲かせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6356
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_f688e61c:

    # "All that is engraved inside my heart."
    "すべてが心に深く刻み込まれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6358
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_91a6076d:

    # "Like those tiny seeds scattered into the wind, I'm sure that Rin too can take her place in this world without the need to create her own inside of it."
    "風の中に散らばっていく小さな種のように、きっと琳も自分の中に世界を作ったりせず、この世界のどこかに居場所を見いだすことができるはずだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6360
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_92de47e3:

    # "Maybe she believes it too, and standing as close to heaven as possible, she is giving the world a big hug."
    "琳もそう信じているんだろうな。天に少しでも近づけるように立って、世界を強く抱きしめている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6362
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_2e70a0c7:

    # "To me it seems like the entire world really could fit there, between those small arms of hers, inside of her all-encompassing embrace."
    "世界全体が本当にそこに収まってしまいそうに見える。その小さな腕のあいだに。その全てを包み込むような抱擁に。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6367
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_7ea48cf2:

    # rin "Hisao?"
    rin "久夫？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6369
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_0d6a7662:

    # "She looks at me in the same way she calls my name, carelessly over her shoulder with a strange happiness in her voice and in her eyes."
    "琳は気楽そうに、振り向いて俺を見つめ、そして名前を呼ぶ。その声にも視線にも同じように、奇妙な喜びが宿っている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6380
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_6c8c180f:

    # "I gaze into those mysterious, dark eyes that are curiously twinkling from below her auburn hair."
    "赤褐色の髪の下で好奇心いっぱいに輝いている、謎めいた濃緑色の目を見つめる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6382
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_eb1b7eba:

    # "Although I'm too far from her to see it, I'm sure they are reflecting my image."
    "とはいえ、俺からは遠すぎて実際に見えるわけじゃない。きっと俺の想像が反映しているんだろう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6384
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_46b9decc_1:

    # hi "What is it?"
    hi "どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6386
translate jp a4_rin_proof_of_existence_c7aa4277:

    # rin "What's the word for when it feels inside your heart that everything in the world is all right?"
    rin "この世界の何もかもがうまくいってるって心の中で感じてるときのこと、なんて言ったらいいのかな？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6404
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_d5203e2e:

    # "The last day before summer vacations is waning slowly."
    "夏休み前の最後の日も終わりに近づいている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6406
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_defa6eb6:

    # "Science is the final exam of the trimester and then we are free."
    "科学が期末テストの最後の科目で、それで俺たちは解放される。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6408
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_67353f28:

    # "The collective yearning for liberty is almost palpable in the classroom, even though the weather seems a tad cloudy."
    "少し天気が悪いけど、クラス全員の自由への切なる思いは、教室の中で目に見えるかのようだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6410
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_d75f9f63:

    # "It might rain today, who knows."
    "今日は雨かもな、何とも言えないけど。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6417
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_90719bae:

    # "I've already finished the test because it was pretty easy, so I'm doodling lazily on the flip side of the paper, waiting for Mutou to call time."
    "テストはやたら簡単で、とっくに全部解き終えてしまったので、武藤先生が終了を告げるまで用紙の裏にだらだらと落書きをしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6419
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_7e3bb01a:

    # "It also prevents Misha from trying to covertly look at my answers over my shoulder."
    "そうすれば、ミーシャが俺の肩越しに答えをこっそり覗いてくるのも防げる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6421
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_8bc66d8f:

    # "She might fool the inattentive teacher, but I can tell that she is trying to look."
    "不注意な先生はだませるかもしれないけど、俺にはミーシャが覗こうとしていると断言できる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6423
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_af1ad692:

    # "I guess it's her best bet at passing the test. Doesn't make me feel any mercy though, so I just ignore her and look around me."
    "きっとミーシャはこうやってテストを乗り切るしかないんだろう。別に義理立ててやる気にはならないので、俺はミーシャを無視して周りを見渡す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6430
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_eff9b4f7:

    # "It's quiet."
    "静かだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6432
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_116de5c0:

    # "The only sounds in the classroom are the quiet shuffling of papers and Mutou's constant coughing."
    "静かに紙をめくる音と、先生の絶え間ない咳き込みだけが聞こえる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6434
translate jp separate_of_dg_and_wl_6453686b:

    # "It makes my awareness of the surroundings slowly drift to the backstage of consciousness, giving room to other things."
    "その静けさに、俺の周囲への注意は徐々に意識の裏側へと漂って行き、代わりに別のものに置き換わる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6441
translate jp a4rc1o1_18720e4d:

    # hi "But aren't you happy people are interested in your paintings?"
    hi "でも、みんながお前の絵に興味を持ってくれて嬉しくないのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6443
translate jp a4rc1o1_87c0a71d:

    # hi "I mean, isn't that why you went ahead with having the exhibition and all?"
    hi "というか、お前が展覧会やら何やらをやってきたのはそのためなんじゃないのか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6445
translate jp a4rc1o1_dc7080cb:

    # hi "Of course they would ask you questions, if they think it's interesting."
    hi "そりゃみんなだって質問するよ、面白いと思ったらさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6450
translate jp a4rc1o1_4871a9fb:

    # rin "It's like having sunrise twice in a row when you want to bathe naked in moonlight."
    rin "月明かりのなかで裸でお風呂に入りたいと思ってたのに、日の出が２回続いたときみたいだね"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6455
translate jp a4rc1o1_051dcce2:

    # rin "Nice, but…"
    rin "悪くないよ、でも……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6457
translate jp a4rc1o1_fab0bf10:

    # "…it's not good enough, I complete the sentence for her even though I don't understand her inappropriate metaphor."
    "……十分じゃない。琳の的外れな例えは理解できないけど、俺は琳に代わって言葉を補う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6459
translate jp a4rc1o1_8ad29a9a:

    # hi "I don't get it."
    hi "わからないなあ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6461
translate jp a4rc1o1_f64309d0:

    # hi "You should try to be happier. It's your big night, after all."
    hi "もっと嬉しそうにしてみろよ。今夜はお前が主役なんだから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6463
translate jp a4rc1o1_eea5f11c:

    # hi "All these people are here to see your paintings. I think it's awesome."
    hi "みんなお前の絵を観にきてるんだぜ。すごいことじゃないか"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6465
translate jp a4rc1o1_91bccc4c:

    # "I wait for her to say something, either for or against, but Rin keeps brooding."
    "俺は琳が肯定なり否定なり、何か言うのを待つけど、じっと考え込んだままだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6467
translate jp a4rc1o1_8780b264:

    # "She doesn't want to answer questions, or explain to me what's wrong."
    "琳は俺の質問に答えるのも、何が気に入らないのか説明するのもいやなんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6469
translate jp a4rc1o1_3a247e77:

    # "If she had something to say, the words are left unspoken."
    "琳に言いたいことがあったとしても、その言葉は語られないまま終わる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6471
translate jp a4rc1o1_21534cbb:

    # "The words that she cannot say."
    "口にすることができない言葉だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6473
translate jp a4rc1o1_4148f075:

    # "I shudder against the chill wind that blows in the streets, and its howling fills the silence."
    "俺は通りを吹き抜ける冷たい風に身震いする。風はうなりをあげて沈黙を破る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6475
translate jp a4rc1o1_28aa5a0b:

    # hi "We should go back in."
    hi "もう中に戻ろう"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6477
translate jp a4rc1o1_54f14009:

    # hi "You've got everyone worried."
    hi "みんな心配してるぜ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6491
translate jp a4rc1o1_fe38fc84:

    # no "Ah, there you are! Feeling better? It can get pretty hot in here, a dizzy spell can catch you off guard."
    no "ああ、戻ったか！　気分はどうだ？　ここはずいぶんと暑いからな、油断しているとめまいを起こしてしまうぞ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6496
translate jp a4rc1o1_240a236e:

    # "He laughs brashly, almost obnoxiously."
    "先生は豪快に、不愉快なくらいに笑う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6501
translate jp a4rc1o1_c849accb:

    # no "You should drink something if you're feeling weak, Tezuka."
    no "元気がないときは何か飲むといいぞ、手塚"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6516
translate jp a4rc1o1_e86f6490:

    # "Rin nods weakly, but it seems to be enough to convince Nomiya that she is fine."
    "琳は弱々しくうなずくけど、先生に琳が大丈夫なことを納得させるのには十分みたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6518
translate jp a4rc1o1_760f0ae4:

    # "He pushes Rin a bit forward to introduce her to the person he was conversing with before."
    "先生は琳を少し前に押し出して、さっきまで話をしていた人に引き合わせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6523
translate jp a4rc1o1_2fe1c94a:

    # no "So, about what we were talking about before…"
    no "さて、さっき話していたことですが……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6525
translate jp a4rc1o1_e2636d67:

    # "Man" "Ah yes, I'm very excited to meet…"
    "男性" "ええ、お会いできるのを楽しみにしてましたよ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6529
translate jp a4rc1o1_e9c3779b:

    # "I am shut out of the conversation, and the background noise of dozens of other discussions fills my ears with indistinct buzz."
    "俺は会話から締め出されて、ほかのいろいろな議論の喧騒が、不明瞭な騒音になって俺の耳を満たす。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6531
translate jp a4rc1o1_2ce4371a:

    # "Even Emi has disappeared somewhere."
    "笑美もどこかへ行ってしまった。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6533
translate jp a4rc1o1_770334b6:

    # "Standing in the middle of a crowd is a surprisingly lonely feeling."
    "人ごみの中心に立っていると、驚くほど寂しい気持ちになる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6535
translate jp a4rc1o1_0da00f08:

    # "Not only Rin, but everyone else here seems to be a part of something I am not a part of."
    "琳だけじゃなく、誰もが何かの一部になっているような気がする。でも俺はその一部じゃないんだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6537
translate jp a4rc1o1_e389ab9e:

    # "I am happy for her, I really am, but it makes me feel that I haven't accomplished anything yet."
    "俺も琳のことが嬉しい。それは本当だ。でも、同時に俺はまだ何も成し遂げていないという気にもなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6539
translate jp a4rc1o1_26eb7d36:

    # "Rin is living proof of the potential of a human being. She overcame her disability, even made it a strength."
    "琳は人間が持つ可能性の生きた証だ。琳は障害を乗り越えて、それを長所にまでした。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6543
translate jp a4rc1o1_2e1e0b92:

    # "She should be happy."
    "琳は嬉しいはずだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6545
translate jp a4rc1o1_5b8d757f:

    # "What is my potential?"
    "俺には何ができるんだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6547
translate jp a4rc1o1_727d0478:

    # "Rin made it this far, but how far can I go?"
    "琳はここまでやり遂げた。でも俺はどこまでやれる？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6557
translate jp a4rc1o2_12952237:

    # hi "But if you found someone like that, then what?"
    hi "でもそんな人に出会ったとして、それでどうするんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6559
translate jp a4rc1o2_bb78d683:

    # hi "Do you really think that it would be some kind of be-all, end-all thing, star-crossed lovers and happily ever after?"
    hi "それが万事を解決する究極の何かだって、不幸な恋人たちが末永く幸せになるようなものだって、ほんとに思ってるのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6564
translate jp a4rc1o2_391938f6:

    # "My question is met with a blank stare, the darkness in her eyes unfazed by the thinly veiled bitterness."
    "俺の質問に虚ろな視線が返ってくる。琳の目の暗がりはオブラートに包まれた皮肉にも動じない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6569
translate jp a4rc1o2_11f58aa4:

    # rin "No, I don't think that."
    rin "ううん、思ってない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6574
translate jp a4rc1o2_24d42360:

    # rin "But at least then I wouldn't have to be alone."
    rin "でもそうなったら、少なくともひとりぼっちじゃなくなるよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6576
translate jp a4rc1o2_0187605a:

    # "She whispers the words to the lights of the town but I hear them anyway."
    "琳は街の光に向かってささやくけど、どのみち俺にも聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6581
translate jp a4rc1o2_80268023:

    # rin "I shouldn't have done this. Not yet."
    rin "やらなければよかった。今はまだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6583
translate jp a4rc1o2_b6bcf26d:

    # hi "The exhibition?"
    hi "展覧会をか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6588
translate jp a4rc1o2_c0434140:

    # "She nods and closes her eyes, breathing calmly out as if to prove she can, and then continues talking to herself."
    "琳はうなずくと目を閉じて、そうできることを証明するかのように静かに息をつくと、また独り言をつづける。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6590
translate jp a4rc1o2_e477ae1d:

    # hi "Why? Wrong conjunction of the planets?"
    hi "どうしてだ？　星のめぐり合わせが悪いなんていうつもりか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6595
translate jp a4rc1o2_b5bcea0b:

    # rin "No, not that. I double-checked, and I got up with the right, I mean left, foot and did everything else left, I mean right."
    rin "違う、そうじゃない。ちゃんと２回確認して、正しい方の、つまり左足で起き上がったし、他のことは全部左、じゃなくて右足でやったよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6600
translate jp a4rc1o2_4418e933:

    # rin "It's me."
    rin "私なんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6605
translate jp a4rc1o2_716d492a:

    # rin "I was wrong."
    rin "私が間違ってたんだ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6610
translate jp a4rc1o2_34bc704c:

    # "She stands straight and stretches before stepping past me out into the street."
    "琳はまっすぐ立つと伸びをして、俺の前を過ぎて通りに踏み出す。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6612
translate jp a4rc1o2_3d95fc07:

    # hi "Wait, where are you going?"
    hi "おい、どこ行くんだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6617
translate jp a4rc1o2_0a8a9421:

    # "She stops on her tracks and turns around, looking at me quizzically."
    "琳は立ち止まって振り向くと、いぶかしげに俺を見る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6622
translate jp a4rc1o2_5b5a364e:

    # rin "School. I'm leaving."
    rin "学校。帰る"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6624
translate jp a4rc1o2_29a331e5:

    # hi "What… why?"
    hi "え……なんでだよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6629
translate jp a4rc1o2_552c9d52:

    # rin "Because I want to be me."
    rin "私でいたいから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6636
translate jp a4rc1o2_e86075f3:

    # "Rin walks off, leaving me behind utterly confused."
    "完全に混乱した俺を後に残して、琳は立ち去ってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6638
translate jp a4rc1o2_8ed7ccf1:

    # hi "Rin!"
    hi "琳！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6640
translate jp a4rc1o2_96f2635f:

    # "But… something she said really touched me, or maybe it was the way she said it."
    "でも……琳の言ったことは本当に俺の心に響いた。もしかしたらその言い方のせいかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6642
translate jp a4rc1o2_7faf4463:

    # "Maybe it was the fact that {b}she{/b} said it."
    "それとも{b}琳が{/b}言ったという事実が響いたのかも。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6644
translate jp a4rc1o2_a245dd68:

    # "I want to say something back to her, before I forget this feeling again."
    "琳に何か言い返したい、この感じを忘れる前に。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6646
translate jp a4rc1o2_367c704e:

    # "As if granting me a wish, Rin stops in her tracks. She doesn't turn around, just keeps waiting for me to say what I want to even though I didn't have time to think what…"
    "その願いを聞き入れてくれたかのように、琳は足を止める。振り向かないまま、俺が言いたいことを言うのをただ待っている。考える時間なんてなかったけど……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6648
translate jp a4rc1o2_11c487bd:

    # hi "Rin… listen. I… I don't believe you have to be alone, even if you never meet anyone like that."
    hi "なあ……琳……俺……ひとりぼっちでいなきゃいけないなんてことはないと思うぞ。もしそういう人に出会えないとしても"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6650
translate jp a4rc1o2_07e66ab3:

    # "I don't know if she heard my words, but either way, she doesn't react in any way."
    "俺の声が届いてるかはわからないけど、どっちにしろ、琳は何も反応を見せない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6652
translate jp a4rc1o2_1f3c09f6:

    # "For the final time, she starts walking away from the gallery."
    "とうとう、琳はギャラリーから立ち去ってしまう。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6666
translate jp a4rc1o2_f4b98541:

    # no "So? Where's Tezuka?"
    no "うん？　手塚はどうした？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6668
translate jp a4rc1o2_d8f9258c:

    # "I can only shake my head, but as it doesn't seem to be a sufficient answer I have to say something."
    "俺は頭を振るだけしかできないけど、それでは答えとしては不十分だったみたいで、結局何か言わざるをえない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6670
translate jp a4rc1o2_59b1f273:

    # hi "She ran away."
    hi "帰ってしまいました"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6675
translate jp a4rc1o2_4d546cdb:

    # no "What?"
    no "なんだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6677
translate jp a4rc1o2_4dcd46e7:

    # "The horrific realization spreads on his face like wildfire."
    "ぞっとするような表情が先生の顔に山火事のように広がる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6682
translate jp a4rc1o2_d211f350:

    # no "This is a fiasco! Catastrophe!"
    no "なんということだ！　大失態だ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6684
translate jp a4rc1o2_f576e242:

    # no "What is that girl thinking, the most important event of her life, and she just runs off?"
    no "なにを考えているんだ、自分の人生でいちばん重要な機会だというのに、ただ逃げ出しただと？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6689
translate jp a4rc1o2_aab0e52b:

    # no "And you! Why didn't you stop her? I'm going to hold you personally responsible…"
    no "お前もだ！　なぜ止めなかった？　この責任は取ってもらうぞ……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6694
translate jp a4rc1o2_4dd132a6:

    # "Sae interrupts him, holding her hands up calmingly."
    "さえさんが静かに手をあげて制止する。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6696
translate jp a4rc1o2_ccf72d37:

    # "It's good she intervened; the teacher was starting to get a few weird looks from the nearby guests."
    "止めに入ってくれてよかった。周りのお客から変に見られはじめている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6701
translate jp a4rc1o2_6186cb54:

    # sa "Now, now, Shinichi. She probably just had stage fright. I don't know her as well as you people do, but I did get the image that she is somewhat peculiar."
    sa "まあまあ、紳一。きっと人前に出て緊張しちゃったのよ。あの子のことはあなたたちほどはよく知らないけど、でもちょっと変わった子だという印象はあったから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6703
translate jp a4rc1o2_699e0211:

    # sa "This kind of thing can happen."
    sa "こういうこともあるわ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6708
translate jp a4rc1o2_e9541e90:

    # sa "It'll be fine. I'll explain that she suddenly became ill. The guests will surely understand."
    sa "きっと大丈夫よ。具合が悪くなったとでも言っておくわ。それなら納得してもらえるはずよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6713
translate jp a4rc1o2_bff5c3a2:

    # no "But…"
    no "しかし……"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6718
translate jp a4rc1o2_bcc4f1ea:

    # sa "Look around you, everyone seems to be rather happy with their free wine and chitchat."
    sa "周りをごらんなさい、みんなワインとおしゃべりで楽しそうじゃない"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6723
translate jp a4rc1o2_26c512d1:

    # no "The guests will be fine, but we are missing on opportunities here! Networking, making contacts and acquaintances!"
    no "客はいいだろうが、こっちはチャンスを逃しているんだ！　人脈とコネと面識を広げるチャンスを！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6740
translate jp a4rc1o2_b72a99cb:

    # "As the adults keep arguing about something that can't be helped, Emi tugs my sleeve to get my attention."
    "どうにもならないことで大人たちが言い争っているのをよそに、笑美が俺の袖を引っ張って気を引く。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6742
translate jp a4rc1o2_be724e19:

    # "She doesn't look very happy either."
    "どうやら笑美も愉快ではないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6747
translate jp a4rc1o2_5b319ca3:

    # emi "Come on."
    emi "いこうよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6749
translate jp a4rc1o2_804bb8e8:

    # hi "Where?"
    hi "どこにだ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6754
translate jp a4rc1o2_5ac06225:

    # emi "We are going to find Rin and kick her ass."
    emi "琳を探し出してケツに蹴り入れてやるの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6756
translate jp a4rc1o2_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだって？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6761
translate jp a4rc1o2_4746b5f5:

    # emi "I can't believe it, she is so stupid!"
    emi "もう信じらんない、ほんとに馬鹿なんだから！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6763
translate jp a4rc1o2_a0a7c883:

    # emi "That Rin, how can she do this? I'm telling you, she doesn't have a bit of common sense in her head!"
    emi "琳ったらこんなことするなんて！　まったく、常識のかけらもないよ！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6765
translate jp a4rc1o2_fc406d47:

    # "Emi is seriously angry, only missing steam rising from her ears."
    "笑美は真剣に怒っている。足りないのは耳から昇る湯気だけだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6767
translate jp a4rc1o2_469a5e22:

    # "I guess I understand Emi, she is {b}that{/b} kind of a person."
    "笑美の気持ちもわかる気がする。笑美は確かにそういうタイプだからな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6769
translate jp a4rc1o2_57d437cc:

    # "'Give up' has never felt like a part of her vocabulary, and maybe she feels it shouldn't be a part of anyone's vocabulary."
    "『諦める』という言葉は笑美の辞書には絶対載らなさそうだなと思っていた。笑美は誰の辞書にも載っていてはいけないと思っているのかも。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6771
translate jp a4rc1o2_c5c7b1c4:

    # hi "It's probably best to leave her alone for tonight."
    hi "今夜はそっとしておいてやるのがいいと思うけどな"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6776
translate jp a4rc1o2_c92c0faf:

    # emi "What? Are you a Rin expert now?"
    emi "なにそれ？　今度は琳の専門家ってわけ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6778
translate jp a4rc1o2_102f9059:

    # "She takes a firm stance and puts her hands on her hips confrontationally."
    "笑美は断固とした態度を見せて、対決するように両手を腰に当てる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6780
translate jp a4rc1o2_b4c8dd33:

    # "It's like she wants to pick a fight with me too."
    "俺にもけんかを売りたいみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6782
translate jp a4rc1o2_b360fb5b:

    # hi "No, I don't think that's even possible in the first place."
    hi "いや、そんなの最初から無理だと思う"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6784
translate jp a4rc1o2_7415e9df:

    # hi "I just don't think kicking her ass would do her any good."
    hi "あいつのケツに蹴りを入れたって、あいつのためになるとは思えないってだけさ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6789
translate jp a4rc1o2_0d60f350:

    # "My melancholic remark surprisingly works, as Emi slumps her shoulders a little and sighs."
    "俺の憂鬱なコメントは驚くほど効いた。笑美は小さく肩を落としてため息をつく。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6791
translate jp a4rc1o2_33b33736:

    # emi "I know that."
    emi "わかってるよ、そんなの"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6793
translate jp a4rc1o2_9f1e5e09:

    # hi "You do?"
    hi "そうなのか？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6800
translate jp a4rc1o2_ea4fef41:

    # emi "The last time I did that, it changed nothing."
    emi "前にやったときは、なんにも変わらなかったから"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6810
translate jp a4rc1o2_141290f6:

    # "The ride back to school in an empty late-night bus is silent."
    "学校に戻るがらがらな深夜のバスはしんとしている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6812
translate jp a4rc1o2_10a2ec94:

    # "Both of us keep staring at the lights flashing past the windows without saying a word."
    "俺たちは一言も話さず、窓の外を流れる光を眺めている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6821
translate jp a4rc1o2_9a67d91c:

    # "The nightly grounds are quiet, lit only by the wan moon and yellow lamp posts."
    "夜の学校の敷地内は静かで、青白い月と黄色い照明だけに照らされている。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6823
translate jp a4rc1o2_6d116af1:

    # "We say our goodnights in front of my dormitory."
    "俺たちは男子寮の前でおやすみを言う。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6828
translate jp a4rc1o2_2d7f296b:

    # "Emi reflexively clenching her fists compels me to ensure that she won't assault Rin the moment I let her out of my sight."
    "笑美が反射的にぐっとこぶしを握るので、俺は笑美が俺の視界から消えたとたん、琳に襲いかかったりしないよう念を押さずにはいられなくなる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6830
translate jp a4rc1o2_a98dd700:

    # hi "Promise me to not go scold her?"
    hi "琳を叱りに行ったりしないって約束しろよ？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6835
translate jp a4rc1o2_457735d4:

    # "She looks up at me, her eyes again flaring with anger that I match with as calming a stare as I can."
    "笑美は俺を見上げる。その目は怒りに煌々としていて、俺はなるべくなだめるように視線を合わせる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6837
translate jp a4rc1o2_48ea0262:

    # "It's only easy to face an angry woman if you are not the target of her ire."
    "その怒りが自分に向けられているのでないなら、怒っている女性と顔を合わせるのは簡単だ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6839
translate jp a4rc1o2_0f65ea78:

    # "After a minute of the mismatched staring contest, she sighs and shakes her head in defeat."
    "不釣り合いなにらめっこが続いたあと、笑美は負けを認めて、ため息をつくと頭を振る。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6844
translate jp a4rc1o2_13518a67:

    # emi "You are too nice, Hisao."
    emi "優しすぎるんだよ、久夫くんは"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6849
translate jp a4rc1o2_afaddf81:

    # emi "Did you know that?"
    emi "知ってた？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6851
translate jp a4rc1o2_68488c56:

    # "Hints of a smile are tugging the corners of her mouth as she says that, and she seems a lot more relaxed."
    "そういうと、少しばかりの笑顔が笑美の口元をつり上げる。かなり落ち着いたみたいだ。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6853
translate jp a4rc1o2_8e0778e9:

    # "What a sudden change of mood."
    "急に雰囲気が変わるもんだな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6855
translate jp a4rc1o2_113949e1:

    # "Maybe she wasn't as angry as it seemed to begin with."
    "最初からそこまで怒ってたわけじゃないのかもな。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6857
translate jp a4rc1o2_a3433504:

    # "Maybe her moods change easily."
    "気分屋なのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6859
translate jp a4rc1o2_c5ad6a42:

    # hi "If I was, I would've let you have your way."
    hi "もしそうなら、お前の好きにさせてたよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6864
translate jp a4rc1o2_81baeec0:

    # emi "Does that mean you are only nice to Rin?"
    emi "ということは、琳にだけ優しくしてるってこと？"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6866
translate jp a4rc1o2_64604aac:

    # "Both of us are hiding our concern behind empty jokes, but at least it puts me in a good mood."
    "俺たちのどちらも無意味な冗談の裏に気遣いを押し隠してるけど、結局それが俺の気分を良くしてくれる。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6868
translate jp a4rc1o2_52c406c1:

    # "Emi waggles her eyebrows with a half-amused smirk, trying to push my buttons. Not gonna work."
    "笑美は俺を挑発しようと、面白半分のにやけ顔で眉毛を揺らす。そうはいくか。"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6870
translate jp a4rc1o2_384eaea7:

    # hi "No, it just means I'm not nice only to you."
    hi "いや、お前だけには優しくしないってことだよ"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6875
translate jp a4rc1o2_00433e07:

    # emi "HEY!"
    emi "ちょっと！"

# game/script-a4-rin.rpy:6879
translate jp a4rc1o2_6f926c60:

    # hi "Good night, Emi."
    hi "おやすみ、笑美"

